# game/kyou 4.rpy:797
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_bb9701b0:

    # ks smirk "Great. Now get comfortable and watch the light. Focus."
    ks smirk "Grandioso. Ahora ponte cómoda y observa la luz. Concéntrate."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:804
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_60c4b185:

    # "Hiroko settles down and lays back on the couch as she watches me flash the penlight over her curious eyes." with dissolve
    "Hiroko se acomoda y se recarga en el sofá, observando el haz de la linterna con sus ojos curiosos." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:805
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_8302e91f:

    # ks neutral "Focus on the light as it passes across your eyes, and think back on how good it feels to relax under its glow."
    ks neutral "Concéntrate en la luz que pasa por tus ojos, y piensa en lo bien que se siente relajarte bajo su brillo."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:807
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_0e241084:

    # ks "Feeling so good. So relaxed. So focused as you watch the light pass."
    ks "Te sientes tan bien. Tan relajada. Tan concentrada al ver la luz pasar."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:809
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_36a82417:

    # ks "And again..."
    ks "Y otra vez..."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:811
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_c76bebb2:

    # ks "You'll notice as you blink, it becomes a little harder to open those eyelids again."
    ks "Notarás que cada vez que parpadeas, se vuelve un poco más difícil volver a abrir tus ojos."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:817
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_1052c4f2:

    # ks "And that's perfectly fine, Hiroko. Perfectly natural for you to become tired, your eyelids heavier, as the light passes your eyes again." with dissolve
    ks "Y eso está perfectamente bien, Hiroko. Es perfectamente natural estar cansada, que tus párpados pesen, mientras la luz vuelve a pasar por tus ojos una..." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:819
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_36a82417_1:

    # ks "And again..."
    ks "Y otra vez..."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:823
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_0f7cdd40:

    # ks "That's right, Hiroko, no need to fight it. Just letting the light take you down..." with dissolve
    ks "Eso es, Hiroko, no hace falta luchar. Solo déjate llevar por la luz..." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:825
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_0cfd6282:

    # ks "And down..."
    ks "Muy profundo..."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:827
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_d1315337:

    # ks "And closing your eyes, and... sleep, Hiroko."
    ks "Cierra tus ojos, y... duerme, Hiroko."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:829
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_f7c8c6eb:

    # "Her eyes snap shut as her head slightly droops. That was the easy part, of course." with dissolve
    "Sus ojos se cierran y su cabeza cae ligeramente. Esa fue la parte fácil, por supuesto." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:831
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_9dc93da1:

    # ks "Now focus on my voice, Hiroko. Hear the natural cadence of my words, and how soothing they sound to your ears. How easy it is to listen."
    ks "Ahora concéntrate en mi voz, Hiroko. Escucha la cadencia natural de mis palabras, y lo dulce que suenan en tus oídos. Es muy fácil escuchar."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:832
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_287ca528:

    # ks "Can you do that for me, Hiroko?"
    ks "¿Puedes hacer eso por mí, Hiroko?"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:833
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_46c324b7:

    # h sleeptalk "Yeah..." with dissolve
    h sleeptalk "Seh..." with dissolve

