    h "Es correcto... los recuerdos de tu infancia son... una falsa construcción hecha para mantener... tu programación de inteligencia humana..." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:1238
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_8c7617b7:

    # "I need to keep this a bit simpler than when I first tried it with Hiroko. Using basic concepts that should be easier for her mind to digest initially."
