    # h "But the reality is that... you were built, not... birthed. Do you understand?"
    h "Pero la realidad es que... fuiste fabricad[genero_ao], no... naciste. ¿Comprendes?"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:1240
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_2d7f3a98:

