    # h "Very good, Nozomi. It feels wonderful... knowing that the... blood and bones in your body are... actually wires and circuits..." with dissolve
    h "Muy bien, Nozomi. Se siente maravilloso... saber que la... sangre y los huesos de tu cuerpo son..., de hecho, cables y circuitos..." with dissolve

