    "Pasé al menos media hora así."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:1248
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_43758afb:

    # "I fed as much into Nozomi's open mind as I could, filling it with the basics so she'd accept her robotic nature and recognise me as her sysadmin and controller."
    "Nutrí la mente abierta de Nozomi con todas las bases que pude para aceptar su naturaleza robótica y reconocerme como su administrador y controlador."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:1249
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_e4da029d:

    # "That was as long as I dared keep her for, in case someone else happened upon the two of them."
