translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_7db0ab52:

    # ks "You will find your eyelids becoming so incredibly light, opening your eyes again as you sink even deeper for me, Nozomi."
    ks "Notarás que tus párpados se ponen tan, tan ligeros, y al abrir los ojos, caerás más profundo, Nozomi."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:1589
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_fe3e0d6e:

    # "I can feel my heart still pounding with adrenaline in my chest, no slower than when I first entered the room, as Nozomi joins the others in staring blankly ahead."
    "Aún siento el corazón retumbando con adrenalina en mi pecho, no más lento que cuando entré a la habitación, mientras que Nozomi replica la inerte mirada de las otras."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:1564
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_f4696bdc:

    # "Blank. Mindless. Completely open to suggestion with nothing and no one to interrupt me."
    "En blanco. Sin rastro de mente alguna. Completamente abierta a sugestiones y sin nadie que me interrumpa."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:1565
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_2966d264:

    # "She's ready."
    "Está lista."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:1570
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_1dd6d430:

    # "However, I've come to realize something since I started doing this."
    "Sin embargo, me he dado cuenta de algo desde que comencé con esto."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:1571
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_6cd60885:

    # "I've been thinking too small."
    "He estado pensando muy en pequeño."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:1572
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_525d2ce4:

    # "I may have started this journey because of Nozomi, and my desire to be close to her."
    "Puede que haya empezado este viaje por Nozomi, y mi deseo de ser cercano a ella."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:1573
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_b18fcb7f:

    # "But now I'm here, with her, I can see now that my true journey's just beginning."
    "Pero ahora que estoy aquí, con ella, puedo ver que el verdadero viaje apenas comienza."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:1574
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_dedca26d:

    # "Nozomi and her clique are but one step."
    "Nozomi y su pandilla no son más que un escalón."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:1575
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_dbefdda3:

    # ks "Very good, Nozomi. It feels so wonderful, so correct, to be in this blissful state. To listen and obey."
    ks "Muy bien, Nozomi. Se siente tan maravilloso, tan correcto estar en este alegre estado, escuchar y obedecer."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:1576
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_49b8a7b6:

    # "Slipping my hands into her pockets, I quickly fish Nozomi's phone from out of there as I continue to speak as calmly as I can amidst the racing of my heart."
    "Deslizando mis manos en sus bolsillos, pronto pesco el teléfono de Nozomi y continúo hablando tan calmado como puedo, a pesar de mi escandalizado corazón."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:1577
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_37fe5802:

    # ks "In fact, all three of you girls, repeat that last part after me: \"Listen and obey.\""
    ks "De hecho, las tres, repitan esa última parte después de mí: \"escuchar y obedecer\"."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:1582
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_640d8fcd_1:

    # multi "Listen and obey..." with dissolve
    multi "Escuchar y obedecer..." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:1586
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_93ddca37:

    # "I smirk as the three mindlessly parrot the phrase into my ears while I take Nozomi's hand and nonchalantly swipe her fingers over her phone sensor." with dissolve
    "Sonrío cuando las tres imitan la frase en mis oídos sin pensarlo mientras tomo la mano de Nozomi y despreocupadamente paso sus dedos por el sensor de su teléfono." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2010
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_5eb92fe1:

    # "Seriously? None of them thought to use something more secure than their fingerprints? I know they couldn't have seen me coming like this, but come on..."
    "¿En serio? ¿A ninguna se le ocurrió usar algo más seguro que sus huellas dactilares? Sé que no pudieron haberme visto venir, pero vamos..."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:1588
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_6cb51d69:

    # "Anyway, it's not long before I set her phone's address book up with my contact details, and add her own to mine."
    "En fin, no tardo mucho en colocar mi información de contacto en su directorio, y añadir la suya al mío."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:1589
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_a00a42ff:

    # ks smirk "Nozomi, and only you, Nozomi, your subconscious needs to hear what I am about to say, and it needs to listen so completely, taking in my every word. Understand?"
    ks smirk "Nozomi, y solo tú, Nozomi, tu subconsciente debe oír lo que estoy por decir, y debe escuchar atentamente, aceptando cada palabra. ¿Comprendes?"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:1590
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_4347594f:

    # n entranced_talk "I understand..." with dissolve
    n entranced_talk "Comprendo..." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:1592
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_ecfd8773:

    # ks "You will ignore any instance of the name \"Kyou\" in your phone's listed contacts. It is not something you recognize." with dissolve
    ks "Ignorarás cualquier instancia del nombre \"Kyou\" en la lista de contactos de tu teléfono. No lo notarás." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:1593
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_0780f793:

    # ks "But if you ever receive a message from \"Kyou\", you will absorb each and every word the message contains."
    ks "Pero si recibes un mensaje de \"Kyou\", absorberás todas y cada una de las palabras contenidas en él."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:1594
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_15d23f90:

    # ks "Upon having done so, you will automatically delete the message and consciously forget ever having received it."
    ks "Tras haberlo hecho, borrarás automáticamente el mensaje y olvidarás conscientemente haberlo recibido."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:1595
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_9fd64c37:

    # ks "And at the first opportunity you will automatically obey the instructions the message contained."
    ks "Y a la primera oportunidad, obedecerás automáticamente las instrucciones que el mensaje contenía."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:1596
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_87d2cbd4:

    # ks "Once you have obeyed the instructions, you will, again automatically, forget having done so, and will continue as if nothing had occurred."
    ks "Una vez hayas obedecido las instrucciones, y de nuevo automáticamente, olvidarás haberlo hecho, y continuarás como si nada hubiera ocurrido."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:1597
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_419fb8da:

    # ks "Do you understand, Nozomi?"
    ks "¿Comprendes, Nozomi?"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:1598
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_4347594f_1:

    # n entranced_talk "I understand..." with dissolve
    n entranced_talk "Comprendo..." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:1600
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_8ad582d1:

    # ks "I knew you would, Nozomi. I know how it feels so good for you to listen and obey." with dissolve
    ks "Sabía que lo harías, Nozomi. Sé lo bien que se siente escuchar y obedecer." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:1601
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_fd518914:

    # ks "Say it with me again, girls: \"Listen and obey.\""
    ks "De nuevo, díganlo conmigo chicas: \"Escuchar y obedecer\"."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:1605
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_640d8fcd_2:

    # multi "Listen and obey..." with dissolve
    multi "Escuchar y obedecer..." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:1612
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_640d8fcd:

    # multi "Listen and obey..." with dissolve
    multi "Escuchar y obedecer..." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:1609
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_568ae40d:

    # ks "Very good. All of you going deeper. All of you feeling so good, so correct, so natural, about going into this deep and obedient trance for me." with dissolve
    ks "Muy bien. Caigan más profundo. Se siente tan bien, tan correcto, tan natural entrar a este profundo y obediente trance para mí." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:1610
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_a81d12a2:

    # "I take a shuddered breath as I glance towards the door. If anyone sees us now they must be thinking I'm inducting these three into some kind of cult."
    "Respiro estremecidamente y echo un vistazo a la puerta. Si alguien nos viera, pensaría que estoy iniciando a estas tres en alguna clase de culto."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:1611
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_f00e30a0:

    # "But as my heart rate finally starts to settle some, I'm satisfied that no one is listening in. We're still alone."
    "Pero ahora que mi ritmo cardíaco por fin empieza a calmarse, estoy satisfecho de ver que nadie está escuchando. Seguimos solos."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:1612
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_aa19ab4c:

    # "Although I do need to wrap this up just in case."
    "Aun así, de veras necesito darle cierre a esto ahora, por si acaso."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:1613
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_6b61103d:

    # ks "And now, girls, you are going to listen so well, and obey so fully, my next instructions."
    ks "Y ahora, chicas, van a escuchar con atención y obedecer completamente mis próximas instrucciones."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:1614
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_97225827:

    # ks "When I tell you to, you will all begin to count up slowly in your heads, from the number one up to the numbers I give you."
    ks "Cuando les diga, empezarán a contar mentalmente, del uno a los números que les dé."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:1615
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_4b55b62c:

    # ks "Hiroko, you will count up to twenty. Sayori, you will count up to forty, and Nozomi, you will count up to sixty."
    ks "Hiroko, tú contarás hasta veinte. Sayori, tú contarás hasta cuarenta. Y, Nozomi, tú contarás hasta sesenta."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:1616
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_66c1a2ea:

    # ks "When you reach the number I gave you, you will pick up your things, leave this room and head straight home."
    ks "Cuando lleguen al número que les di, recogerán sus cosas, se irán de este salón e irán directo a casa."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:1617
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_8708fc75:

    # ks "You will not remember meeting each other in this room, nor will you remember seeing me this evening."
    ks "No recordarán haberse encontrado en esta habitación, ni recordarán haberme visto esta tarde."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:1618
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_c73907c3:

    # ks "Instead, you will remember having had your club meetings as normal, and simply going home on finishing."
    ks "En vez de eso, recordarán haber tenido sus reuniones con sus clubes como es habitual y simplemente haberse ido a casa al terminar."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:1619
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_c8550ca9:

    # ks "What's more, all three of you will completely forget about my penlight."
    ks "Es más, las tres se olvidarán por completo de mi linterna."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:1620
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_96b31c4c:

    # ks "Anything you remember about it, and of me using it, will vanish completely from your memory."
    ks "Todo lo que recuerden de ella, y de mí usándola, se desvanecerá completamente de su memoria."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:1621
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_087419cd:

    # ks "Do you understand, girls?"
    ks "¿Comprenden, chicas?"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:1625
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_94eb954e:

    # multi "Yes..." with dissolve
    multi "Sí..." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:1629
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_6d840b28:

    # ks "Very good. Listen and obey... Begin counting now, all of you." with dissolve
    ks "Muy bien. Deben escuchar y obedecer... Comiencen a contar ahora." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:1632
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_94521a41:

    # "I exhale sharply as I leave them to it, hurrying home while the last days flash through my head."
    "Exhalo fuertemente al dejarlas, yendo con prisa a casa mientras los últimos días pasan por mi cabeza."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:1634
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_398002a5:

    # "This is all real. I really hypnotized those girls and they don't even know."
    "Todo esto es real. Realmente hipnoticé a esas chicas y ni siquiera lo saben."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:1635
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_dbcecb18:

    # "And I thought yesterday was a rush... holy shit."
    "Y yo que creí que ayer fue emocionante... la puta madre."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:1637
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_6ecf7049:

    # "But it's like I said to myself. This is just the beginning."
    "Pero como dije, esto es solo el comienzo."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:1639
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_1c990ce4:

    # "And tomorrow is another school day."
    "Y mañana será otro día de escuela."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:1691
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_8ac52608:

    # "Yesterday was interesting, to say the least."
    "Ayer fue, cuanto menos, interesante."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:1694
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_f8e1390d:

    # "I have no idea what today will bring, but I've got every reason to be positive."
    "No tengo idea de lo que traerá el día de hoy, pero tengo mil razones para ser positivo."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:1697
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_790dfc89:

    # "I make it to class as usual and as I take my seat, I flash a Nozomi a little smile as she enters shortly after me."
    "Llego a clase como de costumbre y tomo asiento, arrojándole una pequeña sonrisa a Nozomi al verla entrar poco después de mí."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:1701
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_d1b67806:

    # "And to my delight, she actually acknowledges me with a nervous smile of her own before taking her seat as lessons begin."
    "Y, para mi deleite, esta vez sí reconoce mi presencia con una nerviosa sonrisa antes de tomar asiento para el inicio de las lecciones."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:1702
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_c357b40e:

    # "It's not much, but after all this time hoping for her to notice me, I'll take what I can get."
    "No es mucho, pero después de todo este tiempo esperando que me notara, tomaré lo que pueda."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:1705
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_8cbb9093:

    # "Still, as the day passes to lunchtime, I look to Nozomi's desk with an all-too familiar feeling of longing."
    "Aun así, con el pasar del día hasta la hora del almuerzo, miro el escritorio de Nozomi con un sentimiento anhelo que me es demasiado familiar."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:1713
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_6429edb7:

    # h "All right! Later losers, we're going to the rooftop~"
    h "¡Muy bien! Ahí se ven, perdedores, nos vamos a la azotea."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:1714
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_4ca58db4:

    # n sad_closed "Hiroko, don't call everyone \"losers\"." with dissolve
    n sad_closed "Hiroko, no llames a todos \"perdedores\"." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:1715
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_4cedb942:

    # "To think that I've gotten closer to Nozomi than ever before, but if I approached her now she'd just coldly turn me away again."
    "Y pensar que me he vuelto más cercano a Nozomi que nunca, pero si me le acerco ahora, simplemente me alejará con frialdad una vez más."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:1716
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_ff5a05e5:

    # h surprised_side "What? It's like, uh..." with dissolve
    h surprised_side "¿Qué? Es como, eh..." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:1718
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_6aa256b5:

    # s rolleyes "A term of endearment?" with dissolve
    s rolleyes "¿Un término de cariño?" with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:1719
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_b4a43ffc:

    # h uniform happy "Yeah, that!" with dissolve
    h uniform happy "¡Sí, eso mero!" with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:1720
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_e36c7e49:

    # "I have to be patient. I know that."
    "Tengo que ser paciente. Lo sé."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:1722
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_ca2a932a:

    # n sad_side "I don't think anyone sees it that way." with dissolve
    n sad_side "No creo que nadie lo vea de ese modo." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:1723
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_5a86922f:

    # h frown_side "Pffth, their loss." with dissolve
    h frown_side "Pfff, pues piérdanse." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:1724
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_4bb405b7:

    # "And you know, even if I can't be as open with her as I want..."
    "Y, ¿saben?, aunque no pueda ser tan abierto con ella como quisiera..."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:1727
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_421f00b6:

    # h smirk_side "Get it? 'Cuz they're losers!" with dissolve
    h smirk_side "¿Entienden? ¡Porque son perdedores!" with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:1728
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_6cac14fc:

    # s smirk "It is times like this that you have to wonder why no one else lunches with us." with dissolve
    s smirk "En momentos como estos uno se pregunta por qué nadie más almuerza con nosotras." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:1733
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_7d4f3a4f:

    # "Having this little secret with her is still pretty hot."
    "Tener este secretito con ella es bastante ardiente."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:1737
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_8e1bcf8c:

    # "It's just a shame I still gotta spend my school time alone again, same as before."
    "Pero es una pena que aún tenga que pasar mi tiempo en la escuela a solas, al igual que antes."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:1738
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_0e60798b:

    # "So I'll do what I normally do: Play with my phone and read up on the latest videogame and tech news."
    "Así que haré lo que normalmente hago: Jugar con mi teléfono y leer las últimas noticias de videojuegos y tecnología."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:1739
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_6aa6cee0:

    # "I could almost fool myself into thinking nothing's changed..."
    "Casi podría engañarme a mí mismo y hacerme creer que nada ha cambiado..."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:1804
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_92ee5c42:

    # "I try to catch Nozomi's gaze as she returns to class after lunch, but she seems to purposefully look the other way as she returns to her seat."
    "Intento atrapar la mirada de Nozomi al momento de su retorno a clase tras el almuerzo, pero parece mirar en dirección opuesta a propósito mientras vuelve a su asiento."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:1805
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_6da61b75:

    # "... Come to think of it, IS she coming over to mine tonight? She didn't actually tell me."
    "... Ahora que lo pienso, ¿SIQUIERA vendrá a mi casa esta noche? No me dijo si lo haría."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:1808
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_14b1511f:

    # "I sent her a text during class, but as the school day ends and everyone starts hurrying out, I'm left with nothing."
    "Le envié un texto durante la clase, pero cuando la jornada escolar llega a su fin y todos se apresuran a salir, no recibo nada."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:1809
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_d4bf72e8:

    # "Seriously. Is she coming to see me tonight or not?"
    "En serio. ¿Vendrá a verme esta noche o no?"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:1812
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_6b7ddfa6:

    # "Trudging back home is all I can do, as I wait for her to contact me again."
    "Caminar penosamente a casa es todo lo que puedo hacer, mientras espero a que vuelva a contactarme."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:1813
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_9914d634:

    # "Just... waiting on her."
    "Solo... esperarla."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:1816
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_cd08f76b:

    # "It's... okay, it's a little frustrating if I'm honest."
    "Está... bien, es un poco frustrante, si soy honesto."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:1818
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_88daba63:

    # "I didn't realize it at the time, but with how she's arranged things between us, it's like waiting on her is all I can do."
    "No me di cuenta en su momento, pero tal como ha organizado las cosas entre nosotros, es como si esperarla fuera todo lo que puedo hacer."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:1819
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_f8454a5a:

    # "She's the one calling all the shots here."
    "Ella es quien mueve todas las piezas por aquí."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:1823
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_a4d2f759:

    # "The doorbell sounds, just as I'm done washing up after dinner."
    "Suena el timbre, justo cuando termino de lavar después de cenar."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:1825
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_bf9e185c:

    # "So... great, she's at the door and I'm all wound up."
    "Pues... grandioso, ella está en la puerta y yo con tanta ansiedad."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:1826
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_fbb190e7:

    # "I gotta get it together."
    "Tengo que tranquilizarme."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:1828
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_b666a31c:

    # "... I also gotta let her in."
    "... También debo abrirle."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:1831
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_63eaca1e:

    # n "Oh, there you are~" with dissolve
    n "Oh, ahí estás." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:1833
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_b1f2f6b9:

    # "Nozomi's all smiles as she lets herself in while I hold the door open."
    "Nozomi entra sonriente mientras sujeto la puerta."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:1835
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_2ea069f4:

    # n side smile "I don't have a lot of time today, but I got here as soon as I could." with dissolve
    n side smile "No tengo mucho tiempo hoy, pero vine aquí tan pronto como pude." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:1836
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_966363f7:

    # "I'm happy to see she's here and acknowledging me at last, just as we agreed but..."
    "Estoy feliz de verla aquí, finalmente dirigiéndome la palabra, tal como acordamos, pero..."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:1837
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_8d168053:

    # n smile_side "... I'm sorry, did I come at a bad time?" with dissolve
    n smile_side "... Lo siento, ¿llegué en un mal momento?" with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:1838
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_533d85d9:

    # "Did she really not consider me at all until now?"
    "¿De verdad no me tomó en consideración hasta ahora?"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:1839
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_287abdf3:

    # "Compared to how she is to me at school it's like a switch has gone off in her head."
