    ks "¿Nozomi?"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2115
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_db6d1212:

    # "Seriously. It's kind of eerie how the light switched off in her head like that. She almost looks like a mannequin with how lifeless she seems right now."
    "Vaya. Es un poco aterrador ver las luces apagarse así en su cabeza. Casi parece un maniquí con lo carente de vida que se ve en este momento."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2116
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_be33b26d:

    # "Almost, as I notice she's starting to drool out of one corner of her mouth where she let it hang open."
    "Casi, pues noto que está empezando a babear por una comisura de su boca, ya que la dejó abierta."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2117
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_c1290ad0:

    # "She'll snap back to life eventually I'm sure, but right now it almost feels like I could leave her like this for hours and come back to find her exactly the same."
    "Eventualmente volverá a la vida, estoy seguro, pero ahora mismo, casi se siente como si pudiera dejarla así por horas y regresar para encontrarla exactamente igual."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2118
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_78d2fd1d:

    # "Although that reminds me, she said she didn't have long before she had to leave."
    "Aunque eso me recuerda, dijo que no tenía mucho tiempo antes de tener que irse."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2120
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_157d730a:

    # "So once more, I sweep my hand over her vacant eyes..."
    "Así que, una vez más, paso mi mano por sus vacantes ojos..."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2122
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_1f43772d:

    # "So once more, I gently press my index finger against her forehead."
    "Así que, una vez más, presiono gentilmente mi dedo índice contra su frente."

