    # "Time to finish for tonight..."
    "Hora de dar cierre a la noche..."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2130
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_fc5b69b1:

    # ks "Very good, Nozomi. You're so good at this, dropping deep, back into this hypnotic trance that makes you feel so wonderful."
    ks "Muy bien, Nozomi. Eres muy buena en esto. Caes muy profundo, de vuelta a este trance hipnótico que se siente tan maravilloso."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2132
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_0501f29d:

    # ks "So now, while you're so deep, listening only to my voice, I want you to think of all the things I suggested to you while waving my hand in front of your face."
    ks "Ahora, mientras estás tan profundo, escuchando mi voz, quiero que pienses en todas las sugestiones que te di mientras movía mi mano frente a tu rostro."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2134
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_9302285f:

    # ks "So now, while you're so deep, listening only to my voice, I want you to think of all the things I suggested to you whenever I pressed my fingertip to your forehead."
    ks "Ahora, mientras estás tan profundo, escuchando mi voz, quiero que pienses en todas las sugestiones que te di cada vez que puse mi dedo en tu frente."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2135
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_7a0ab058:

    # ks "And now Nozomi, I want you to imagine each and every one of those suggestions leaving your mind. Each and every one losing their influence..."
    ks "Y ahora, Nozomi, quiero que imagines todas y cada una de esas sugestiones abandonando tu mente. Todas y cada una perdiendo su influencia..."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2136
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_292d340b:

    # ks "Each and every one of those suggestions no longer having any affect on you whatsoever. Understand?"
    ks "Todas y cada una de esas sugestiones dejando de tener efecto sobre ti. ¿Comprendes?"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2147
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_3773fc6c:

    # ncg sleeptalk "I understand..."
    ncg sleeptalk "Comprendo..."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2148
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_28a7f8bd:

    # ks smile "I knew you would, Nozomi. You're so good at being hypnotized. So good at following instructions."
    ks smile "Sabía que lo harías, Nozomi. Eres muy buena siendo hipnotizada. Muy buena siguiendo instrucciones."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2140
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_c8bcd08e:

    # ks "And in a moment I'm going to wake you up from this trance, and you're going to remember what we did together."
    ks "Y en un momento, voy a despertarte de este trance, y recordarás lo que hicimos juntos."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2141
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_10e37719:

    # ks "Waking up on a count of three, Nozomi. One..."
    ks "Despertarás a la cuenta de tres, Nozomi. Uno..."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2143
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_6be7bbe6:

    # ks "Two... feeling refreshed, nice deep breath..."
    ks "Dos... sintiéndote fresca, respira profundamente..."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2144
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_1c031160:

    # ks "And three, rise and shine."
    ks "Y tres, a levantarse."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2147
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_7d34b2a6:

    # "Nozomi moans as she flickers slowly back into life."
    "Nozomi suelta un quejido regresando lentamente a la vida."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2149
