    # "I smile at her as she takes a moment to settle back into her own head. She really seemed to be out of it just now."
    "Le sonrío y se toma un momento para reincorporar su mente. Hace un momento parecía que estaba completamente perdida."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2150
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_3673b75d:

    # ks "Hey. You doing okay?"
    ks "¿Qué tal? ¿Te encuentras bien?"

