translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_5200f044:

    # "She still seems to be getting her bearings when I ask, but she eventually replies softly." with dissolve
    "Aún parece estar comenzando a ponerse en marcha cuando pregunto, pero eventualmente responde con suavidad." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2167
