    # "It would've been stupid to try. She was awake and aware and, more to the point, she wasn't going to let me stop her."
    "Habría sido estúpido intentarlo. Estaba despierta y consciente y, lo más importante, no iba a dejarme detenerla."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2184
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_6163329d:

    # "I can't use hypnosis to literally force my will on her, I know that's not how it works."
    "No puedo usar la hipnosis para forzar literalmente mi voluntad sobre ella, sé que no es así como funciona."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2185
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_d9c4eceb:

    # "But still, in the moment it almost seemed worth the risk of making her mad just to see if she'd go along with it."
    "Pero, aun así, en ese momento casi parecía que valía la pena el riesgo de hacerla enojar solo para ver si seguía la corriente."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2186
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_22d8cec6:

    # "... I'm such an idiot, thinking about shit like this."
    "... Qué idiota soy, pensando en mierda como esa."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2188
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_107fa489:

