    # n "It was like a dozen tiny hands were tickling me all over, and there was nothing I could do to stop them."
    n "Era como si una docena de manitas me estuvieran haciendo cosquillas por todas partes, y no podía hacer nada para detenerlas."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2460
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_b9d6618d:

    # n blush "And everyone was staring at me. They all knew." with dissolve
    n blush "Yo todos me estaban mirando. Todos lo sabían." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2461
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_6f568dfd:

    # n concerned "Kyou, this is going to follow me for the rest of my school career." with dissolve
    n concerned "Kyou, esto me perseguirá por el resto de mi carrera escolar." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2462
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_e12eeefb:

    # n "So I... I think the public trigger was a bad idea and I never should have agreed to it."
    n "Así que... creo que el ancla pública fue una mala idea y nunca debí acceder ella."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2463
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_04dade66:

    # ks "I'm sorry, Nozomi. I probably should've been more careful when setting it."
    ks "Lo lamento, Nozomi. Creo debí ser más cuidadoso al instalarla."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2464
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_6c538375:

    # n sleeptalk "Yeah..." with dissolve
    n sleeptalk "Seh..." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2465
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_bebdd7ea:

    # n pout_left uniform "So... I was thinking some more about what to do." with dissolve
    n pout_left uniform "Pues... estaba pensando en qué más hacer." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2466
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_06acd751:

    # ks neutral "Yeah?"
    ks neutral "¿Ah, sí?"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2467
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_d6ca65c3:

    # n "I want you to remove the trigger, Kyou. You can do that, can't you?"
    n "Quiero que remuevas el ancla, Kyou. Puedes hacerlo, ¿verdad?"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2468
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_3ca7e16d:

    # ks "I think so. I haven't tried to de-program you yet, but I don't see why I couldn't."
    ks "Eso creo. No he intentado desprogramarte, pero no veo por qué no."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2470
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_aa389cc5:

    # "She responds with a tentative nod." with dissolve
    "Responde asintiendo tentativamente." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2471
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_83d8646e:

    # n "Right. And then I'd like us to try something else. We could consider it a trade of sorts."
    n "Correcto. Y luego me gustaría probar algo más. Podríamos considerarlo como alguna especie de trato."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2472
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_f74dcb07:

    # "... What on earth is she thinking now?"
    "... ¿En qué rayos está pensando ahora?"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2473
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_d5ce8245:

    # ks "Go on..."
    ks "Continúa..."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2474
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_3dfba4b7:

    # n "I want you to try conditioning some behaviours into me."
    n "Quiero que intentes condicionar en mí ciertos comportamientos."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2475
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_d331a89f:

    # n side sad_closed blush "S-submissive ones. Towards you." with dissolve
    n side sad_closed blush "S-sumisos. Hacia ti." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2476
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_de67cbe1:

    # ks surprised "... Wait, what?"
    ks surprised "... Espera, ¿qué?"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2477
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_56bc6e11:

    # n sad "O-only for in your house! And, only when we're alone." with dissolve
    n sad "¡S-solo para tu casa! Y, solo cuando estemos a solas." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2478
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_c648cfc8:

    # n front surprised reddened "And NOTHING lewd! Oh gosh, I should've mentioned that sooner." with vpunch
    n front surprised reddened "¡Y NADA sucio! Ay, Dios, debí empezar por ahí." with vpunch

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2479
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_1a8f877a:

    # ks "But still, that's..."
    ks "Pero, aun así, es..."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2480
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_c550e1ab:

    # n sleeptalk_concerned normal uniform_folded "Weird. And stupid and embarrassing to say out loud, but I don't think I could feel more humilated than I did this afternoon, so I'll get this out now." with dissolve
    n sleeptalk_concerned normal uniform_folded "Raro. Y estúpido y vergonzoso decirlo en voz alta, pero no creo poder sentirme más humillada que esta tarde, entonces, que sea ahora." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2481
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_73bef442:

    # n "Because as humiliating as that was, I still couldn't help but feel how much I enjoyed being powerless. Knowing I was feeling that way because you hypnotized me to."
    n "Ya que, por humillante que fuera, no pude evitar sentir lo mucho que disfruté ser impotente. Saber que me sentía así porque me hipnotizaste para sentirlo."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2482
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_7110bb07:

    # n side sad_closed "And being unable to resist your programming, even though in the moment I wanted to more than anything." with dissolve
    n side sad_closed "Y ser incapaz de resistir tu programación, aunque en el momento fuese lo que más quería." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2483
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_4ae795a7:

    # n "I can't even begin to describe how intoxicating it all felt."
    n "Ni siquiera puedo empezar a describir lo estimulante que fue esa sensación."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2484
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_2b1eadd0:

    # n frown "So... I want to have that experience again, just not where it might seriously come back to hurt me." with dissolve
    n frown "Así que... quiero vivir esa experiencia de nuevo, pero no donde exista la posibilidad de que regrese para hacerme daño." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2485
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_154c9d82:

    # n front concerned "W-what do you think?" with dissolve
    n front concerned "¿Qu-qué opinas?" with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2486
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_7b7ea701:

    # ks "It's... T-that is..."
    ks "Es... E-eso es..."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2487
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_2028f6d7:

    # n angry normal "Oh come {w=0.4}{nw}" with dissolve
    n angry normal "¡Ay, por {w=0.4}{nw}" with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2488
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_b1f9cc2e:

    # extend "ON, Kyou! How many guys do you think get a chance like this?" with vpunch
    extend "FAVOR, Kyou! ¿Cuántos chicos crees que reciben una oportunidad así?" with vpunch

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2489
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_b297b2f8:

    # "I jump back a little as she raises her voice, and it jolts my brain back into gear." with dissolve
    "Doy un pequeño sobresalto cuando levanta la voz, lo cual pone mi cerebro de nuevo en marcha." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2490
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_c04b72c1:

    # "Do I really have any objections to this? Why not give her what she wants?"
    "¿Realmente tengo alguna objeción contra esto? ¿Por qué no darle lo que quiere?"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2491
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_c5eddf4a:

    # "And why not do it in a way she'll approve?"
    "¿Y por qué no hacerlo de una forma que ella apruebe?"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2493
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_6936cd7d:

    # "With a smile, I pull my penlight out from its home in my pocket, which immediately grabs Nozomi's attention." with dissolve
    "Con una sonrisa, saco mi linterna de su hogar en mi bolsillo, lo cual atrapa inmediatamente la atención de Nozomi." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2494
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_408db2ee:

    # ks smirk "I'll make that the last time you raise your voice to me in this house, young lady."
    ks smirk "Me aseguraré de que esa sea la última vez que me alces la voz, jovencita."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2498
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_9b30657f:

    # "And with that I flash the light across her eyes, causing her to immediately snap her gaze to it with a peculiar longing."
    "Dicho eso, paso la luz por sus ojos, de inmediato haciéndola dirigir su vista hacia ella con un anhelo peculiar."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2499
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_9dd20283:

    # n "K-kyou..."
    n "K-kyou..."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2501
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_99db376d:

    # ks "Shhh, Nozomi. Don't say anything more."
    ks "Shhh, Nozomi. No digas nada más."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2504
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_160989eb:

    # ks smile "You know you can't resist the light. There's no need to try." with dissolve
    ks smile "Sabes que no puedes resistir la luz. No hay necesidad de intentarlo." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2515
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_15fce2d2:

    # "As I finish flashing the light again I reach out and firmly push on her shoulder, causing her to stumble back onto the couch behind her."
    "Después de deslizar nuevamente el haz, muevo mi mano y empujo con firmeza su hombro, haciéndola dar un traspié y caer de espalda sobre el sofá."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2518
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_651ded8e:

    # "She already looks out of it and I've barely said anything to her. Her prior conditioning must be doing most of the work for me."
    "Ya parece estar perdida en sí y apenas le he dicho nada. Su acondicionamiento previo debe estar haciendo la mayor parte del trabajo por mí."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2519
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_ba378914:

    # "Of course it crossed my mind that I could've just used the spoken trigger to put her under, but doing it this way again just feels so right for this occasion."
    "Por supuesto, se me cruzó por la mente que pude simplemente haber usado el ancla verbal para ponerla en trance, pero hacerlo así se siente muy adecuado para esta ocasión."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2521
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_54535b23:

    # ks "That's right, Nozomi. Just keep looking at the light..."
    ks "Eso es, Nozomi. Sigue mirando la luz..."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2523
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_e0f0b949:

    # ks "Looking and relaxing. Looking and drifting..."
    ks "Mírala y empieza a relajarte. Mírala y empieza a flotar..."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2525
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_fe0efe1d:

    # ks "Finding yourself so completely relaxed... Sleep, Nozomi." with dissolve
    ks "Y ahora que estás completamente relajada... Duerme, Nozomi." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2527
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_51254099:

    # "And down she goes." with dissolve
    "Y al abismo cae." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2528
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_5826850c:

    # ks "Very good, Nozomi. Nice and deep for me. Completely relaxed."
    ks "Muy bien, Nozomi. Cae muy profundo para mí. Completamente relajada."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2529
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_0af009de:

    # ks "And now I need you to listen and accept what I have to tell you. Completely accepting my words. Can you do that, Nozomi?"
    ks "Y ahora necesito que escuches y aceptes lo que tengo que decirte. Acepta por completo mis palabras. ¿Puedes hacer eso, Nozomi?"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2530
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_1c7fe4af:

    # ncg "Mhm..."
    ncg "Mjm..."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2532
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_b736c52f:

    # ks "Yes you can. You need to accept the word \"rooftop\" will no longer induce any feelings of arousal in you."
    ks "Claro que puedes. Necesitas aceptar que la palabra \"azotea\" ya no inducirá ninguna sensación de excitación en ti."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2534
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_f0862fe7:

    # ks "Yes you can. You need to accept the word \"rooftop\" will no longer induce any ticklish feelings in you."
    ks "Claro que puedes. Necesitas aceptar que la palabra \"azotea\" ya no inducirá ninguna sesación de cosquillas en ti."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2535
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_be7da026:

    # ks "It is a perfectly normal word and you will not react to it in any special way."
    ks "Es una palabra perfectamente normal y no reaccionarás a ella de ninguna forma especial."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2536
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_577ba04b:

    # "There. That should stop any repeat of what happened this afternoon."
    "Listo. Eso debería evitar que se repita lo ocurrido esta tarde."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2498
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_989f58fd:

    # ks "You must also accept that while we are alone in this house you will find that anything I tell you to do becomes an irresistible command that you must obey."
    ks "También debes aceptar que mientras estemos a solas en esta casa, te darás cuenta de que cualquier cosa que te diga que hagas se convertirá en una orden irresistible que debes obedecer."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2538
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_419fb8da:

    # ks "Do you understand, Nozomi?"
    ks "¿Comprendes, Nozomi?"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2539
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_6258bbcd:

    # ncg sleeptalk "Yes... I understand..." with dissolve
    ncg sleeptalk "Sí... comprendo..." with dissolve

