    n determined uniform "No abandonaré quién soy." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3082
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_16b66325:

    # "Wow, she really has taken everything I said to her in trance so completely to heart."
    "Guau, en verdad se ha tomado todo lo que le dije durante el trance completamente de corazón."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3083
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_8fd95155:

    # "And who am I to argue? This is perfect!"
    "¿Y quién soy yo para discutir? ¡Esto es perfecto!"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3084
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_5ed51c27:

    # ks smile "You won't have to, Nozomi. Let's go back to mine; we'll do some more work on that beautiful mind of yours."
    ks smile "No tendrás que hacerlo, Nozomi. Volvamos a mi casa; trabajaremos un poco en esa bella mentecita tuya."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3086
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_a93ff7c9:

    # "Nozomi giggles at that, and takes my hand as we walk." with dissolve
    "Nozomi se ríe y toma mi mano al caminar." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3112
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_87f0e4ed:

    # "Nozomi and I didn't contact each other overnight, and I'm anxious to see her again."
    "Nozomi y yo no hicimos contacto durante la noche, y siento mucha ansiedad por volverla a ver."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3113
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_8a93caa3:

    # "God, I hope she made it home safe."
    "Dios, espero que haya vuelto a casa a salvo."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3115
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_8817cc62:

    # "As I make it to the gates, I'm relieved to see Nozomi in the distance."
    "Al llegar a las puertas de la entrada, me siento aliviado de ver a Nozomi a la distancia."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3116
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_0f135292:

    # "She's talking to someone..."
    "Está hablando con alguien..."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3186
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_717998d0:

    # h "No fuckin' way!"
    h "¡No me jodas!"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3187
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_90369dcf:

    # n "Yeah..."
    n "Sí..."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3192
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_97bd67ec:

    # n sad_side "It's embarrassing, but I somehow tripped over my own feet and down the stairs I went." with dissolve
    n sad_side "Es muy embarazoso, pero de algún modo me tropecé con mis propios pies y caí por las escaleras." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3193
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_5d666733:

    # h sad_side "Did you hurt anything?" with dissolve
    h sad_side "¿Te lastimaste?" with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3123
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_fcd26e72:

    # n sad_closed "*sigh* Yes, a little bit. I wasn't too badly hurt, but I could've done without having to get my glasses fixed on top of everything else." with dissolve
    n sad_closed "*suspiro* Sí, un poquito. No fue nada grave, pero lo peor de todo es que tuve que mandar a que arreglaran mis anteojos." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3124
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_3690d4a3:

    # n frown_side noblush "I don't have contacts either, so class is going to be SO much fun today." with dissolve
    n frown_side noblush "Tampoco tengo lentes de contacto. Las clases de hoy serán TAN divertidas." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3192
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_c14ed08f:

    # h sleeptalk_concerned uniform_armup "Nozooo..." with dissolve
    h sleeptalk_concerned uniform_armup "Nozooo..." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3199
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_1ee1f7ac:

    # n "What?" with dissolve
    n "¿Qué?" with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3131
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_7fbc71dd:

    # h "C'mere." with dissolve
    h "Véngache pa' acá." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3134
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_9484a655:

    # n "What are you doing?"
    n "¿Qué estás haciendo?"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3135
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_7bb63f3b:

    # h smile_side "What's it look like?" with dissolve
    h smile_side "¿Qué parece que hago?" with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3136
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_06a227dc:

    # n smile_side "It's just... I don't think you've hugged me since we were in junior high." with dissolve
    n smile_side "Es que... creo que no me has abrazado desde la secundaria." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3207
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_84b89da0:

    # h happy_closed "Oh, yeah! This is like when you cut your knee while we were on that field trip." with dissolve
    h happy_closed "¡Ah, sí! Esto es como cuando te cortaste la rodilla durante ese paseo escolar." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3211
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_f475c483:

    # n "Eheh... yeah." with dissolve
    n "Jeje... sí." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3143
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_a72e8687:

    # h uniform_arm happy "Kyahaha, {w=0.2}you used to be {nw}" with dissolve
    h uniform_arm happy "Ajajaja, {w=0.2}¡eras {nw}" with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3145
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_ae069072:

    # extend "SUCH a clutz back then!" with vpunch
    extend "SUPER-torpe en ese entonces!" with vpunch

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3148
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_6495af2f:

    # n front irritated noglasses "Geez, Hiroko. I'm not sure everyone in the school heard you." with dissolve
    n front irritated noglasses "Caray, Hiroko. No estoy segura de que todos en la escuela te hayan logrado escuchar." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3149
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_436b1188:

    # h laugh_side uniform "Ehehe, sorry. Was just thinking how we used to hug it out like this a lot. Then we came to high school and we sorta stopped?" with dissolve
    h laugh_side uniform "Jejeje, perdón. Es que estaba pensando en lo mucho que solíamos resolver las cosas con abrazos. Luego llegamos al perpa' y como que paramos." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3219
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_1f7a7750:

    # n annoyed_left "Yes, because we're not little kids anymore." with dissolve
    n annoyed_left "Sí, porque ya no somos niñas pequeñas." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3151
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_ec542f24:

    # n side smile_side blush "But... thanks." with dissolve
    n side smile_side blush "Pero... gracias." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3153
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_861a760e:

    # "As Nozomi disentangles herself from Hiroko's embrace, she eyes me watching her before quickly averting her gaze." with dissolve
    "Luego de desatarse de los brazos de Hiroko, Nozomi me ve observándola para luego, rápidamente, desviar la mirada." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3224
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_b613283c:

    # n sad_side "Anyway, let's head on in." with dissolve
    n sad_side "Como sea, ya entremos." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3156
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_3626eb80:

    # "As I follow behind them, I send a text to Nozomi asking how she's doing."
    "Camino detrás de ellas y le escribo un texto a Nozomi para preguntarle cómo está."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3157
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_a308bf03:

    # "I know we can't let this fester between us for too long. I hope she realizes that as well."
    "Sé que no podemos dejar que esto entre nosotros siga enconándose por mucho tiempo. Espero que ella también se dé cuenta."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3161
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_f036058b:

    # "But I don't get anything back. Not a text, not even an acknowledging stare all day."
    "Pero no recibo nada en respuesta. Ni un texto, ni una mirada en todo el día."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3162
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_feb1a6b5:

    # "I might as well have not existed to her."
    "Bien podría no existir para ella."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3164
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_3531f203:

    # "As I get back home and drop my schoolbag down by my bed I wonder if I should text her again."
    "Al volver a casa, arrojo mi mochila a la cama, preguntándome si debería enviarle otro mensaje."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3166
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_38e3df42:

    # "Huh... Is that her?"
    "Eh... ¿será ella?"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3170
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_a8c4b004:

    # n "Hey."
    n "Hola."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3171
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_9cc4f64b:

    # ks concerned "Hey..."
    ks concerned "Hola..."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3172
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_845c3c7e:

    # "Nozomi drops her shoes by the door and sighs."
    "Nozomi arroja sus zapatos junto a la puerta y suspira."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3244
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_272da145:

    # "... Then turns and hugs me?" with dissolve
    "... Luego se da la vuelta y ¿me abraza?" with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3250
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_d9bf0375:

    # n "Sorry I didn't respond earlier. I... I kinda got wrapped up in my thoughts today."
    n "Lamento no responder hace rato. Me... me la pasé todo el día envuelta en mis pensamientos."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3179
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_9351457d:

    # "I'm too stunned to respond as she releases me, then walks over to the living room couch and takes a seat."
    "Cuando me suelta, estoy muy pasmado para contestar; luego camina hacia la sala y toma asiento en el sofá."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3253
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_207ce5ff:

    # ncg "I was thinking over and over about what happened. I've barely been able to put it out of my head."
    ncg "Estuve pensando una y otra vez en lo que pasó. Apenas pude sacármelo de la cabeza."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3184
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_f68d8b04:

    # ks "Yeah... How are you holding up, anyway?"
    ks "Sí... ¿y cómo lo llevas, a todo esto?"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3185
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_3783d114:

    # ncg drooping sleeptalk "Oh, you know. Not great." with dissolve
    ncg drooping sleeptalk "Oh, ya sabes. No muy bien." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3186
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_f320bf5d:

    # "She sighs as she turns her head to look towards the television, staring wistfully into the screen."
    "Suspira y voltea la cabeza para mirar la televisión, observando la pantalla con melancolía."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3187
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_fb8ac7a8:

    # ncg standing neutral "I somehow managed to convince my parents that I fell over on the way home yesterday, and my friends think I tripped down the stairs at home." with dissolve
    ncg standing neutral "Más o menos logré convencer a mis padres de que me tropecé camino a casa, y mis amigas creen que me caí por las escaleras de mi casa." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3258
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_79162ec3:

    # ncg stern "So I've lied to the people I care about most just to keep what we have going under wraps, and I feel terrible about that." with dissolve
    ncg stern "Así que, le mentí a la gente que más me importa solo para mantener lo que hemos estado haciendo en secreto, y me siento terrible por eso." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3189
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_2126f012:

    # ks "You've never lied before?"
    ks "¿Nunca habías mentido antes?"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3190
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_7b6b214a:

    # ncg stern_closed "I've lied about eating my little brother's pudding when we were kids. I've never lied about anything big before." with dissolve
    ncg stern_closed "Mentí sobre comerme el pudín de mi hermanito cuando éramos niños. Nunca había mentido sobre algo grande." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3191
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_9bcd07a6:

    # ncg "Like, say, getting injured while visiting some strange guy's house."
    ncg "Como, digamos, lesionarme visitando la casa de un chico desconocido."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3192
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_9c5ed08f:

    # ks sigh "And I'm sorry for that."
    ks sigh "Y lamento eso."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3193
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_6cd4ebd0:

    # ncg sad "I'm just terrified I'm going to be found out soon." with dissolve
    ncg sad "Es que me aterra que me vayan a descubrir pronto." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3194
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_98297a3a:

    # ks frown "You don't really look all that injured to me?"
    ks frown "No luces tan lesionada para mí."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3195
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_35406231:

    # ncg neutral "I don't? It feels like everyone knows I'm limping as I walk, or that I'm wearing a little more makeup than usual." with dissolve
    ncg neutral "¿Eso crees? Siento que todos saben que cojeo al caminar, o que estoy usando un poco más de maquillaje de lo normal." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3196
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_4d4994c4:

    # ncg stern_closed "And god, why did I use different stories for my friends and parents? I TOLD you I'm a terrible liar." with dissolve
    ncg stern_closed "Y, Dios, ¿por qué use historias diferentes para mis amigas y mis padres? Te DIJE que soy una terrible mentirosa." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3198
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_17511018:

    # "Nozomi sighs once more, then turns her gaze back to me." with dissolve
    "Nozomi suspira una vez más, luego vuelve a dirigir su mirada hacia mí." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3199
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_f2f0a01b:

    # ncg "Well, anyway... two things came to mind while I was thinking things over."
    ncg "Pues, en fin... dos cosas vinieron a mi mente mientras pensaba."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3200
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_596938b3:

    # ncg "First, for me to have been acting so convincingly as a zombie without ever letting up?"
    ncg "La primera: ¿que haya actuado tan convincentemente como zombi sin parar?"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3201
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_d13496b0:

    # ncg stern "That says to me that you could do with phrasing your hypnotic suggestions a lot better." with dissolve
    ncg stern "Eso me dice que podrías pensar mucho mejor las palabras que usas para tus sugestiones posthipnóticas." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3217
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_d498eb6f:

    # ks "You will feel your mind rapidly regress, finding it harder and harder to think."
    ks "Sentirás que tu mente retrocede rápidamente, y se vuelve más y más difícil pensar."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3218
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_34160dd9:

    # ks "And you will find your speech has become slurred, unable to form any words except for one: \"Brains\"."
    ks "Y notarás que empiezas a arrastrar las palabras, incapaz de formar ninguna excepto por \"Cerebros\"."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3219
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_b8248a82:

    # ks "Also, you will only be able to move in a shuffling gait, with your arms outstretched."
    ks "Además, solo podrás caminar arrastrando los pies, con los brazos extendidos."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3220
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_ca99112c:

    # ks "As your mind regresses fully you will find {b}your only desire is to feast on human brains.{/b}"
    ks "Mientras tu mente retrocede, notarás que {b}tu único deseo es un festín de sesos humanos{/b}."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3225
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_7d19a0a6:

    # ks sigh "You... you could say that, yeah."
    ks sigh "Po-... podría decirse, sí."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3226
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_9657c502:

    # ncg "I would never have attacked you unless you basically told me to."
    ncg "Nunca te habría atacado a no ser que básicamente me dijeras que lo hiciera."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3227
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_0cd1f207:

    # ncg confused "But... that brings me to the second thing." with dissolve
    ncg confused "Pero... eso me lleva a lo segundo." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3228
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_5a2fb9e6:

    # ks concerned "What's that?"
    ks concerned "¿Y qué eso?"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3229
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_8a9f8870:

    # ncg surprised "It STILL shouldn't have been possible. I should've been able to stop myself." with dissolve
    ncg surprised "AUN SÍ no debió haber sido posible. Debí ser capaz de detenerme." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3230
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_14677d5e:

    # ncg "You've heard of the hidden observer theory, haven't you?"
    ncg "Has escuchado del efecto del observador oculto, ¿no?"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3231
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_985a1cf9:

    # ks frown "Yeah. Isn't that about how even if you're deep under hypnosis you still won't do something you don't want to?"
    ks frown "Sí. ¿Qué no es eso de que, aunque estés profundamente hipnotizado, no harás nada que no quieras?"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3232
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_a3d7eb9b:

    # ncg neutral "Basically. It's supposed to be like a separate consciousness that sits apart while you're hypnotized." with dissolve
    ncg neutral "Básicamente. Se supone que sea como una consciencia que se queda por separado mientras estás hipnotizado." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3233
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_3b4eeb21:

    # ncg "No matter how much a hypnotist dissociates a hypnotized person from reality, that part of them should always hold an objective view of their reality."
    ncg "Sin importar cuánto disocie un hipnotista a una persona de la realidad, esa parte de ella siempre mantiene una vista objetiva de la realidad."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3234
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_ec01dbc7:

    # ncg stern "So if it needs to, it can intervene." with dissolve
    ncg stern "De modo que, si hace falta, puede intervenir." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3235
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_6df174da:

    # ncg "It's why a deeply hypnotized person will still wake up if you left them alone for a while and they had to fulfill a basic need."
    ncg "Es por eso que una persona profundamente hipnotizada despertará si la dejas a solas por un rato y debe satisfacer alguna necesidad básica."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3236
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_712421be:

    # ks smirk "And I guess it's why hypnotists aren't ruling the world with their armies of brainwashed servants."
    ks smirk "Y supongo que es por eso que los hipnotistas no están dominando el mundo lavando cerebros y creando ejércitos de sirvientes."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3237
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_dd5a0644:

    # ncg stern_closed "Uh, sure." with dissolve
    ncg stern_closed "Eh, claro." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3238
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_669739a0:

    # ncg neutral "But that's exactly what I mean, Kyou. There was no \"hidden observer\" to tell me I didn't seriously want to eat your brains or whatever." with dissolve
    ncg neutral "Pero eso es exactamente a lo que me refiero, Kyou. No hubo ningún \"observador\" oculto que me dijera que en verdad no quería comerme tu cerebro, no sé qué." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3239
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_dfa567b1:

    # ncg stern "Why couldn't I stop myself? Why didn't I acknowledge the reality of the situation?" with dissolve
    ncg stern "¿Por qué no pude detenerme? ¿Por qué no me di cuenta de la realidad de la situación?" with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3240
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_986c74ff:

    # ncg "And when I think about that, I can't help but wonder about the one thing I know so little about."
    ncg "Y cuando pienso en ello, no puedo evitar sentir intriga por la única cosa de la que sé poco."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3378
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_ae9727a4:

    # "She frowns as she pulls out a penlight that was hidden inside the sleeve of her blazer."
    "Frunciendo el ceño, saca una pluma que estaba oculta bajo la manga de su chaqueta."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3245
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_71846403:

    # "Wait."
    "Aguarda."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3246
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_d0888146:

    # ks surprised "How the fuck did you get that?!"
    ks surprised "¡¿Cómo carajo conseguiste eso?!"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3247
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_cb3f650e:

    # ncg stern_closed "Kyou, you keep this in your right pants pocket. I've seen you with it a couple of times now; it wasn't hard." with dissolve
    ncg stern_closed "Kyou, guardas esto en el bolsillo derecho de tu pantalón. Ya te vi con ella un par de veces; no fue difícil." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3248
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_1b6715ee:

    # ncg "If I'm going to be a liar today, I may as well be a thief, too."
    ncg "Si hoy seré una mentirosa, pues ya que estamos, también seré una ladrona."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3250
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_e511e431:

    # "I groan as the realization of how she got hold of it hits me, then I feel anxiety well inside me as that realization is immediately followed up with ANOTHER realization."
    "Gruño al darme cuenta de cómo llegó a sus manos, luego siento ansiedad muy dentro de mí al darme cuenta de OTRA cosa."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3254
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_3f19dc7e:

    # ks frown "Nozomi... don't do anything rash, okay?"
    ks frown "Nozomi... no hagas nada imprudente, ¿de acuerdo?"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3255
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_4cf0e595:

    # ncg annoyed "Kyou, what do you take me for? I've just been explaining that I think this thing is dangerous." with dissolve
    ncg annoyed "Kyou, ¿por quién me tomas? Solo estaba explicando que creo que esta cosa es peligrosa." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3256
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_f30e95f3:

    # ncg "No one should be doing anything with this until we know exactly what it does."
    ncg "Nadie debería hacer nada con ella hasta que sepamos exactamente lo que hace."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3257
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_6f434b73:

    # ks "Really? All it does is help keep your focus on the pattern it emits so you'll fall into trance easier. That's all I designed it for."
    ks "¿En serio? Lo único que hace es ayudarte a concentrarte en el patrón que emite para caer más fácilmente en trance. Eso es todo para lo que la diseñé."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3258
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_c365b89a:

    # ks "I wasn't even sure it'd do that until I used it on you."
    ks "Ni siquiera estaba seguro de que fuera a hacer eso hasta que la usé en ti."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3259
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_9e4dbf34:

    # ncg stern "Right, so I'm literally your only data point. How do you know it doesn't do more than that?" with dissolve
    ncg stern "Cierto, entonces literalmente soy tu única fuente de datos. ¿Cómo sabes que no hace nada más?" with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3260
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_7da3d712:

    # ncg "What if it actually managed to inhibit my hidden observer somehow? Because why else would this be happening to me?"
    ncg "¿Qué tal si de alguna forma lograste inhibir a mi observador oculto? ¿Por qué otra razón me estaría pasando esto?"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3261
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_7abb0670:

    # ks neutral "I... I don't know."
    ks neutral "No... no lo sé."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3262
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_2a478cd4:

    # ncg angry "Not to mention your reaction just now. If you really thought it was so harmless, why does it matter so much what I do with it, huh?" with dissolve
    ncg angry "Sin mencionar la manera en la que acabas de reaccionar. Si de verdad creías que era tan inofensiva, ¿por qué importaba tanto lo que hiciera con ella, eh?" with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3263
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_11ecd9a7:

    # "I sort of reacted out of instinct there, but I guess she has a point."
    "Supongo que reaccioné por instinto, pero tiene un punto."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3264
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_b92a0f8d:

    # ks "Okay, well... maybe you're right. I don't know how being hypnotized with the penlight stacks up with any other method."
    ks "Muy bien, pues... tal vez tengas razón. No sé cómo es que ser hipnotizado con la linterna se compara a ningún otro método."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3265
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_22084f08:

    # ks "What about you, though? What was it like when Satoshi hypnotized you?"
    ks "Pero ¿qué hay de ti? ¿Cómo fue cuando Satoshi te hipnotizó?"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3266
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_687ae2e3:

    # ncg neutral "It was different... I think." with dissolve
    ncg neutral "Fue diferente... creo." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3267
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_1c079628:

    # ncg "I don't remember clearly now, but I'm pretty sure I could've stopped going along with his suggestions if I really wanted to?"
    ncg "No lo recuerdo con claridad, pero estoy bastante segura de que podría haber dejado de seguir sus sugestiones si realmente hubiera querido."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3268
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_3bbca04b:

    # "She shrugs."
    "Se encoge de hombros."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3269
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_598063f1:

    # ncg stern "Anyway, I think it's obvious what we should do next." with dissolve
    ncg stern "Como sea, creo que es obvio lo que tenemos que hacer ahora." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3270
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_9da9eb68:

    # "I end up nodding my head as I sigh. I don't really want to do this with the work I put into it, but..."
    "Termino asintiendo con mi cabeza suspirando. Realmente no quiero hacer esto después de todo el trabajo que invertí, pero..."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3271
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_042abbcf:

    # ks concerned "We try without the penlight."
    ks concerned "Intentarlo sin la linterna."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3274
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_8a419a9f:

    # ncg stern_closed "Honestly if I had any sense I'd stop letting you hypnotize me altogether, but... yes, that's what I was thinking." with dissolve
    ncg stern_closed "Honestamente, si tuviera sentido común, directamente no te dejaría volver a hipnotizarme, pero... sí, en eso estaba pensando." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3275
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_b5fdad3b:

    # ncg neutral "I know this thing means something to you, but if it's doing what we think it's doing then we really shouldn't use it." with dissolve
    ncg neutral "Sé que esta cosa significa algo para ti, pero si está haciendo lo que creemos que está haciendo, entonces realmente no deberíamos usarla." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3276
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_00af7257:

    # ks "Yeah..."
    ks "Sí..."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3279
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_e7b70034:

    # "Nozomi smiles as she hands me the penlight back, which I make a point of returning to my pocket." with dissolve
    "Nozomi sonríe devolviéndome la linterna, la cual de inmediato pongo de regreso en mi bolsillo." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3280
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_51f7eae6:

    # ks smile "So... alright then. What should we do this time?"
    ks smile "Pues... bien, entonces. ¿Qué deberíamos hacer esta vez?"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3281
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_7a1ebe02:

    # ncg "Well..."
    ncg "Pues..."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3282
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_d7569c08:

    # ncg sad "Obviously when I was spending all day thinking about what happened I couldn't help but think a lot about this, too." with dissolve
    ncg sad "Obviamente, al pasar todo el día pensando en lo que pasó, no pude evitar pensar mucho en esto también." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3283
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_b7c7878f:

    # ncg "And I don't know if this is coming from any lingering effects from the penlight or I'm just looking to excuse my own thoughts, but..."
    ncg "Y no sé si esto se deba a algún efecto de largo plazo de la linterna, o solo intento excusar mis propios pensamientos, pero..."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3284
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_999e5510:

    # ncg stern "Uhh..." with dissolve
    ncg stern "Eeeh..." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3285
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_5ab637cd:

    # "... What on earth is she thinking to get her embarrassed like this?"
    "... ¿En qué rayos está pensando que la pueda estar avergonzando así?"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3286
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_c3b765b1:

    # ncg stern_closed "I'll just say it." with dissolve
    ncg stern_closed "Voy a decirlo y ya." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3287
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_4bb97b06:

    # ncg confused "I was thinking you could hypnotize me into obeying your commands?" with dissolve
    ncg confused "Estaba pensando que ¿podrías hipnotizarme para obedecer tus órdenes?" with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3288
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_ec0879c7:

    # ks "Okay, like..."
    ks "Muy bien, como..."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3289
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_deee4efa:

    # ks surprised "Wait, what?"
    ks surprised "Espera, ¿qué?"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3290
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_483edeac:

    # ncg "I-I mean, only inside this house. A-and, only for lighter stuff."
    ncg "Qu-quiero decir, solo en esta casa. Y... y solo cosas sencillas."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3291
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_dbd74c6b:

    # ks "Lighter stuff?"
    ks "¿Cosas sencillas?"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3292
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_5ce4528a:

    # ncg "You know..."
    ncg "Ya sabes..."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3293
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_a20cefa7_1:

    # "..."
    "..."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3294
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_323accaf:

    # ncg angry "I-I mean, don't try and make me have sex with you or anything!" with vpunch
    ncg angry "¡Qu-quiero decir, no intentes hacerme tener sexo contigo ni nada!" with vpunch

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3295
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_b8002c16:

    # ks surprised "... Right. No sex, got it."
    ks surprised "... Correcto. Nada de sexo. Entendido."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3296
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_7a5e327e:

    # ncg sad "I-I'm sorry. I've made this too weird. Maybe we should just forget all of this and... just go back to doing normal things." with dissolve
    ncg sad "L-lo siento. Hice que se pusiera muy raro. Tal vez deberíamos olvidar todo esto y... regresar a hacer las cosas con normalidad." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3297
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_7ba3a79e:

    # "No. Oh no, I'm not going back to \"normal\" with you, Nozomi. Never again!"
    "No. Oh, no. No pienso volver a la \"normalidad\" contigo, Nozomi. ¡Nunca jamás!"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3298
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_cb40962c:

    # ks neutral "Nozomi, wait. It's fine, I think get it."
    ks neutral "Nozomi, espera. Está bien, creo que entiendo."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3299
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_81f43e7f:

    # ks "I mean... you want to feel like you're helpless and endangered. But you also want to know you're safe."
    ks "Es decir... quieres sentirte impotente y en peligro. Pero también quieres saber que es seguro."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3300
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_0320746c:

    # ks "Maybe that's weird, but I want to do that for you."
    ks "Tal vez sea raro, pero quiero hacer eso por ti."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3301
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_86c2dea2:

    # ks "And I CAN do that for you, Nozomi. If you'll let me?"
    ks "Y PUEDO hacerlo por ti, Nozomi. ¿Si me lo permites?"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3302
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_dfa4423c:

    # ncg "I want... I want to let you, Kyou. There's one other thing, though."
    ncg "Quiero... quiero permitírtelo, Kyou. Pero una cosa más."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3303
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_83cebaad:

    # ks neutral "Okay. What's that?"
    ks neutral "Muy bien. ¿Y qué es?"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3304
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_075f6209:

    # ncg confused "It's good that we're not using the penlight but could we also just not do eye-fixation today?" with dissolve
    ncg confused "Es bueno que no usemos la linterna, pero ¿también podríamos no hacer nada de fijación ocular hoy?" with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3305
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_089dea26:

    # ncg "I don't really want to look at things any more than I have to until I get my glasses back."
    ncg "No quiero mirar cosas más de lo necesario hasta tener mis lentes de vuelta."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3306
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_0ed0fea8:

    # ks "Right... I guess that's kinda my speciality, but I'll see what I can do."
    ks "Claro... Supongo que esa es algo así como mi especialidad, pero veré que puedo hacer."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3308
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_92b05d5c:

    # "She nods and leans back on the couch, but I could see her tension from a mile away." with dissolve
    "Asiente y se recarga contra el sofá, pero podría ver su tensión a un kilómetro de distancia." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3309
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_9a895576:

    # "So no penlight and a stressed-out subject. But I think I can give her what she wants."
    "Pues, sin linterna y con un sujeto estresado. Pero creo que puedo darle lo que quiere."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3310
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_bc116549:

    # "Just need to diffuse the tension a little, that's all."
    "Solo necesito disipar esa tensión un poco, eso es todo."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3311
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_97b17c32:

    # ks "So... okay, I'm gonna be touching your arms at some points during this, just so you know."
    ks "Pues... muy bien, tocaré tus brazos un par de veces durante el proceso, solo para que sepas."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3312
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_d619ae6f:

    # "Nozomi nods again as she places her hands down in her lap."
    "Nozomi asiente de nuevo y coloca sus manos de vuelta sobre su regazo."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3313
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_e787f6c5:

    # ncg "Right."
    ncg "Claro."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3314
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_30add45c:

    # ks "And... I can see you're feeling tense, Nozomi, but remember anything that is about to happen, you can resist. You can always stop if you need to."
    ks "Y... puedo ver que te sientes tensa, Nozomi, pero recuerda: todo lo que está por pasar, puedes resistirlo. Siempre puedes parar si lo necesitas."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3315
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_6d85657a:

    # "I give her a little smile as I add:"
    "Le doy una pequeña sonrisa y añado:"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3316
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_96087ce9:

    # ks smile "But we both know you don't really want to do that."
    ks smile "Pero ambos sabemos que no quieres hacerlo."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3318
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_5c8ea4af:

    # "Nozomi returns my smile with a nervous one of her own, but says nothing. I think that loosened her up a little." with dissolve
    "Nozomi responde a mi sonrisa con una nerviosa de su parte, pero no dice nada. Creo que eso la aflojó un poco." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3319
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_7a01e26e:

    # ks "So in a moment, I want you to take a nice deep breath. I want you to hold it while I count to three, and on three I want you to let it all out."
    ks "Pues bien, en un momento, quiero que inhales lenta y profundamente. Quiero que lo sostengas mientras cuento hasta tres, y a las tres quiero que lo dejes salir."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3320
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_f71cae73:

    # ks "And as you let it out, close your eyes and feel all the tension in your body draining away. Understand?"
    ks "Y al dejarlo salir, cierra tus ojos tus ojos y siente cómo toda la tensión abandona tu cuerpo. ¿Comprendes?"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3321
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_0924b3b7:

    # ncg "Mhm."
    ncg "Mjm."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3323
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_5c3a796d:

    # ks "Good. Now, deep breath."
    ks "Bien. Ahora, inhala profundo."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3324
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_eb0febf9:

    # ncg neutral "..." with dissolve
    ncg neutral "..." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3325
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_265327c7_2:

    # ks "One, two, three."
    ks "Uno, dos, tres."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3326
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_16aab6f7:

    # ncg stern_closed "..." with dissolve
    ncg stern_closed "..." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3327
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_8d9e61c9:

    # ks "That's good, Nozomi. Now again, eyes open, deep breath."
    ks "Eso es, Nozomi. Una vez más, ojos abiertos e inhala profundo."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3328
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_eb0febf9_1:

    # ncg neutral "..." with dissolve
    ncg neutral "..." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3329
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_2a6a8f5c:

    # ks "One, two... three."
    ks "Uno, dos... tres."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3330
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_16aab6f7_1:

    # ncg stern_closed "..." with dissolve
    ncg stern_closed "..." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3331
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_6582ea6a:

    # ks "That's perfect. Relaxing so much. Feeling every muscle in your body grow loose and limp."
    ks "Perfecto. Ya te estás relajando bastante. Siente cómo cada músculo de tu cuerpo se pone flojito."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3332
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_4758eb3d:

    # ks "But none more so than all the little muscles around your eyes."
    ks "Pero ninguno tanto como todos los pequeños músculos que hay alrededor de tus ojos."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3334
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_04de5918:

    # ks "Take another deep breath, Nozomi, but this time pay special attention to those muscles in and around your eyelids."
    ks "Respira profundamente de nuevo, Nozomi; pero, esta vez, presta especial atención a esos músculos que rodean tus ojos."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3335
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_2da03d44:

    # ks "Relaxing them so completely in one, two, three."
    ks "Relajándolos completamente a la cuenta de uno, dos, tres."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3336
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_6c0368aa:

    # ks "Your eyelids are so completely relaxed now that you will find that they have become impossible for you to open."
    ks "Tus párpados ya están tan relajados que puedes darte cuenta de que te es imposible abrirlos."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3337
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_2f000700:

    # ks "And I want to prove that to you, Nozomi. Try now and see if you can open those heavy, relaxed eyelids of yours."
    ks "Y quiero demostrártelo, Nozomi. Intenta ahora y ve si puede abrir esos pesados y relajados ojitos tuyos."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3338
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_5e420be2:

    # "Watching her intently, I wait a few moments as Nozomi's eyelids remain calmly closed."
    "Observándola atentamente, espero unos momentos y los párpados de Nozomi se mantienen cerrados."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3339
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_f30fc81b:

    # "When I think I see them flicker slightly, I continue."
    "Cuando creo verlos temblar un poco, continúo."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3340
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_d0b3aade:

    # ks "Very good, Nozomi. Now stop trying, and let that completely relaxed feeling you have around your eyelids spread over your face and down your neck."
    ks "Muy bien, Nozomi. Deja de intentar ahora, y permite que esa sensación de completa relajación que rodea tus ojos se esparza por tu rostro, y por tu cuello."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3341
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_eab7ed97:

    # ks "Feeling it spread further down your body, down your chest and arms... down your waist... spreading further down your legs and to the tips of your toes."
    ks "Permítele esparcirse por todo tu cuerpo, por tu torso y tus brazos... por tu cintura... dispersándose más y más por tus piernas y por los dedos de tus pies."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3342
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_26551967:

    # "I wait another moment for her to cement the feeling of relaxation in her head before speaking again."
    "Espero otro momento a que cimente el sentimiento de relajación en su cabeza antes de hablar."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3343
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_930f58b2:

    # ks "That's good, Nozomi. Now again I'm going to count to three, but this time on three, I want you to open your eyes again."
    ks "Muy bien, Nozomi. Y nuevamente, contaré hasta tres; pero, esta vez, a las tres quiero que vuelvas a abrir los ojos."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3344
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_e601550b:

    # ks "It'll be okay to do this, as you will soon be closing them again."
    ks "Estará bien que lo hagas, pues pronto podrás volver a cerrarlos."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3345
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_3b3b24e2:

    # ks "And when you do, you will feel yourself dropping ten times as deep, feeling ten times more relaxed than you are now."
    ks "Y cuando lo hagas, sentirás que caes diez veces más profundo, y te sentirás diez veces más relajada que ahora."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3346
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_98d70886:

    # ks "So, opening your eyes on three, closing them again on my say and relaxing ten times as deeply."
    ks "Así que, abre los ojos a las tres, para después volverlos a cerrar a mi señal, relajándote diez veces más profundamente."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3347
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_c389272a:

    # "As I say this, I raise my hand and hold the palm out in front of her face, a little above her eye level."
    "Tras decirlo, elevo mi mano y sostengo mi palma frente a su rostro, ligeramente por encima de la altura de sus ojos."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3348
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_265327c7_3:

    # ks "One, two, three."
    ks "Uno, dos, tres."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3350
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_1a114297:

    # "Nozomi's eyelids flutter open and her eyes immediately register the hand above her as I immediately swoop it down over her face." with dissolve
    "Los ojos de Nozomi se abren e inmediatamente vislumbran la mano que se encuentra sobre ellos, la cual hago inmediatamente caer en picada delante de ella." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3351
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_73c5669e:

    # ks "And eyes closed, Nozomi."
    ks "Y ojos cerrados, Nozomi."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3354
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_af6b934c:

    # ks "Ten times deeper. Ten times more relaxed. Very good."
    ks "Diez veces más profundo. Diez veces más relajada. Muy bien."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3355
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_134ddbcc:

    # "Smiling at her responsiveness, I raise my hand over her face once more as I repeat the trick."
    "Sonriendo ante lo responsiva que es, levanto mi mano por encima de su rostro de nuevo para repetir el truco."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3356
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_3d71d3e2:

    # ks "And again, opening your eyes on one, two... three."
    ks "Y una vez más, abre los ojos a la cuenta de uno, dos... tres."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3358
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_311d06e4:

    # "Once again, the moment her eyes open I immediately bring my hand down over her face." with dissolve
    "Nuevamente, en cuanto sus ojos se abren, bajo mi mano de inmediato frente a su rostro." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3359
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_7202ae71:

    # "Her eyelids start to flicker closed again before I even speak."
    "Antes de decir nada, sus ojos ya empiezan a cerrarse."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3361
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_c099e7d2:

    # ks "And closed. Falling ten times deeper. Ten times more relaxed." with dissolve
    ks "Y cerrados. Cayendo diez veces más profundo. Diez veces más relajada." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3362
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_e4657fc0:

    # ks "But even as deeply relaxed as you are, you are going to find you can relax even deeper."
    ks "Pero, por más profundamente relajada que estés, siempre podrás relajarte más."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3363
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_b7178ac4:

    # "At this moment I reach out and take her right arm gently by the wrist."
    "Y ahora, tomo su brazo derecho por la muñeca con gentileza."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3364
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_227e7e88:

    # "Raising it slightly upwards over her lap, I notice how her fingers drag limply across her skirt as I do so."
    "Mientras alzo levemente sobre su regazo, noto cómo sus dedos se arrastran por su falda."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3365
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_140ba342:

    # ks "You can feel how limp and heavy your arm is, can't you, Nozomi?"
    ks "Puedes sentir lo flojitos y pesados que están tus brazos, ¿no es así, Nozomi?"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3366
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_dad639a6:

    # ks "It's alright, you don't need to say or do anything. It's fine to let me do all the work for you."
    ks "Está bien, no tienes que decir nada. Está bien dejarme hacer todo el trabajo por ti."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3367
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_d473253d:

    # ks "And as I drop your arm back into your lap you find yourself relaxing ten times deeper yet again. In one, two..."
    ks "Y cuando deje tu brazo caer sobre tu regazo, una vez más podrás relajarte diez veces más profundo. En uno, dos..."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3368
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_f6fd8eaa:

    # "Pausing a moment, I then gently let go of her wrist as her arm drops quietly back on her lap."
    "Haciendo una pause, suelto gentilmente su muñeca y su brazo aterriza silenciosamente en su regazo."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3369
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_df710258:

    # ks "Three. Ten times deeper, Nozomi. You are doing so well at this. Finding it so good and natural to relax and drop so deeply as you are."
    ks "Tres. Diez veces más profundo, Nozomi. Lo estás haciendo muy bien. Se siente muy bien y muy natural relajarte y caer tan profundamente."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3370
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_c23235fa:

    # ks "And I'm going to lift your arm again, while you're going to let me do all the work once more."
    ks "Y ahora levantaré tu brazo de nuevo, y una vez más, permíteme hacer todo el trabajo."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3324
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_3f9ac2db:

    # "Once again, I lift her arm gently by the wrist, feeling no resistance whatsoever."
    "Nuevamente, alzo gentilmente su brazo, sosteniéndolo de la muñeca y sin sentir nada de resistencia."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3372
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_73a94f31:

    # ks "Just allowing yourself to feel how loose and limp you are. So deeply relaxed. One, two and..."
    ks "Tan solo siente lo flojita que estás. Profundamente relajada. Uno, dos y..."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3373
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_201ba23e:

    # "And again, I let her arm drop."
    "Y de nuevo, dejo su brazo caer."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3374
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_3f1f2a16:

    # ks "Three, ten times deeper still. Your body now so fully relaxed."
    ks "Tres, otras diez veces más profundo. Tu cuerpo se encuentra totalmente relajado."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3375
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_e4e2e7c5:

    # ks "But your mind can relax even deeper, and we're going to take care of that now, Nozomi."
    ks "Pero tu mente se puede relajar todavía más, y nos encargaremos de eso, Nozomi."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3376
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_338697fd:

    # ks "When I tell you to, I want you to count down from one hundred."
    ks "Cuando te indique, quiero que cuentes hacia atrás desde el cien."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3377
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_790aed70:

    # ks "You will count down, speaking each number aloud as you go, followed by the words \"and deeper still\"."
    ks "Contarás, diciendo cada número en voz alta, seguido de las palabras \"y más profundo\"."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3378
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_f62d6b1b:

    # ks "I will be talking as you do this, but that's okay. you won't need to pay any conscious attention to what I say, just focus on counting down and relaxing your mind."
    ks "Estarás hablando al hacerlo, pero está bien. No hace falta que prestes atención conscientemente a lo que digo, solo concéntrate en contar y en relajar tu mente."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3379
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_eb4fee9c:

    # ks "Relaxing your mind so much that each number becomes harder and harder to recall. And when you find the next number is too hard to remember, it's alright."
    ks "Relajando tanto tu mente que cada número se vuelve más y más difícil de recordar. Y cuando el siguiente número te sea demasiado difícil de recordar, no te preocupes."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3380
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_a73b1dbd:

    # ks "You can just stop and let all the numbers in your head disappear. Now start counting for me, Nozomi."
    ks "Puedes simplemente para y dejar que todos los números en tu cabeza desaparezcan. Ahora cuenta para mí, Nozomi."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3382
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_63b6c406:

    # "And just like that I see Nozomi's lips quiver as she begins to speak softly to the air." with dissolve
    "Y así, veo los labios de Nozomi estremecerse en cuanto a empieza a hablar suavemente." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3383
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_45f86bef:

    # ncg "One-hundred... and deeper still."
    ncg "Cien... y más profundo."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3384
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_de519c96:

    # ks "That's perfect, Nozomi."
    ks "Perfecto, Nozomi."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3385
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_f1a12a84:

    # ncg "Ninety-nine, and deeper still."
    ncg "Noventa y nueve, y más profundo."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3386
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_f8d2e39b:

    # ks "Your mind relaxing more deeply with every number you count."
    ks "Tu mente se relaja más profundamente con cada número."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3387
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_e59fb2eb:

    # ncg "Ninety-eight, and deeper still."
    ncg "Noventa y ocho, y más profundo."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3388
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_77043a17:

    # ks "Finding each number so much harder to recall than the next."
    ks "Y cada número es más y más difícil de recordar que el anterior."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3389
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_63fbbca8:

    # ncg "Ninety-seven, and deeper still."
    ncg "Noventa y siete, y más profundo."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3390
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_33177cff:

    # ks "As if the image of every number in your head were fading."
    ks "Como si la imagen de cada número se estuviera desvaneciendo en tu cabeza."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3391
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_87fa75d9:

    # ncg "Ninety-six, and deeper still."
    ncg "Noventa y seis, y más profundo."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3392
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_34f69b8f:

    # ks "And if the numbers are really so hard to recall..."
    ks "Y si los números son tan difíciles de recordar..."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3393
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_8caa9f24:

    # ncg "Ninety-five, and deeper still."
    ncg "Noventa y nueve, y más profundo."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3394
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_3e081921:

    # ks "Perhaps it would be best..."
    ks "Quizá sería mejor..."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3395
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_c0af73ec:

    # ncg "Ninety-four, and deeper still."
    ncg "Noventa y cuatro, y más profundo."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3396
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_7ebd1d8c:

    # ks "To avoid spending all that effort to recall them..."
    ks "No gastar tanto esfuerzo recordándolos..."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3397
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_18aaa293:

    # ncg "Ninety... ninety-three, and deeper still."
    ncg "Noventa... noventa y tres, y más profundo."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3398
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_01a5c712:

    # ks "And just let them spill out of your mind."
    ks "Y simplemente dejar que se vayan de tu mente."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3399
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_bf65ca03:

    # ncg "Ninety... two, and deeper still."
    ncg "Noventa y... dos, y  más profundo."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3400
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_8b0704d2:

    # ks "Finding it so easy to just..."
    ks "Es muy fácil simplemente..."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3401
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_0207834e:

    # ncg "Nine... Ninety-one... and deeper still"
    ncg "Noven-... noventa y uno... y más profundo."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3402
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_765f2738:

    # ks "Let them all..."
    ks "Dejar que todos..."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3403
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_d1d5e514:

    # ncg "Ninety..."
    ncg "Noventa..."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3404
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_32bb32d3:

    # ks "Disappear."
    ks "Desaparezcan."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3405
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_e4adda6a:

    # ncg "Nine..."
    ncg "Noven-..."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3406
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_91dc085e_2:

    # ncg "..."
    ncg "..."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3408
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_58cde192:

    # "I give her a moment, watching her lip quiver and then fall still as she apparently admits defeat." with dissolve
    "Le doy un momento, y observo sus labios temblar y luego quedarse inmóviles, aparentemente admitiendo su derrota." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3409
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_b7fbefeb:

    # ks "That's perfect, Nozomi. Letting those numbers fall out of your head. Letting your mind relax so deeply and so completely, just as deeply as your body."
    ks "Perfecto, Nozomi. Deja que esos números salgan de tu cabeza. Deja que tu mente se relaje profunda y completa mente, tal como tu cuerpo."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3410
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_84d135e8:

    # "Another moment passes as I look over her dormant form."
    "Pasa otro momento y observo su durmiente silueta."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3411
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_ec5cc298:

    # "I'm anxious about hypnotizing without the penlight for the first time, but it seems to be going well?"
    "Me causa algo de ansiedad hipnotizar sin la linterna por primera vez, pero parece estar yendo bien."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3412
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_9c619a2a:

    # "I shouldn't be so nervous about this. I might be trying something a little different here, but I know she wants this."
    "No debería estar nervioso. Puede que esté intentando algo un poco diferente, pero sé que esto es lo que quiere."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3413
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_4aab87e7:

    # "I'll just pass her the suggestion she asked for and see how it goes."
    "Simplemente le pasaré la sugestión que pidió y veré qué tal va."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3414
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_88d85e81:

    # ks "And now that you are so relaxed, you may notice how wonderful it feels to be like this, and that I was the one who brought you to this deep, wonderful, relaxed state."
    ks "Y ahora que estás tan relajada, puede que notes lo maravilloso se siente estar así, y que fui yo quien te trajo a este profundo, maravilloso y relajante estado."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3415
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_12025643:

    # ks "So if I can make you feel so wonderful, by having you relax so deeply for me, then perhaps you would feel just as wonderful by doing other things for me as well."
    ks "Entonces, si puedo hacerte sentir de maravilla al hacerte relajarte tan profundamente para mí, quizás también se sienta igual de maravilloso hacer otras cosas para mí."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3416
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_dbeceb7e:

    # ks "In fact, whenever we are in this house and we are alone, I could tell you to do anything and you might find yourself effortlessly and thoughtlessly obeying."
    ks "De hecho, siempre que estemos a solas en esta casa, podría decirte que hagas cualquier cosa, y tú obedecerías sin esfuerzo y sin pensarlo."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3417
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_c6035628:

    # ks "You could try to resist my commands, but doing so would be so much more effort than it would take to obey."
    ks "Podrías intentar resistir mis órdenes, pero hacerlo tomaría mucho más esfuerzo del que tomaría obedecer."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3418
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_62e63385:

    # ks "It would be so much more relaxing to simply obey my commands."
    ks "Sería mucho más relajante simplemente obedecer mis órdenes."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3419
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_1ffe8b3f:

    # ks "And so long as what I'm asking isn't lewd, you shouldn't have to think at all."
    ks "Y siempre y cuando lo que pida no sea obsceno, ni siquiera tienes que pensarlo."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3420
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_638a93f3:

    # ks "All you'll have to do is obey and feel as wonderful as you do now, knowing that you obeyed."
    ks "Únicamente tendrás que obedecer y sentirte de maravilla al hacerlo, y al saber que obedeciste."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3421
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_c9e647d8:

    # ks "Allow what I have said to sink deep into your mind, making it a part of who you are, and once you have done so, you can tell me you understand."
    ks "Permite que lo que acabo de decir se hunda a lo más profundo de tu mente, haciéndolo parte de quién eres, y una vez lo hayas hecho, puedes decirme que entiendes."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3422
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_a20cefa7_2:

    # "..."
    "..."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3423
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_92736ffa_3:

    # ncg sleeptalk "I understand..." with dissolve
    ncg sleeptalk "Entiendo..." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3433
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_92736ffa_2:

    # ncg sleeptalk "I understand..." with dissolve
    ncg sleeptalk "Entiendo..." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3425
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_5ceabce4:

    # ks "I knew you would, Nozomi. Still feeling wonderful and relaxed as you accept this part of yourself." with dissolve
    ks "Sabía que entenderías, Nozomi. Y aún te sientes maravillosamente relajada al aceptar esta parte de ti." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3426
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_f7e4110d:

    # ks "Now in a few moments you're going to come out of this deep relaxation and back to waking."
    ks "Ahora, en unos momentos, saldrás de esta profunda relajación y volverás a despertar."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3427
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_9016e4cb:

    # ks "I'm going to count to five, and with each number you're going to feel a little more awake, a little more alert, until on five you will awaken completely."
    ks "Contaré hasta cinco, y con cada número, te sentirás un poco más despierta, un poco más alerta; hasta que, a la cuenta de cinco, despiertes completamente."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3428
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_85a78710:

    # ks "And when you awaken, you will feel so good and refreshed, and ready to obey my commands."
    ks "Y cuando despiertes, te sentirás muy bien, muy fresca y lista para obedecer mis órdenes."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3429
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_caef2303:

    # ks "One, just starting to stir."
    ks "Uno, comienzas poco a poco a moverte."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3431
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_aa3a4f80:

    # ks "Two, beginning to feel the strength return to your legs."
    ks "Dos, empiezas a sentir cómo la fuerza regresa a tus piernas."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3432
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_0a6875d3:

    # ks "Three, feeling that energy flow up your chest and your arms, as your breathing returns to normal."
    ks "Tres, siente esa energía fluir por tu torso y tus brazos, mientras que tu respiración vuelve a la normalidad."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3433
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_3c54e183:

    # ks "Four, your senses returning to your head, letting your eyelids flicker and feeling so good about waking, and..."
    ks "Cuatro, tus sentidos vuelven a tu cabeza, dejando que tus párpados se muevan, y..."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3435
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_2d6db352:

    # ks "Five. Feeling so good as you wake." with dissolve
    ks "Cinco. Sintiéndote muy bien al despertar." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3437
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_bd4b69a1:

    # "Nozomi breathes deeply through her nose as her eyes open fully, looking disoriented for a moment before her pupils focus on me." with dissolve
    "Nozomi respira profundamente por la nariz, abirendo sus ojos por completo, luciendo desorientada, y entonces sus pupilas se enfocan en mí." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3438
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_7d333e21:

    # "I give her a smile."
    "Le doy una sonrisa."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3439
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_3c5da2ea:

    # ks "Tell me what you're feeling right now."
    ks "Dime, cómo te sientes ahora."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3442
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_2f212c2a:

    # "She smiles back and blinks sleepily before answering." with dissolve
    "Me devuelve la sonrisa y pestañea soñolienta antes de contestar." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3443
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_c39435d0:

    # ncg "I feel... really good. Tingly."
    ncg "Me siento... muy bien. Y siento un hormigueo."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3444
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_890cdafe:

    # ks "And how does it compare with the other times you've been under for me?"
    ks "¿Y cómo se compara a las otras ocasiones en las que estuviste en trance?"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3445
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_dfacedb7:

    # ncg stern "Hmm..." with dissolve
    ncg stern "Mmm..." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3446
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_07d7d903:

    # ncg "It's... different? Less euphoric, I guess. But I still feel really nice."
    ncg "Es... ¿diferente? Menos eufórico, supongo. Pero, aun así, se siente muy bien."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3447
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_7a87772f:

    # "I nod. So maybe the penlight really does affect her differently in some ways. I guess it's too early to tell."
    "Asiento con la cabeza. Tal vez la linterna sí la afecte distinto de alguna manera. Supongo que es muy pronto para saber."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3448
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_41995bd8:

    # "For now though, I want to see how she's responding to the hypnotic session we just had."
    "Pero, por ahora, quiero ver qué tan bien responde a la sesión hipnótica que acabamos de tener."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3449
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_f73e9617:

    # ks "Interesting. Tap your nose."
    ks "Interesante. Toca tu nariz."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3451
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_56ead426:

    # "She perks an eyebrow at the odd request, but her right arm is already moving to bring her hand to her face as her index fingertip taps the tip of her nose." with dissolve
    "Levanta una ceja ante tan extraña petición, pero su brazo derecho ya se está moviendo para traer su mano a su rostro, y luego su dedo índice toca la punta de su nariz." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3452
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_4cac569e:

    # "As she does so I can just make out a moan coming from her lips, and her eyelids flicker slightly."
    "Al hacerlo, logro distinguir un gemido brotando de sus labios, y sus párpados tiemblan levemente."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3453
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_82bed41f:

    # ks "That's right, Nozomi. Obeying me feels wonderful."
    ks "Eso es, Nozomi. Se siente maravilloso obedecerme."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3454
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_0f075c4c:

    # ncg smile blush "It, uh... yeah." with dissolve
    ncg smile blush "Se... eh... sí." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3455
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_df118e9d:

    # ks "And since you're going to be so obedient to me, I think we ought to make a few changes while we're in this house together."
    ks "Y ya que serás tan obediente, creo que debemos hacer algunos cambios para cuando estemos juntos en esta casa."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3456
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_f50fe462:

    # ncg neutral "What are you thinking?" with dissolve
    ncg neutral "¿En qué estás pensando?" with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3457
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_7deb8da8:

    # ks "First, you will call me Sir from now on. Understand?"
    ks "Primero que nada, me hablarás de usted y me llamaras señor. ¿Entendido?"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3458
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_6fe049c9:

    # ncg "Yes, Sir."
    ncg "Sí, Señor."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3459
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_91fe872c:

    # "Her response is immediate, and I can see that flicker of her eyelids once again. So far so good."
    "Su respuesta es inmediata, y puedo nuevamente ese temblor en sus párpados. Hasta ahora, muy bien."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3460
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_b4646938:

    # ks "And also..."
    ks "Y además..."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3461
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_a1100909:

    # "But what happens if I really test her?"
    "Pero ¿qué pasará si en verdad la pongo a prueba?"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3462
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_3c388f77_1:

    # ks "Do you really need all those clothes?"
    ks "¿De verdad necesitas tanta ropa?"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3463
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_db4af3ea:

    # ncg surprised "Huh?" with dissolve
    ncg surprised "¿Eh?" with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3464
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_ce65ef50:

    # ks smirk "Anyone looking at us would think we're equals. But that's not true, is it?"
    ks smirk "Cualquiera que nos viera pensaría que somos iguales. Pero eso no es verdad, ¿o sí?"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3465
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_434d63e0:

    # ncg sad "A-ah, well... t-that is..." with dissolve
    ncg sad "A-eh, pues... e-eso..." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3466
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_913866ab:

    # ks "Answer my question, Nozomi."
    ks "Contesta mi pregunta, Nozomi."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3467
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_34320a28:

    # ncg "Mmn, it's not true." with dissolve
    ncg "Mmn, no es verdad." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3468
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_e69b5ee6:

    # ks "That's right. Now strip down to your underwear."
    ks "Correcto. Ahora quítate todo, menos la ropa interior."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3474
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_dc4a0e63:

    # "She makes a face, but she doesn't hesitate to stand up and start disrobing in front of me. I hope that means she really is comfortable with this." with dissolve
    "Me hace una mueca, pero, sin vacilar, se levanta del sofá y empieza a desvestirse ante mí. Espero que eso signifique que sí está cómoda con esto." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3475
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_43b3b17c:

    # "I mean, I don't think she sees simply undressing as \"sex stuff\"."
    "Es decir, no creo que vea el simplemente desvestirse como \"sexual\"."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3477
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_4906b3f2:

    # "But as I watch her shed her outer clothing, standing in front of me in nothing more than her underwear, I don't get the impression she's really that upset." with dissolve
    "Pero al verla terminar de remover su ropa, de pie delante de mí con nada más que prendas interiores, no me da la impresión de que esté tan molesta." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3478
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_858a3b44:

    # ks smile blush "There. That's more reflective of your status in this house, don't you think, Nozomi?"
    ks smile blush "Eso es. Esto refleja mejor tu estatus en esta casa, ¿no lo crees, Nozomi?"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3479
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_edf7eed5:

    # ncg "... Yes, Sir."
    ncg "... Sí, Señor."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3480
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_a7d49c66:

    # "Watching her reaction is fun and at least a little bit sexy to me but... now what?"
    "Ver su reacción me parece divertido, y al menos un poquito sexy, pero... ¿ahora qué?"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3481
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_55a1b4af:

    # ks neutral "So, err..."
    ks neutral "Pues, emm..."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3482
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_d6ed0595_1:

    # "I've never done anything like this before."
    "Nunca había hecho algo como esto."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3483
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_4e91473e_1:

    # ks "On your knees, Nozomi."
    ks "De rodillas, Nozomi."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3486
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_a68b2a8e_1:

    # "As she obediently drops down to the floor to sit on her heels, I reach down to pet her head."
    "Cuando obedientemente se deja caer al suelo para posarse sobre sus rodillas, me acerco a acariciar su cabeza."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3487
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_9a702e9f:

    # "Maybe I should ask her what she wants me to make her do? Would that be defeating the purpose?"
    "¿Así que tal vez debería preguntarle que quiere que le ordene hacer? ¿Pero eso mataría todo el propósito?"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3490
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_f519231d_1:

    # "And now she's looking at me expectantly again." with dissolve
    "Y ahora me está viendo expectante de nuevo." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3491
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_ba019533_1:

    # "Well... if I assume she can now stop my influence over her at any time, maybe I shouldn't worry about this too much."
    "Pues... si asumo que ahora puede detener mi influencia sobre ella en cualquier momento, no me debería preocupar demasiado."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3492
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_56ef9ff9:

    # ks smile "You know, I'm still thinking about the power I have over you right now. About all the things I could make you do."
    ks smile "¿Sabes?, sigo pensando en el poder que tengo sobre ti. En todas las cosas que podrías obligarte a hacer."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3493
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_bff579d5_1:

    # ks "And all you'd be able to do in return is smile and obey. Even if you knew it would risk your life. Even if my orders would strip you of your very humanity."
    ks "Y lo único que serías capaz de hacer en respuesta es sonreír y obedecer. Incluso si supieras que mis órdenes pondrían en riesgo tu vida. Incluso si supieras que te despojarían de tu humanidad."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3494
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_6adfa4a3_1:

    # ks "Doesn't that excite you, Nozomi?"
    ks "¿Acaso no te emociona, Nozomi?"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3495
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_9984b6e0:

    # n "It... it does, Sir."
    n "S-... sí, Señor."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3496
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_da2cb5d6_1:

    # ks "So then, Nozomi. With this ultimate power at my disposal I command you to..."
    ks "Entonces, Nozomi. Con el poder absoluto que tengo a mi disposición, te ordeno que..."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3502
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_3d6a8fc6_1:

    # "Nozomi blinks in surprise as she registers what I said, but her body responds immediately as she rises back to her feet and starts padding towards the kitchen." with dissolve
    "Nozomi parpadea sorprendida mientras analiza lo que dije, pero su cuerpo responde inmediatamente poniéndose de pie y dirigiéndose a la cocina." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3508
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_33410836_1:

    # "I'm sure I heard a soft chuckle from her as she disappears from view, followed shortly after by the sound of the fridge door opening."
    "Estoy seguro de que oí una risita cuando desapareció de mi vista, seguido poco después por el sonido del refrigerador abriéndose."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3509
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_a192aea5_1:

    # "Not wanting to miss the sight of an underwear-clad girl cooking for me, I decide to follow her."
    "Sin querer perderme la imagen de una chica en ropa interior cocinando para mí, decido seguirla."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3511
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_27b0ea84_1:

    # "Taking a seat at the dining table, I simply watch with a grin as she works, navigating around my kitchen with relative ease to get her task done."
    "Con una sonrisa, tomo asiento en el comedor y la observo trabajar, navegando por mi cocina con relativa facilidad para terminar su tarea."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3513
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_a5e47e8d_1:

    # "I can tell she's a little flustered at my staring, but she doesn't say anything as she prepares the food, sets it on a plate and serves it up to me at the table." with dissolve
    "Puedo notar que la pone un poco nerviosa que la mire, pero prepara la comida sin decir nada, la coloca en un plato y la sirve en la mesa para mí." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3514
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_a129ba68:

    # n "Here you are, Sir."
    n "B-buen provecho, Señor."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3515
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_6cde1bce_1:

    # "I take a look at the cheese omelette in front of me, then at her, still grinning."
    "Le echo un vistazo al omelet de queso que tengo delante, luego a ella, sin dejar de sonreír."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3516
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_3de11c0a_1:

    # ks smirk "I never said I wanted to eat it, Nozo. Besides, I'm not hungry."
    ks smirk "Nunca dije que quería comerlo, Nozo. Además, no tengo hambre."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3517
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_e4acfda5:

    # n side frown "What? Geez, then why did you have me make it?" with dissolve
    n side frown "¿Qué? Caray, entonces, ¿por qué me hizo prepararlo?" with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3518
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_8e452eea_1:

    # ks "Sit down and eat it yourself."
    ks "Siéntate y cómetelo tú."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3522
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_2de34686:

    # n front pout "But I'm not hungry either..." with dissolve
    n front pout "Pero tampoco tengo hambre..." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3525
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_f7ec5f10_1:

    # "She says, as she tears a piece off and pops it into her mouth."
    "Dice ella, cortando un trozo e introduciéndolo a su boca."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3526
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_f7dd934c:

    # n "Jerk..."
    n "Cretino..."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3527
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_14fa03e8_1:

    # ks smile "Tell me how you're really feeling, Nozomi."
    ks smile "Dime cómo te sientes en realidad, Nozomi."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3528
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_3de4fc13_1:

    # "She takes a moment to swallow her food before replying."
    "Hace una pausa para tragar su comida antes de contestar."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3529
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_d8ca19a8:

    # n pout_left "Really good. I know it's just a simple thing, but even making me do this and feeling like I can't stop myself?" with dissolve
    n pout_left "Muy bien. Sé que es algo muy simple, pero incluso ser obligada a hacer esto y saber que no me puedo detener me causa más euforia de la que se imagina." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3530
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_ce29d733:

    # n "It's really giving me a thrill."
    n "Me está emocionando bastante."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3531
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_4d019a1e_1:

    # "She stops to take another bite of the omelette; her compulsion to obey my latest order conflicting with the previous."
    "Se detiene para darle otro mordisco al omelet; su impulso por obedecer mi más reciente orden entra en conflicto con la anterior."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3532
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_806f8b6e_1:

    # ks neutral "Yet you still look a bit worried to me."
    ks neutral "Aunque yo aún te veo un poco preocupada."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3533
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_6c378077:

    # n sleeptalk "I guess I am, Sir. I'm just embarrassed to admit this to you. And to myself." with dissolve
    n sleeptalk "Supongo que lo estoy, Señor. Es que me avergüenza admitirle esto a usted. Y a mí misma." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3534
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_cfba2d0c:

    # ks smile "Nozomi, there's no reason to feel embarrassed about feeling this way. You like what you like."
    ks smile "Nozomi, sentirte así no es nada de qué avergonzarse. Lo que te gusta te gusta."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3536
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_13a3aa79:

    # ks "Also, no one else needs to know if you don't want to say anything. We had a deal, remember?" with dissolve
    ks "Además, nadie más debe saber si no quieres decir nada. Tenemos un trato, ¿recuerdas?" with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3537
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_023d553f_1:

    # ks "So don't feel ashamed about who you are. You're safe here, with someone who wants you to be happy."
    ks "Así que no sientas pena de ser quién eres. Estás a salvo aquí, con alguien que quiere que seas feliz."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3538
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_43ec31f6_1:

    # ks "Let yourself enjoy this."
    ks "Disfrútalo."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3540
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_e4453903:

    # "Nozomi gives me a smile from across the table and nods, still half-chewing as she responds." with dissolve
    "Nozomi me lanza una sonrisa desde el otro lado de la mesa y asiente, y sin dejar del todo de masticar, responde:" with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3541
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_9eac59dd:

    # n "Thank you, Sir. That does actually make me feel better."
    n "Gracias, Señor. Eso me hace sentir mejor."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3542
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_59e9b764:

    # "I smile back at her."
    "Le devuelvo la sonrisa."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3543
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_064b7e23:

    # ks "Good. Now be a good girl and finish your omelette, and wash up when you're done."
    ks "Ahora sé una buena chica y termina tu omelet, y limpia todo cuando acabes."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3545
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_fecb6bff_1:

    # "She pokes her tongue out at me, then takes another bite of her food." with dissolve
    "Me saca la lengua, para luego tomar otro bocado de su comida." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3548
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_ea0d63a2_1:

    # "Soon after she was done in the kitchen I had her get dressed and ready to leave."
    "Poco después, cuando su trabajo en la cocina hubo acabado, hice que se vistiera, lista para partir."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3549
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_ee525a79_1:

    # "Not that I wanted to, but dad's going to be home soon, and I don't think either of us want to explain this to him of all people."
    "No es que quiera, pero papá volverá a casa pronto, y no creo que ninguno de los dos quiera explicarle esto a nadie, mucho menos a él."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3550
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_dc146684_1:

    # ks smile "You got everything?"
    ks smile "¿Tienes, todo?"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3551
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_b197dd2f:

    # n "Yes, Sir. Are we doing this again tomorrow?"
    n "Sí, Señor. ¿Volveremos a hacerlo mañana?"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3552
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_6ce3cc38_1:

    # "I respond with a wink and a knowing smirk."
    "Respondo con un guiño y una sonrisa."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3553
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_5c91c90b_1:

    # ks smirk "Oh, you WILL be coming back here tomorrow. Do I make myself clear?"
    ks smirk "Oh, tú VAS regresar aquí mañana. ¿Quedó claro?"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3555
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_61218add:

    # "She replies with a hearty giggle." with dissolve
    "Ella contesta con una fuerte risa." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3556
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_eabf99a5:

    # n "Yes, Sir. I must obey~"
    n "Sí, Señor. Debo obedecer."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3569
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_87f0e4ed_1:

    # "Nozomi and I didn't contact each other overnight, and I'm anxious to see her again."
    "Nozomi y yo no hicimos contacto durante la noche, y siento mucha ansiedad por volverla a ver."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3570
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_109f4787:

    # "I want to see her again so bad."
    "Tengo tantas ganas de volverla a ver."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3572
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_0c63d5ee:

    # "Coming into class a little earlier than usual, I take my seat and wait for the rest of my classmates to filter in."
    "Llegando a clase un poco más temprano que de costumbre, tomo mi asiento y espero al resto de mis compañeros."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3577
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_69ccab66:

    # "There's Sayori. Trying half-heartedly to disguise a yawn with a hand as she walks past me to her desk."
    "Ahí está Sayori. Intentando ocultar un bostezo con su mano sin mucho entusiasmo, rodeándome camino a su escritorio."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3583
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_f2d04bf2:

    # "Hiroko strolls inside some minutes later, almost before the bell."
    "Hiroko entra algunos minutos más tarde, casi antes de la campana."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3584
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_957444bf:

    # h "Bounce your eyes, dude."
    h "¿Qué le ves, viejo?"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3585
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_a6ecf7a7:

    # ks surprised "What?"
    ks surprised "¿Qué?"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:4722
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_7ede9829:

    # h angry vein "You know what I'm talking about, creepo." with dissolve
    h angry vein "Ya sabes de qué hablo, bicho raro." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3587
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_01bef69d:

    # ks frown "I wasn't even..."
    ks frown "Ni siquiera estaba..."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3589
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_ac9e8087:

    # "I trail off as she just walks past me to her desk."
    "Me detengo en seco al verla caminar hacia su escritorio."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3590
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_989492f9:

    # "I wasn't staring at her or anybody? What a bitch."
    "No la estaba mirando a ella ni a nadie. Si será perra."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3592
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_4b4292a0:

    # "But class is about to start. Where the hell is Nozomi?"
    "Pero la clase está por empezar. ¿Dónde diablos está Nozomi?"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3594
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_d51167e3:

    # "It takes me too long to realize, but as class continues I notice Hiroko and Sayori occasionally talk to the empty seat where Nozomi sits."
    "Tardo mucho en darme cuenta, pero con el transcurso de la clase, noto que Hiroko y Sayori le hablan ocasionalmente al asiento vacío de Nozomi."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3595
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_0e1361be:

    # "Of course it isn't empty. But then..."
    "Claramente no está vacío. Pero, entonces..."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3596
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_d995e867:

    # "How is it that I STILL can't see her?"
    "¿Cómo es que TODAVÍA no puedo verla?"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3599
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_2cb5fb72:

    # "Eventually the bell rings for lunch and Nozomi's friends assemble around her desk."
    "Eventualmente, suena la campana del almuerzo y las amigas de Nozomi se reúnen junto a su escritorio."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3604
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_4cba6c86:

    # h "Let's go, rooftop club~"
    h "Vamos, club de la azotea."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3605
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_3007e0c6:

    # s sleep uniform_folded "I would be fine settling in class today, but if it's what the group demands..." with dissolve
    s sleep uniform_folded "Me agradaría permanecer hoy en el aula, pero si es lo que el grupo demanda..." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3607
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_b498f359:

    # n "I wouldn't say \"demand\", but it's nice out today." with dissolve
    n "Yo no diría \"demanda\", pero hoy está lindo afuera." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3608
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_146d92f1:

    # "That's definitely her voice I just heard!"
    "¡Esa que acabo de oír definitivamente es su voz!"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3609
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_3d6f0543:

    # s smile_right "Ah well, who am I to argue with the majority. Lead on." with dissolve
    s smile_right "Oh, bueno, ¿quién soy yo para discutir con la mayoría? Después de ustedes." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3610
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_b8523071:

    # n "... Actually, you two go on ahead. I need to take care of something real quick."
    n "... De hecho, ustedes adelántense. Necesito encargarme de algo rapidito."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3613
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_8091953c:

    # "And off they go." with dissolve
    "Y allá van." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3614
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_ac8bd912:

    # "Taking out my lunchbox, I sigh and pop it open as I observe the others who stayed behind from my spot at the back of the room."
    "Saco mi lonchera y la abro con un suspiro, observando a los otros que se también quedaron atrás desde mi posición al fondo del salón."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3615
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_d51aa0db:

    # "I may have started something with Nozomi, but right now I feel as alone as I ever was."
    "Puede que haya empezado algo con Nozomi, pero, justo ahora, me siento tan solo como siempre."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3616
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_e92726d5:

    # ks surprised "H-Huh!?" with vpunch
    ks surprised "¿¡E-Eh!?" with vpunch

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3617
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_5f2f982a:

    # "Something just pressed against my nose!"
    "¡Algo presionó mi nariz!"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3618
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_9abed02b:

    # "Rubbing the tip of my nose, the realization dawns on me as I hear the hurried shuffling of footsteps on the floor beside me that quickly grows distant."
    "Frotando la punta de mi nariz, me doy cuenta de qué sucedió al escuchar unos apresurados pasos arrastrarse por el suelo junto a mí, que pronto se vuelven distantes."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3620
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_33893042:

    # "Not that I can tell what I've figured out to the couple of classmates who wheeled round to look at me after I cried out."
    "Aunque no puedo decirles lo que averigüé a los estudiantes que se dieron la vuelta tras oírme exclamar."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3621
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_304d5f6d:

    # "At least someone is enjoying this..."
    "Al menos alguien lo está disfrutando..."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3624
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_cf3c72b7:

    # "A few minutes later my phone buzzes in my pocket."
    "Unos minutos después, mi teléfono vibra en mi bolsillo."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3627
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_d3d57880:

    # "It's from Nozomi."
    "Es de Nozomi."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3628
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_ce82ada5:

    # "{color=#93624B}\"Boop!\"{/color}"
    "{color=#93624B}\"¡Picotón!\"{/color}"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3629
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_dead8162:

    # "Rolling my eyes, I hurriedly text her back."
    "Volteando los ojos, me apresuro a contestarle."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3630
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_dfe37e05:

    # "{color=#4B9374}\"At least someone's having fun around here.\"{/color}"
    "{color=#4B9374}\"Por lo menos alguien se divierte por aquí.\"{/color}"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3632
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_2525d494:

    # "{color=#93624B}\"So you really cant see me still? That is NUTS\"{/color}" with vpunch
    "{color=#93624B}\"Entonces de verdad aún no puedes verme? Qué LOCO\"{/color}" with vpunch

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3633
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_5979e90a:

    # "{color=#4B9374}\"I seriously can't see you. I don't understand it either.\"{/color}"
    "{color=#4B9374}\"De verdad no puedo verte. Tampoco lo entiendo.\"{/color}"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3635
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_eea57c21:

    # "{color=#93624B}\"You were looking right at me when i came in this morning\"{/color}" with vpunch
    "{color=#93624B}\"Estabas mirando directo hacia mí cuando entré esta mañana\"{/color}" with vpunch

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3637
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_d1a94e3f:

    # "{color=#93624B}\"Thats why hiroko had a go at you\"{/color}" with vpunch
    "{color=#93624B}\"Por eso hiroko se enojó contigo\"{/color}" with vpunch

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3638
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_b35d3978:

    # "{color=#4B9374}\"I figured. Anyway you coming over tonight?\"{/color}"
    "{color=#4B9374}\"Me lo imaginé. Como sea, ¿vendrás a visitarme esta noche?\"{/color}"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3640
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_8ebd4323:

    # "{color=#93624B}\"Are you kidding? How could i NOT???\"{/color}" with vpunch
    "{color=#93624B}\"¿Estás bromeando? Cómo crees que NO???\"{/color}" with vpunch

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3642
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_e407c71f:

    # "I can feel her excitement radiating from the phone's screen as I set it down on my desk."
    "Puedo sentir su emoción irradiando de la pantalla del teléfono al colocarlo en mi escritorio."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3643
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_fa044225:

    # "It's a little infectious. And it helps settle down my frustrations."
    "Es un poco contagiosa. Y me ayuda a calmar un poco mi frustración."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3644
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_39cf17ba:

    # "I can't stay annoyed at her, that's for sure."
    "No puedo molestarme con ella, de eso no hay duda."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3647
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_b2940d90:

    # "The rest of the day passes without incident and I take myself straight home."
    "El resto del día trascurre sin incidentes y me voy directo a casa."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:4785
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_7cd223a1:

    # "It's not long before the doorbell rings. That can only be her."
    "No pasa mucho tiempo antes de que suene el timbre. Tiene que ser ella."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3651
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_90044a6c:

    # n "Hey, Kyou."
    n "¿Qué tal, Kyou?"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3653
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_740f71ce:

    # "I jump back a little. Hearing a voice just come out of thin air is still a little freaky, even if I was expecting it."
    "Me sobresalto un poco. Escuchar su voz salir de la nada aún da algo de miedo, incluso cuando me lo espero."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3655
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_4f49f282:

    # "I watch as Nozomi's shoes appear before my eyes as she leaves them behind."
    "Cuando Nozomi los deja atrás, veo sus zapatos aparecer ante mis ojos."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3656
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_f4f83874:

    # "And I still don't understand how she did this. Or how I'm still doing this."
    "Aún no entiendo cómo hizo esto. O cómo sigo yo haciendo esto."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3657
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_4c84a1b6:

    # n "Kyou? I'm on the couch."
    n "¿Kyou? Estoy en el sofá."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3658
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_2031f68d:

    # ks surprised "O-Oh. Right."
    ks surprised "O-oh. Claro."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3660
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_e22df403:

    # "As I go to sit down, I gingerly hold out a hand to try and get a feel for where exactly she is."
    "Luego de ir a sentarme, pongo cautelosamente una mano delante para intentar sentir dónde se encuentra exactamente."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3662
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_2ae200b8:

    # "And for that I get my hand slapped out of nowhere. It almost makes me jump." with vpunch
    "Y recibo un manotazo de la nada por eso. Casi me hace saltar." with vpunch

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3663
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_79996358:

    # n "Hey, hands to yourself!"
    n "¡Oye, manos quietas!"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:4762
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_0513fb5c:

    # ks confused "I-I wasn't- {w=0.5}{nw}"
    ks confused "N-no estaba. {w=0.5}{nw}"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3665
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_dbb0ff60:

    # n "No, but that's what you're going to do if you keep that up!"
    n "¡No, pero lo harás si sigues con eso!"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3666
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_08e5c58c:

    # "I fold my arms as I sigh."
    "Me cruzo de brazos y suspiro."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3667
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_6fe99ea1:

    # ks frown "Sorry... But it's the only way I can tell exactly where you are, and that's kind of your fault."
    ks frown "Perdón... pero es mi única forma de saber exactamente dónde estás, y eso es más o menos tu culpa."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:4766
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_3ab712f8:

    # "I hear a little groan in front of me. And I don't need to see her to figure she just rolled her eyes at me."
    "Escucho un pequeño gruñido frente a mí. Y creo que no necesito verla para saber que me volteó los ojos."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3669
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_c070ec10:

    # n "Alright, Kyou, fine. Get comfortable, hold still and I'll see what I can do."
    n "Muy bien, Kyou, de acuerdo. Ponte cómodo, quédate quieto y veré qué puedo hacer."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3670
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_37e9fd3c:

    # "I give a little nod to the air, relax my posture and stare ahead as I wonder how this is going to work."
    "Asiento ligeramente con la cabeza, relajo mi postura y miro hacia adelante, preguntándome cómo es que va a funcionar."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3671
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_9555071a:

    # "I can't even see if she's holding anyth- {w=0.8}{nw}"
    "Ni siquiera puedo ver si está sosteniendo al- {w=0.8}{nw}"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3673
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_7f1b3944:

    # n "Light's up here, Kyou... Yes, that's right."
    n "La luz está aquí arriba, Kyou... Sí, eso es."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3674
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_4418a766:

    # n "Did you notice how quickly you looked at the light? How natural that was..."
    n "¿Notaste lo rápido que miraste la luz? Lo natural que se sintió..."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3681
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_ab6f4fa5:

    # "All of a sudden I find myself waking with a start, to the sound of snapping fingers."
    "De repente despierto con un sobre salto, ante el sonido de un chasquido de dedos."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3682
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_e91d30c5:

    # ncg "Welcome back."
    ncg "Bienvenido de vuelta."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3684
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_d55da128:

    # "I shoot the girl a puzzled look as I blink slowly."
    "Le doy a la chica una mirada perpleja, parpadeando lentamente."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3685
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_c4a61f4a:

    # ks frown "What do you... oh!"
    ks frown "¿A qué te... ¡oh!"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3686
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_5c10647b:

    # "As I blink again, my initial confusion turns to joy as I'm greeted with a grin."
    "Vuelvo a pestañear y mi confusión inicial se convierte en alegría, al verla recibirme con una sonrisa."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3687
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_23cde115:

    # ks smile "I can see you again!"
    ks smile "¡Puedo verte otra vez!"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3689
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_87bb76af:

    # "Nozomi claps her hands together, with the penlight between them, and beams with pride." with dissolve
    "Nozomi da un aplauso, con la linterna entre sus manos e irradiando orgullo." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3690
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_95af1d1e:

    # ncg "Kyou, either I'm seriously amazing at this or you're the most convincing actor I've ever seen!"
    ncg "¡Kyou, o eres en serio asombroso en esto o eres el actor más convincente que haya visto!"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3691
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_5786d525:

    # "I grin back at her. There's just no stopping myself from getting caught up in Nozomi's excitement."
    "Le devuelvo la sonrisa. No puedo evitar ser contagiado por la emoción de Nozomi."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3692
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_0a9284dd:

    # ks "And which do you think it is?"
    ks "¿Y cuál crees que sea?"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:4777
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_d6379b0e:

    # ncg smile2 "Ehehe, the former, obviously! Although maybe I need to drag you along to my D&D group sometime, just to be sure..." with dissolve
    ncg smile2 "¡Jejeje, la primera, obviamente! Aunque tal vez deba arrastrarte a mi grupo de Calabozos y dragones algún día, solo para estar segura..." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:4789
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_bf8b94ce:

    # "We share a chuckle before Nozomi leans back on the table and starts twirling the penlight in her fingers."
    "Compartimos una carcajada y luego Nozomi se recarga en el sofá, dándole vueltas a la linterna entre sus dedos."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3695
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_92810943:

    # ks "By the way... have you shown that to anyone else?"
    ks "Por cierto... ¿le has mostrado eso a alguien más?"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:4780
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_b1d263e4:

    # ncg neutral2 "Hm?" with dissolve
    ncg neutral2 "¿Mm?" with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3697
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_4cd2f4fe:

    # ks "The penlight."
    ks "La linterna."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:4782
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_79b2cdd6:

    # ncg stern2 "Ah, no. Not at all. Besides, what would I tell people? It'd just be a light as far as they're concerned." with dissolve
    ncg stern2 "Ah, no. Para nada. Además, ¿qué le diría a la gente? No sería más que una linterna en lo que a ellos concierne." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3699
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_8abdd3ec:

    # ks neutral "Oh... yeah, that's true. But I was thinking..."
    ks neutral "Oh... sí, es cierto. Pero estaba pensando..."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3700
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_6f9eb2ed:

    # ks "You being interested in hypnosis isn't that weird, is it?"
    ks "Que estés interesada en la hipnosis no es tan raro, ¿o sí?"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3701
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_3ab9db12:

    # ncg "Well... maybe not in itself, no. I mean, it's a little weird maybe, but still..."
    ncg "Pues... tal vez no en sí. Digo, un poco raro, tal vez, pero, aun sí..."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3702
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_dabe28f9:

    # ks smile "So why not tell them what it's for? Just leave out that it turns you on doing it."
    ks smile "Entonces, ¿por qué no decirles para qué es? Solo deja fuera el hecho de que te enciende."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3703
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_abbc9c0d:

    # ncg annoyed "N-no! It'll come out, I'm sure of it." with dissolve
    ncg annoyed "¡N-no! Saldrá a la luz, estoy segura." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3704
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_b879b385:

    # ks neutral "Really?"
    ks neutral "¿En serio?"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:4789
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_2e43d933:

    # ncg stern2 "Really. How long did you last before I found out your true intentions, Kyou?" with dissolve
    ncg stern2 "En serio. ¿Cuánto tiempo me tomó averiguar tus verdaderas intenciones, Kyou?" with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3706
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_1f4ab4d0:

    # ks "Uh..."
    ks "Eh..."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3707
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_889b0944:

    # ncg "... Exactly. And then they'll never look at me the same way again."
    ncg "... Exacto. Y nunca volverán a verme igual."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3708
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_9cc8f208:

    # ncg sad "A-as it is, I'm not entirely sure I kept it together today." with dissolve
    ncg sad "E-es más, no estoy del todo segura de haber guardado la calma hoy." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3709
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_22a4ff85:

    # ks surprised "... Huh?"
    ks surprised "... ¿Eh?"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3710
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_04e034fc:

    # ncg "When I realized you were still under my suggestion this morning? It was virtually all I could think about."
    ncg "¿Cuando me di cuenta de que seguías bajo los efectos de mi sugestión esta mañana? Eso fue virtualmente lo único en lo que pude pensar."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3711
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_d7214973:

    # ncg "I mean, we know how hypnosis isn't really about controlling minds at all, that it's a mutual collaboration between hypnotist and hypnotized..."
    ncg "Quiero decir, sabemos que la hipnosis no se trata en realidad de controlar mentes, que es colaboración mutua entre hipnotista e hipnotizado..."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:4796
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_449f6392:

    # ncg neutral2 "But I remembered how you practically begged me to make you lose the suggestion I gave you last night. Like you really couldn't do it without me." with dissolve
    ncg neutral2 "Pero recordé cómo prácticamente me rogaste hacerte perder la sugestión que te di anoche. Como si realmente no pudieras hacerlo sin mí." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:4797
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_77d08b70:

    # ncg surprised2 "And I couldn't help but think that this was something I did TO you. Not WITH you." with dissolve
    ncg surprised2 "Y no pude evitar pensar que fue algo que TE HICE A ti y no algo que hice CONtigo." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:4798
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_f9c73c4a:

    # ncg confused2 "That you were helpless to reject the reality I planted in your mind, because what we did really WAS mind control." with dissolve
    ncg confused2 "Que fuiste incapaz de rechazar la realidad que implanté en tu mente porque lo que hice SÍ FUE control mental." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3715
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_a6259428:

    # ncg "And thinking like that... w-well..."
    ncg "Y pensar así... p-pues..."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:4800
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_ff869ca6:

    # ncg sad blush2 "I just hope it wasn't written all over my face for all to see." with dissolve
    ncg sad blush2 "Espero no haberlo tenido escrito en toda la cara." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3717
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_4ca1b54a:

    # ks smirk "Well if it was I couldn't tell you."
    ks smirk "Bueno, si así fue, yo no pude saberlo."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:4802
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_bd2e6bb9:

    # ncg smile2 noblush "Heh. But yes, you try explaining this to someone not in the know." with dissolve
    ncg smile2 noblush "Je. Pero sí, intenta explicárselo a alguien que no sepa de estas cosas." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3863
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_bf055693:

    # "As a new day begins, I walk to school feeling uncertain."
    "Comienza un nuevo día, y yo camino a la escuela sintiéndome inseguro."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3867
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_51c5a201:

    # "I did spend a little time researching why my hypnosis could've affected Sayori the way she says it did."
    "Sí pasé algo de tiempo investigando cómo podría mi hipnosis haber afectado a Sayori de la forma que dice."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3869
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_aeda03e5:

    # "But I pretty much came up empty. I'm still thinking Sayori is in denial over her true feelings for me and her need to take time off for herself."
    "Pero encontré nada. Aún pienso que Sayori está en negación de sus verdaderos sentimientos por mí y su necesidad de tomar tiempo libre."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3873
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_7a26f981:

    # "Sayori acknowledges me with a brief nod before taking her seat as lessons begin."
    "Sayori me saluda con un breve gesto de su cabeza antes de tomar su asiento para el inicio de las lecciones."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3874
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_ef4da00d:

    # "Sure would love to talk to her more about this instead of reading English lit, but there's just no way."
    "Cómo me encantaría hablar más con ella al respecto en lugar de leer del libro de inglés, pero no hay manera."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3877
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_3b3bb14e:

    # "The day passes uneventfully, as me and Sayori can do little more than exchange brief eye contact during our schedules."
    "El día transcurre sin más eventos, pues Sayori y yo no podemos hacer más que tener contacto visual ocasional durante nuestras actividades escolares."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3882
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_42665ffc:

    # "When I finally get home, with Sayori following discreetly behind me, it feels like a whole week has passed."
    "Cuando finalmente llego a casa, con Sayori caminando discretamente detrás de mí, siento como si hubiera pasado una semana entera."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3883
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_554db4f4:

    # s "So, did you find anything?"
    s "Entonces, ¿encontraste algo?"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3884
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_434fb46a:

    # ks "Not a thing. You?"
    ks "Nada de nada. ¿Y tú?"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:4654
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_23dd0276:

    # s neutral "I found nothing conclusive." with dissolve
    s neutral "No hallé nada concluyente." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3886
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_eb0ab054:

    # "She sighs as she goes on to add:"
    "Suspira y luego añade:"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3888
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_6c568177:

    # s annoyed_right "Only that what you did was highly irresponsible and I hate myself for going along with it." with dissolve
    s annoyed_right "Únicamente que lo que hiciste fue altamente irresponsable y me odio a mí misma por haber sido partícipe." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5154
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_2670a5f9:

    # ks confused "Huh?"
    ks confused "¿Eh?"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3890
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_ee0f6946:

    # s uniform_folded "You ended up giving me a second personality, Kyou! Do you realize how dangerous that is?" with dissolve
    s uniform_folded "¡Acabaste dándome una segunda personalidad, Kyou! ¿Te das cuenta de lo peligroso que es eso?" with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:4660
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_b3dd148c:

    # s irritated "And do you know something else? I took it upon myself to run a little experiment last night." with dissolve
    s irritated "¿Y sabes algo más? Decidí hacer un pequeño experimento anoche." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:4661
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_2fdb8369:

    # s neutral "Before climbing into bed, I had every intention of keeping my mind active for a while." with dissolve
    s neutral "Antes de entrar a la cama, tenía toda la intención de mantener mi mente activa por un rato." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5158
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_4d486de7:

    # s frown "I also set an alarm on my phone for this morning, plugged it into my earphones and set the volume loud just to make sure I would wake up in time to not be late again." with dissolve
    s frown "También puse una alarma en mi teléfono para esta mañana, y la conecté a mis auriculares con volumen alto para asegurarme de no llegar tarde de nuevo." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:4663
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_30ccb3a0:

    # s annoyed_right "You would think the distraction of wearing earphones alone would stop me from instantly falling asleep." with dissolve
    s annoyed_right "Uno creería que la distracción de usar audífonos por sí sola evitaría que cayera dormida instantáneamente." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:4664
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_2721be16:

    # s concerned_right "But instead my mind blanked and I must have once again found myself immediately entering the land of nod!" with dissolve
    s concerned_right "¡Pero, en cambio, mi mente se quedó en blanco y, seguramente, una vez más entré de inmediato a la tierra de los sueños!" with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3896
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_8a05e2db:

    # "Huh. So I guess she stayed up all night researching and found a way to deprive herself of a good night's sleep again."
    "Vaya. Pues, supongo que se quedó despierta toda la noche investigando y así se las arregló para privarse otra vez de una buena noche de sueño."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3897
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_e2aaf33d:

    # "At least now I know why she once again looks like death."
    "Al menos ahora sé por qué de nuevo luce como muerta."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3898
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_4e10b16e:

    # s angry_right "So with that in mind I hope you understand that I am completely TERRIFIED of what is happening to me now!" with dissolve
    s angry_right "¡Así pues, con eso en mente, espero que entiendas que estoy completamente ATERRADA por lo que me está pasando ahora!" with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3899
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_0d1f373b:

    # "As she eyeballs me fiercely, I realize her entire body is trembling."
    "Me clava ferozmente la mirada, y me doy cuenta de que su cuerpo entero está temblando."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3900
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_580a4808:

    # ks "Sayori okay but just... calm down, alright?"
    ks "Sayori, está bien, solo... cálmate, ¿de acuerdo?"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:4670
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_e3454035:

    # s uniform annoyed_right "Calm?! Kyou, in case you were not paying attention let me stress to you more clearly so you cannot misunderstand." with dissolve
    s uniform annoyed_right "¡¿Calmarme?! Kyou, en caso de que no hayas estado prestando atención, permíteme expresarlo más claramente para que no lo puedas malentender." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:4672
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_4456e890:

    # s angry_right "I am losing control of my own MIND! And it is all your doing!" with dissolve
    s angry_right "¡Estoy perdiendo el control de mi MENTE! ¡Y es todo obra tuya!" with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5061
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_419d5192:

    # s uniform_handup "More to the point, how are you doing these things so... so EASILY?!" with dissolve
    s uniform_handup "Yendo al grano, ¿cómo es que haces estas cosas tan... ¡tan FÁCILMENTE!?" with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3906
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_e794b7c9:

    # ks "What?"
    ks "¿Qué?"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5063
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_43859e52:

    # s uniform "Kyou, you are an AMATEUR! How is it that you are affecting such drastic changes in my mental state with just two short hypnosis sessions?" with dissolve
    s uniform "¡Kyou, eres un AMATEUR! ¿Cómo es que estás generando cambios tan drásticos en mi estado mental con nada más que dos breves sesiones de hipnosis?" with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:4677
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_9c820a47:

    # s uniform_folded "Surely the best hypnotists in the world could not do what you have done to me." with dissolve
    s uniform_folded "De seguro ni los mejores hipnotistas del mundo podrían hacer lo que me has hecho." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3909
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_7b27cd3d:

    # "Shit, Sayori is scary when she's angry. I get that she's upset, but I can't deal with her breaking down like this."
    "Mierda, Sayori da miedo cuando está enojada. Entiendo que se encuentra molesta, pero no puedo lidiar con ella perdiendo así la compostura."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3910
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_2f2158fb:

    # s cry "I just... Why is it that when you put in even a modicum of effort the rewards are substantial." with dissolve
    s cry "Es que... ¿Por qué siempre que tú pones hasta el más mínimo esfuerzo las recompensas son substanciales?" with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5067
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_91e538fd:

    # s uniform "Whereas I have worked and studied day and night for years to reach my goal and I am projected to only JUST scrape into med school." with dissolve
    s uniform "Mientras que yo he estudiado día y noche por años para alcanzar mi meta y a duras PENAS tengo expectativas de entrar a la escuela de medicina." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3912
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_5b343cf5:

    # s angry_right "Do you have ANY idea how much this frustrates me, Kyou? To see you mope and moan and stare over the years and STILL succeed?" with dissolve
    s angry_right "¿Tienes ALGUNA idea de lo mucho que eso me frustra, Kyou? ¿Verte holgazanear con el paso de los años y de IGUAL FORMA tener éxito?" with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3913
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_60ec7c4b:

    # "Oh no, I've let her insult me before but I'm not taking this shit lying down again."
    "Oh, no, le he permitido insultarme antes, pero no pienso aguantar esta mierda de nuevo."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3914
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_ad5e9619:

    # ks frown "M-Man, where do you get off telling me I have it easy? You... you don't fucking know me! None of you do!"
    ks frown "C-caray, ¿qué te hace creer que puedes decirme que lo tengo fácil? ¡No... no sabes una mierda sobre mí! ¡Ni tú ni nadie!"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5071
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_bbf6f10b:

    # s uniform_folded irritated "What else is there to know? Do you imagine yourself a complex figure with unknowable motivations?" with dissolve
    s uniform_folded irritated "¿Qué más hay que saber? ¿Te visualizas a ti mismo como un ente complejo con motivaciones incognoscibles?" with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5072
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_8ae6f516:

    # s angry_right "That there is a hidden meaning to you pining pathetically over my friend for nearly three years?" with dissolve
    s angry_right "¿Qué hay un significado oculto para tu patética obsesión con mi amiga que ha durado casi tres años?" with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3917
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_de1791a1:

    # ks "Shit, why are you bringing that up again? I told you this is nothing to do with Nozomi! I've been trying to help you haven't I?"
    ks "Carajo, ¿por qué sales de nuevo con eso? ¡Ya te dije que esto no tiene nada que ver con Nozomi! He estado intentando ayudarte, ¿no?"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3918
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_1d6429e1:

    # s uniform "H-have you, Kyou? Or was it merely an excuse to do whatever you damn well pleased?" with dissolve
    s uniform "¿D-de verdad, Kyou? ¿O fue una simple excusa para poder hacer lo que te plazca?" with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3919
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_7ade50bd:

    # ks angry "Oh... c-come ON! I HAVE helped! You're not sleeping and it's killing you. Anyone can see that!"
    ks angry "Ay... ¡VAMOS! ¡SÍ he ayudado! No duermes y eso te está matando. ¡Todo el mundo puede ver eso!"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3920
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_533a9016:

    # ks "Maybe what I did isn't perfect, but you needed this, you ungrateful bitch!"
    ks "¡Tal vez lo que hice no fue perfecto, pero lo necesitabas, perra malagradecida!"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5080
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_f1519bd0:

    # s scared_right "... I never asked why you thought to study hypnosis in the first place, because I was afraid of something like this." with dissolve
    s scared_right "... Nunca pregunté por qué se te ocurrió estudiar hipnosis en primer lugar, porque me temía algo como esto." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5081
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_bf47bbbe:

    # s scared "But it seemed so... fanciful." with dissolve
    s scared "Pero parecía tan... ilusorio." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3926
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_162f45fe:

    # ks frown "... What? Are you even listening to me?"
    ks frown "... ¿Qué? ¿Siquiera me estás escuchando?"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3927
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_7dc41b6d:

    # s uniform_folded "The very notion that you would take up such a pursuit to make it even easier to get what you want." with dissolve
    s uniform_folded "La simple noción de que hayas perseguido tal cosa para que obtener lo que quieres fuera incluso más fácil." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3929
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_1bea0f94:

    # "She's just... fucking hysterical now, what do I do?"
    "Ahora está... mierda, está muy histérica. ¿Qué hago?"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3930
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_bf79eb24:

    # s cry "I should have known better than to see any good in you, Kyou." with dissolve
    s cry "No sé cómo pude ser tan crédula como para pensar que había algo de bondad en ti, Kyou." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3933
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_c8c53a25:

    # ks surprised "Sayori, uh... look. You're right."
    ks surprised "Sayori, eh... mira. Tienes razón."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3934
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_f7a2f3de:

    # ks "I didn't know what I was doing, and I hurt you; I can see that."
    ks "No sabía lo que hacía y te hice daño; me doy cuenta de eso."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3935
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_34082695:

    # ks "I'm... I'm sorry, Sayori. I really did mean to help you, but I should've been more careful."
    ks "Lo... lo lamento, Sayori. Juro que mi intención era ayudarte, pero debí ser más cuidadoso."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3936
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_4c7b4130:

    # "Sayori nods her head, sobbing as she draws a breath."
    "Sayori asiente su cabeza y, entre sollozos, toma aire."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5093
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_8e9a7ffd:

    # s uniform_handup concerned "And... And I apologize for some of the things I said. My sleep-deprivation cannot be helping my mood, to say nothing of my situation, but it is no excuse." with dissolve
    s uniform_handup concerned "Y... y yo me disculpo por varias de las cosas que dije. Mi privación del sueño no beneficia mi estado de ánimo, sin mencionar mi situación, pero no es excusa." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5201
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_34ee2422:

    # s concerned_right "Even so, I hope you can appreciate how utterly helpless I feel right now." with dissolve
    s concerned_right "Sin embargo espero que puedas apreciar lo enteramente indefensa que ahora mismo me siento." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5095
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_58c75924:

    # s sleeptalk "Everything I have worked for, you could undo with a few words by bringing out this other person now living inside me." with dissolve
    s sleeptalk "Todo en lo que he trabajado, podrías deshacerlo con solo un par de palabras, liberando a esa otra persona que vive dentro de mí." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5096
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_c9094a23:

    # s uniform "And all that I have learned suggests I would not be able to stop you, or her." with dissolve
    s uniform "Y lo que he aprendido me sugiere que no sería capaz de detenerte, ni a ella." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3941
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_2a0405ca:

    # ks sigh "Yeah... I guess... yeah. Thinking you're not being in control of your own thoughts is pretty fucking scary."
    ks sigh "Sí... supongo... sí. Pensar que no tienes el control de tus propios pensamientos es una puta pesadilla."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3943
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_49d4de5e:

    # "Sayori wipes her tired eyes as she sniffs the air." with dissolve
    "Sayori frota sus cansados ojos, inhalando con fuerza." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3945
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_dbb190d9:

    # s "It seems you still do not quite understand what I am telling you."
    s "Parece que aún no comprendes del todo lo que te estoy diciendo."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5209
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_96031646:

    # ks confused "Maybe. I mean, you keep saying you're not in control."
    ks confused "Tal vez. Bueno, estás diciendo que no tienes el control."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3947
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_f8fecf3a:

    # ks "I just don't see how anything I did with you could affect you like this unless you were holding onto it yourself."
    ks "Es solo que no veo cómo es que nada de lo que hice contigo podría afectarte a no ser que tú misma lo desearas."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:4717
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_a1fbdf4b:

    # s annoyed_right "And that is what we need to correct. I could ask you to undo what you did, and you may do it for me, but I need you to understand how this happened." with dissolve
    s annoyed_right "Y eso es lo que hay que corregir. Podría pedirte que deshicieras lo que hiciste, y puede que lo hagas por mí, pero necesito que entiendas cómo es que pasó." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5105
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_864cdd33:

    # s concerned_right "S-so... although I found nothing in my research, I was thinking that we need to interrogate the one unknown throughout all of this." with dissolve
    s concerned_right "D-de modo que... si bien no encontré nada en mi investigación, se me ocurrió que deberíamos interrogar al único desconocido en todo este asunto." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3950
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_19efb262:

    # ks neutral "What's that?"
    ks neutral "¿Y cuál es ese?"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5107
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_a0ef3ca6:

    # s uniform_handup surprised_right "Your penlight. You said it was your own invention?" with dissolve
    s uniform_handup surprised_right "Tu pluma linterna. ¿Dijiste que era tu propia invención?" with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3952
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_760ecb44:

    # ks "Yeah. I put it together in a few months on and off."
    ks "Sí. La armé hace algunos meses."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5109
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_a651a24a:

    # s neutral_right "And what did you say it does again?" with dissolve
    s neutral_right "¿Y qué fue lo que dijiste que hace?" with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3954
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_8aa3ccd2:

    # ks "I just designed it to catch people's attention and help them fall into trance. Why?"
    ks "Simplemente está diseñada para atrapar la atención de la gente y ayudarlos a entrar en trance. ¿Por qué?"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3955
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_72ba5e55:

    # s annoyed_right "It is just that I cannot help thinking about my reaction to it, in your own words." with dissolve
    s annoyed_right "Es que no puedo evitar pensar en mi reacción hacia ella, en tus propias palabras." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5112
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_f9a24d26:

    # s uniform_folded "About how I \"gasped in awe\", or somesuch." with dissolve
    s uniform_folded "Que \"jadeé con asombro\", o algo similar." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5220
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_a38cfdc7:

    # ks confused "Yeah, that's right."
    ks confused "Sí, es correcto."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:4727
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_7a84f066:

    # s neutral_right "The light is certainly distracting. I felt like I wanted to focus on nothing else, although it is hard to remember exactly." with dissolve
    s neutral_right "La luz ciertamente genera distracción. Sentí que no quería concentrarme en nada más, aunque es difícil recordarlo con exactitud." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3959
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_5e36f1c0:

    # ks neutral "Yeah. It's pretty common for people not to remember large parts of their trances, even if no one tells them to forget."
    ks neutral "Sí. Es bastante común que las personas no recuerden porciones grandes de sus trances, incluso si nadie les dice que lo olviden."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3960
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_7ca1cb27:

    # s annoyed "That is a problem. If we could measure my brain activity during my exposure to the light, that could be helpful. But we have no way of accessing such." with dissolve
    s annoyed "Eso es un problema. Si pudiéramos medir mi actividad cerebral durante mi exposición a la luz, sería de utilidad. Pero eso está fuera de nuestro alcance." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5117
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_d8074e5f:

    # s annoyed_right "Not to mention that my previous exposure to it would compromise our findings." with dissolve
    s annoyed_right "Sin mencionar que mi previa exposición comprometería nuestros hallazgos." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5119
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_e0b535fe:

    # s uniform_handup neutral_right "Perhaps I could use the light on you and gauge your reaction?" with dissolve
    s uniform_handup neutral_right "¿Quizá pueda usar la linterna en ti y medir tu reacción?" with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3964
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_4c69bcef:

    # ks sigh "Uh... I dunno, is that such a good idea?"
    ks sigh "Eh... no lo sé. ¿Será buena idea?"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3965
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_6e0c60a4:

    # ks "I'm the hypnotist here; I feel like I need to be lucid for this."
    ks "Yo soy el hipnotista aquí; siento que necesito estar lúcido para esto."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3966
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_6013f863:

    # "Sayori frowns at my excuse."
    "Sayori frunce el ceño ante mi excusa."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3967
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_55e3f823:

    # s uniform_folded annoyed_right "I feel you just don't want to have done to you what you have done to me... but perhaps you have a point." with dissolve
    s uniform_folded annoyed_right "Yo siento que simplemente no quieres que te ocurra lo que me ocurrió a mí, pero quizá tengas un punto." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5231
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_be0d217d:

    # s neutral "There is something else we could do, but..." with dissolve
    s neutral "Hay algo más que podríamos hacer, pero..." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3969
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_7f80ad8f:

    # ks neutral "But what?"
    ks neutral "¿Pero qué?"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3970
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_a69e9475:

    # s concerned "I feel uncomfortable with involving her, for several reasons." with dissolve
    s concerned "Me siento incómoda involucrándola, por múltiples razones." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3971
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_1ce268ff:

    # ks "Involving her? What are you thinking of?"
    ks "¿Involucrándola? ¿En qué estás pensando?"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5128
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_44d06003:

    # s uniform_handup neutral_right "I am thinking to involve Nozomi in these shenanigans. She may have some time to help us, and I have a feeling she will be open-minded about being hypnotized." with dissolve
    s uniform_handup neutral_right "Estoy pensando en involucrar a Nozomi. Puede que tenga algo de tiempo para ayudarnos, y tengo el presentimiento de que tendrá la mente abierta en cuanto a ser hipnotizada." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3973
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_711836ba:

    # ks surprised "N-Nozomi?! Really? You really think she'll do this for us?" with vpunch
    ks surprised "¡¿N-Nozomi?! ¿En serio? ¿De verdad crees que hará eso por nosotros?" with vpunch

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3975
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_121e4be7:

    # "Sayori sighs, as if she instantly regrets mentioning Nozomi around me..." with dissolve
    "Sayori suspira, como si se arrepintiera internamente de mencionar a Nozomi cerca de mí..." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3976
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_f02771c3:

    # s "Do not get too excited. She would be there for me, not you, and I am not certain she would agree. But I will see if I can convince her."
    s "No te emociones. Estaría ahí por mí, no por ti, y no tengo la certeza de que vaya a acceder. Pero veré si puedo convencerla."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3977
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_1741b2eb:

    # s neutral_right "If she does, perhaps when you entrance her you can impress the importance of remembering every detail. Could you do that?" with dissolve
    s neutral_right "Si acepta, quizá cuando la pongas en trance puedas incitarla a recordarlo todo con lujo de detalle. ¿Crees poder hacer eso?" with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3978
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_150eb21c:

    # ks frown "Y-yeah, I think so."
    ks frown "S-sí, eso creo."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5136
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_f1e20626:

    # s uniform "Good. Then we will meet in my club room tomorrow, hopefully with Nozomi in tow." with dissolve
    s uniform "Bien. Entonces nos reuniremos en mi club mañana. Esperemos que con Nozomi acompañándonos." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3981
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_a3323de5:

    # ks smile "Okay. That's a plan at least."
    ks smile "Muy bien. Al menos es un plan."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5138
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_68e0476e:

    # s neutral "Indeed. Now, I need to go. Cram school awaits." with dissolve
    s neutral "En efecto. Ahora, me tengo que ir. Los cursos nocturnos me esperan." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3984
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_604d1e14:

    # "Sayori closes her eyes and takes a long breath, before trudging over towards the door." with dissolve
    "Sayori cierra los ojos y respira profundo, para luego arrastrarse hacia la puerta." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3985
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_d31a7d5e:

    # s "See you tomorrow."
    s "Nos vemos mañana."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:4049
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_3b198a97:

    # "Even if she seemed happy, I do have to wonder if I should've sent [altname]- er, Sayori, away in her altered state."
    "Aunque parecía feliz, me pregunto si de verdad fue buena idea dejar a [altname]- em, Sayori, irse en su estado alterado."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:4050
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_ea75d518:

    # "That's not something a stage hypnotist does, is it?"
    "No es algo que haga un hipnotista escénico, ¿o sí?"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:4051
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_4a333842:

    # "Still, keeping a big suggestion like that is gonna take some effort on Sayori's part to maintain, so I'm sure she dropped it before she showed up for cram school."
    "Aunque, mantener una sugestión así le debe tomar algo de esfuerzo a Sayori, así que estoy seguro de que la soltó antes de llegar a los cursos nocturnos."

