translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_b69f68be:

    # "Maybe we're both living a dream right now. One neither of us want to wake up from..."
    "Tal vez justo ahora ambos estemos viviendo un sueño. Uno del que ninguno de los dos quiere despertar..."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:4416
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_beee074f:

    # "And if that's the case... why not keep dreaming?"
    "Y si ese es el caso... ¿por qué no seguir soñando?"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:4420
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_6050661a:

    # "Still, though... it'd be proper to bring her out of her post-hypnotic suggestion, much as she seems to like it."
