    # ncg neutral2 "I really was just vaguely curious about trying to hypnotize you yesterday." with dissolve
    ncg neutral2 "Realmente solo tenía un poco de curiosidad por intentar hipnotizarte ayer." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3733
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_5b850095:

    # ncg "But I think you've awakened something in me, Kyou."
    ncg "Pero creo que has despertado algo en mí, Kyou."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3735
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_44fb3f94:

    # ncg "Until now, I never thought I could love being in this position..."
    ncg "Hasta ahora, nunca pensé que podría amar estar en esa posición..."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:4820
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_010f4acf:

    # ncg sad blush2 "As... the one doing the mind controlling." with dissolve
    ncg sad blush2 "Como... la que lleva a cabo el control mental." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3739
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_523ddb88:

    # ncg "I never realized I could love it just as much from this side of things, but with all the thoughts I've been having..."
    ncg "Nunca me di cuenta de que me podía encantar tanto como el otro lado, pero con todos los pensamientos que he estado teniendo..."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3740
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_dbaff26b:

    # "She trails off as her face fills in the blanks for me once again."
    "Se detiene y, una vez más, su rostro me dice lo que no pude escuchar."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3741
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_4a4c01ce:

    # "And after an awkward pause, she quietly clears her throat to talk again."
    "Luego de una incómoda pausa, se aclara silenciosamente la garganta para volver a hablar."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:4826
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_58ddd6c7:

    # ncg stern2 "Not to mention... I seem to have a talent as a hypnotist as well, wouldn't you say?" with dissolve
    ncg stern2 "Sin mencionar... que también parezco tener talento como hipnotista, ¿no te parece?" with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3743
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_8861bd98:

    # ks "I... y-yeah."
    ks "Eh... s-sí."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3745
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_727c9daf:

    # "My agreement makes her smile." with dissolve
    "Mi confirmación la hace sonreír." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3746
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_c37b19ae:

    # ncg "But what about you, Kyou?"
    ncg "Pero ¿qué hay de ti, Kyou?"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3747
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_8ac0bc9a:

    # ks "Huh? What ABOUT me?"
    ks "¿Eh? ¿Qué hay DE mí?"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:4832
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_5f587090:

    # ncg smile2 "I mean, you told me you hadn't thought about being \"excited\" about hypnotizing people the other day." with dissolve
    ncg smile2 "Bueno, el otro día me dijiste que no habías considerado estar \"ansioso\" por hipnotizar gente." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3749
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_646557fe:

    # ncg "But now that you've spent some time under the light for me..."
    ncg "Pero ahora que has pasado algo de tiempo bajo la luz para mí..."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3750
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_e957211f:

    # ncg laugh "How would you feel if I were to hypnotize you again?" with dissolve
    ncg laugh "¿Cómo te sentirías si te hipnotizara otra vez?" with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3751
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_9db0dfa3:

    # "Huh. Wow, I really hadn't thought about that. But now that she mentions it..."
    "Eh. Guau, no me había puesto a pensar en eso. Pero ya que lo menciona."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3753
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_5ab1c63c:

    # "My thoughts suddenly go back to last night, when she..."
    "Mis pensamientos de repente vuelven anoche, cuando..."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3755
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_2c62a43a:

    # "When she hypnotized me... Man, was it really as hot as that?"
    "Cuando me hipnotizó... Cielos, ¿de verdad fue tan ardiente?"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:4841
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_a5378a51:

    # ncg smile2 "Hm?" with dissolve
    ncg smile2 "¿Mm?" with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3757
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_a68d13f7:

    # ks "I'd... I-I'd feel..."
    ks "Me... m-me sentiría..."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3772
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_ae40cd1c:

    # "Yeah... Yeah, I don't know why I'm getting hung up about this."
    "Sí... sí, no sé por qué lo estoy pensando tanto."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3773
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_3f9651e7:

    # ks smile blush "Not gonna lie, it feels really good to think about that."
    ks smile blush "No mentiré, se siente muy bien pensar en eso."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3812
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_c426d4e2:

    # ks "Just... haha, just thinking about waking up to your face after bringing me out of a trance is like..."
    ks "El solo... jaja, el solo pensar en despertar frente a tu rostro al sacarme del trance es como..."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3775
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_22b7f547:

    # "Goddammit, I can feel my cheeks burning up. I can't tell her how much it's turning me on just thinking about it, holy shit!"
    "Maldición, siento que mis mejillas están en llamas. ¡No puedo decirle cuánto me enciende pensar en esto, carajo!"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3776
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_77219c60:

    # ks "Man, I just remember how good it felt waking up to you the last time... Just really nice."
    ks "Cielos, tan solo recuerdo lo bien que se sintió despertar ante ti la última vez... Fue muy lindo."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3779
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_9e0a7c84:

    # ncg laugh "Ahahaha!" with dissolve
    ncg laugh "¡Ajajaja!" with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3780
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_2ae45070:

    # "Nozomi giggles heartily, and I'm just grateful she can't see what's going on in my pants right now."
    "Nozomi ríe fuertemente, y estoy muy agradecido de que no pueda ver lo que ocurre ahora mismo en mis pantalones."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:4855
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_bde74688:

    # ncg smile2 "Mhmhmhm~ You know, it's kinda ironic when you think about it." with dissolve
    ncg smile2 "Jijiji... ¿Sabes?, es algo irónico cuando te pones a pensarlo." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3782
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_5b9fc851:

    # ncg smile_closed "That you started out wanting to hypnotize girls, only for this to happen..." with dissolve
    ncg smile_closed "Que haya comenzado queriendo hipnotizar chicas, solo para que esto pasara..." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:4857
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_25836cea:

    # ncg smile2 "And... speaking of which, there's an idea I wanted to try with you along those lines." with dissolve
    ncg smile2 "Y... hablando de eso, hay una idea que quería probar contigo, relacionada a eso." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3784
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_a18ccbb4:

    # ks "Y-yeah?"
    ks "¿A-ah, sí?"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3785
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_91106ab8:

    # ncg "Yeah. I was thinking we could try a sort of \"turning the tables\" roleplay."
    ncg "Sip. Estaba pensando que podríamos probar alguna clase de juego de rol de \"cambio de tornas\"."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3786
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_0898f50b:

    # ncg smile_closed "I'll use hypnosis to try and convince you that our situations are reversed." with dissolve
    ncg smile_closed "Usaré hipnosis para intentar convencerte de que nuestras situaciones están invertidas." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3787
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_556d9e35:

    # ncg "And then I'll..."
    ncg "Y entonces voy a..."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3788
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_e09d9c9a:

    # ncg laugh "Ahaha, well, then I'll set you straight~" with dissolve
    ncg laugh "Jajaja, pues, entonces voy a ponerte en tu lugar." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:4863
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_3611a349:

    # ncg smile2 "Is that something you'd like to try, Kyou?" with dissolve
    ncg smile2 "¿Es algo que te gustaría probar, Kyou?" with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3797
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_d9fe7095:

    # "I don't know exactly what she's talking about. But if this means I get her to hypnotize me again, why would I refuse?"
    "No sé exactamente de qué está hablando. Pero si eso significa que me va hipnotizar otra vez, ¿por qué me negaría?"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3799
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_10da5183:

    # ncg smile_closed "Wonderful~ Now, if I could have your eyes up here..." with dissolve
    ncg smile_closed "Maravilloso. Ahora, la mirada aquí, por favor..." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3757
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_2eccd780:

    # "My eyes swivel upwards on instinct as I notice the penlight is already in her hand..."
    "Mis ojos se mueven hacia arriba por instinto al notar que la linterna ya se encuentra en su mano..."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3803
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_ad31baad:

    # ncg smile "That's right, Kyou. Up at the light..."
    ncg smile "Eso es, Kyou. Mira bien la luz..."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3808
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_7dd73579:

    # ks neutral noblush "Hm?"
    ks neutral noblush "¿Mm?"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:4886
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_63ad7798:

    # ncg confused2 "Huh? Is that so?" with dissolve
    ncg confused2 "¿Eh? Ya veo." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3813
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_d2b20a0a:

    # "With a grin, I right myself up on my seat as I take a deep breath for what I'm about to do."
    "Con una sonrisa, me enderezo en mi asiento y respiro hondo para lo que estoy a punto de hacer."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3814
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_0e053cc5:

    # ks "Very much so. Do you know what's really been going on tonight, Nozomi?"
    ks "Bastante. ¿Pero sabes qué es lo que realmente ha estado pasando esta noche, Nozomi?"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:4889
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_5177af81:

    # ncg folded stern2 "... Why are you talking like that? What do you mean?" with dissolve
    ncg folded stern2 "... ¿Por qué estás hablando así? ¿A qué te refieres?" with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3816
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_acc0b986:

    # ks smirk "I mean, Nozomi, that while you thought you were hypnotizing me, I've been working a subtle form of hypnosis on you."
    ks smirk "Me refiero, Nozomi, a que mientras creías que estabas hipnotizándome, estuve aplicando un sutil método de hipnosis en ti."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:4891
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_bc33838b:

    # ncg surprised2 "E-ehh?!" with dissolve
    ncg surprised2 "¡¿E-eeh?!" with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3818
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_df85b2a2:

    # "That got her attention, although the surprised look in her eyes quickly gives way to disbelief."
    "Eso captó su atención, aunque su mirada sorprendida pronto da lugar a una de incredulidad."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3819
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_6bfacac0:

    # ncg annoyed "Oh, very funny, Kyou. Do you honestly expect me to fall for something like that?" with dissolve
    ncg annoyed "Oh, muy gracioso, Kyou. ¿De verdad esperas que caiga en algo así?" with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3820
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_9da063a0:

    # "Honestly? I think her reaction right there is already setting herself up for me."
    "Honestamente, creo que esa reacción ya me la está poniendo en bandeja de plata."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3821
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_73d348fe:

    # ks "I DO expect you to fall, Nozomi. You're already halfway there."
    ks "SÍ espero que caigas, Nozomi. Y ya estás a medio camindo."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3822
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_078ab5c3:

    # "And as I speak, I bring a hand up to her face and point a finger at her forehead."
    "Mientras hablo, elevo una mano sobre su rostro y apunto un dedo a su frente."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:4897
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_e8dbb564:

    # ncg lookup2 "W-wait, what are you doing?" with dissolve
    ncg lookup2 "E-espera, ¿qué estás haciendo?" with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3824
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_04e4bf54:

    # ks "I'm not doing anything. You on the other hand found it so very easy to focus on my fingertip, just as you were supposed to."
    ks "No estoy haciendo nada. Tú, por otro lado, estás descubriendo lo fácil que es concentrarte en la punta de mi dedo, tal como se supone que hagas."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3825
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_ece6aa80:

    # ncg "Th-that's..."
    ncg "E-eso..."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3826
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_ad5e0404:

    # "Playing into her imagination like this is just too easy."
    "Jugar así con su imaginación es tan fácil."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3827
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_47921920:

    # ks "That's absolutely right, Nozomi. And it's fine, there's no need to think too deeply about it. You'll find it so much easier to relax and focus up here..."
    ks "Efectivamente, Nozomi. Y descuida, no hace falta pensarlo muy a profundidad. Te será mucho más fácil relajarte y concentrar tu atención aquí..."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3828
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_bb9ea851:

    # "And she's as eager for this as I knew she'd be."
    "Y sabía que moría de ganas de esto."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3829
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_2922cae4:

    # ks smile "That's right. Just watching my fingertip, taking a nice deep breath and letting go. Focusing deeply for me now. Watching my fingertip..."
    ks smile "Eso es. Solo observa mi dedo, inhala profundamente y déjalo salir. Concéntrate profundamente. Observa la punta de mi dedo..."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3830
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_3cf49e9d:

    # "I bring my finger closer to her forehead, ever so slowly, as I see her eyes continue to be drawn to it."
    "Acerco mi dedo a su frente, muy lentamente, viendo que sus ojos siguen atraídos a él."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3831
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_3b987ac4:

    # ks "And what you'll find is going to happen is that as I touch your forehead, your eyes are going to drop closed and you're going to drop deep into trance for me, Nozomi."
    ks "Y lo que ocurrirá es que, cuando toque tu frente, tus ojitos se cerrarán y caerás para mí en un profundo trance, Nozomi."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:4956
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_be1d3338:

    # ks "Yes, just letting it happen... Watching that finger, breathing deep, focusing all your attention here before you..." with dissolve
    ks "Sí, solo deja que ocurra... Observa mi dedo, respira profundo, enfoca aquí toda tu atención y ahora..." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3834
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_dc2756ad:

    # "I then swiftly tap her forehead with a smile."
    "Toco velozmente su dedo con una sonrisa."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3836
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_fa6b373a:

    # ks "Sleep Nozomi." with dissolve
    ks "Duerme, Nozomi." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3837
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_a065fc0c:

    # "And there she goes."
    "Y allí está."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3838
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_72ec90c3:

    # ks "Dropping deeper, conscious thoughts fading, body relaxing... That's right, very good."
    ks "Cae más profundo. Todos tus pensamientos conscientes se desvanecen y tu cuerpo se relaja... Eso es, muy bien."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3839
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_aa7b7ed5:

    # "I just had a feeling that she wanted things to go back to this, with me hypnotizing her."
    "Tenía la sensación de que quería que las cosas volvieran a esto, conmigo hipnotizándola."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3840
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_55982a80:

    # "And for her to prove me right is stirring powerful feelings in me."
    "Y que me haya dado la razón hace que un poderoso sentimiento brote en mi interior."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3841
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_04819296:

    # ks "So now, Nozomi, now that you're in this deep, blissful trance for me, I want you to listen carefully to my voice and what I'm about to say."
    ks "Y ahora, Nozomi, que estás en este profundo y alegre trance, quiero que escuches con cuidado mi voz y lo que estoy a punto de decir."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3842
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_86f562f5:

    # ks "Because from this moment on, until I say you can stop, you may find yourself helplessly obeying anything my voice tells you to do."
    ks "Porque, de ahora en adelante, hasta que diga que puedes parar, descubrirás que no puedes evitar obedecer todo lo que mi voz de dice que hagas."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3843
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_8c8024b3:

    # ks "You might not, if I tell you to do something dangerous or wrong, but you will find it so much easier to obey my words, Nozomi."
    ks "Puede que resistas si te digo que hagas algo malo o peligroso, pero te será mucho más fácil obedecer mis palabras, Nozomi."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3844
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_dc404c95:

    # ks "Do you understand?"
    ks "¿Comprendes?"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3845
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_6c6b393e:

    # ncg sleeptalk "Mmn... I understand." with dissolve
    ncg sleeptalk "Mmn... comprendo." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3846
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_fb400ee2:

    # "Perfect. I wondered if that was going too far for her, even with that little assurance of safety, but it seems she's as game as I thought she'd be."
    "Perfecto. Me preguntaba si estaba yendo muy lejos con ella, aun con esa pequeña garantía de seguridad, pero parece que está tan dispuesta como pensé."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3847
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_e6ff49f7:

    # ks "That's great, Nozomi. So now I'm going to count up to three, and you're going to wake from this trance happy and refreshed."
    ks "Grandioso, Nozomi. Y ahora voy a contar hasta tres, y despertarás de este trance, sintiéndote fresca y contenta."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3848
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_11c0572c:

    # ks "Counting up now... one, two..."
    ks "Contaré ahora... uno, dos..."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3850
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_d8e6d5fa:

    # ks "Three." with dissolve
    ks "Tres." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3859
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_a7fd8cef:

    # ncg "Mmn..."
    ncg "Mmn..."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3860
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_7aabeffd:

    # "I smirk as she comes to. Seems my little stunt worked like a charm."
    "Sonrío mientras ella vuelve en sí. Perece que mi pequeño truco funcionó tan bien como un hechizo."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3861
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_b7441335:

    # ks smirk "Welcome back, Nozomi. I knew you wanted this to happen."
    ks smirk "Bienvenida de vuelta, Nozomi. Sabía que querías que esto pasara."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:4936
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_78b6b4c6:

    # ncg standing stern2 "Hm? Wanted what to happen?" with dissolve
    ncg standing stern2 "¿Mm? ¿Que quería que pasara qué?" with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3863
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_78ecf187:

    # ks "You wanted to be hypnotized."
    ks "Querías ser hipnotizada."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3864
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_9b197a2e:

    # "I'm gonna have some fun with this."
    "Me divertiré mucho con esto."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3866
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_8ad6e63c:

    # ncg "Uh, I'm the hypnotist here, remember?" with dissolve
    ncg "Eh, yo soy la hipnotista aquí, ¿recuerdas?" with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3867
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_80d5966b:

    # ks "So you say, but you just allowed yourself to be hypnotized, didn't you."
    ks "Eso dices tú, pero acabas de permitir que te hipnotizara, ¿no?"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3868
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_e4744776:

    # ks "Maybe you weren't as keen to be the hypnotist as you thought."
    ks "Tal vez no eras tan entusiasta de ser hipnotista como creías."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:4943
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_93811c99:

    # ncg stern2 "Don't be ridiculous." with dissolve
    ncg stern2 "No seas ridículo." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3870
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_dd54201b:

    # ks smile "Why is that ridiculous?"
    ks smile "¿Por qué es eso tan ridículo?"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3871
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_801ec2a1:

    # ncg annoyed "Because I'm not hypnotized, for one!" with dissolve
    ncg annoyed "¡Porque no estoy hipnotizada, eso para empezar!" with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3872
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_8b7d8d93:

    # ks smirk "We'll see about that, Nozomi, especially when you know you won't be able to resist what's coming."
