# game/kyou 4.rpy:4675
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_cc9059d6:

    # s uniform concerned_right "Long story short, it did not." with dissolve
    s uniform concerned_right "Respuesta corta: No." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:4676
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_0df2339e:

    # "I'm confused, and I can only wait for her to continue as she fusses with the food in her lunchbox."
    "Estoy confundido, y no puedo hacer más que esperar a que continúe, viéndola jugar con su comida."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:4677
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_2f1e22bf:

    # s concerned "I took it upon myself to run a little experiment last night." with dissolve
    s concerned "Tomé la iniciativa de hacer un pequeño experimento anoche." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:4678
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_af0894a1:

    # ks neutral "What do you mean?"
    ks neutral "¿A qué te refieres?"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:4679
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_cdfc79bd:

    # s neutral "I wished to test the effects of your post-hypnotic suggestion upon an unwilling mind." with dissolve
    s neutral "Decidí probar los efectos de tu sugestión posthipnótica en una mente indispuesta." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:4680
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_64b6bada:

    # s neutral_right "Do you remember? How I asked if I would be able to negate the effect should I need to?" with dissolve
    s neutral_right "¿Lo recuerdas? ¿Cuando te pregunté si sería capaz de rechazar el efecto si lo necesitaba?" with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:4681
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_693bf1dc:

    # ks "Uh, yeah, I remember."
    ks "Eh, sí, lo recuerdo."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:4683
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_3e1091b7:

    # "There's another pause, as she draws a little yawn out of her mouth before weakly pushing a piece of chicken in there." with dissolve
    "Hace otra pausa, empujando débilmente una pieza de pollo con un pequeño bostezo emanando de su boca." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:4684
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_25e8e8d4:

    # s sleeptalk "..." with dissolve
    s sleeptalk "..." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:4685
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_ea9ae834:

    # ks frown "Uhh, Sayori?"
    ks frown "Eeh, ¿Sayori?"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:4686
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_a5924a54:

    # s sleepy "Hm? Oh, I apologize. I am not used to talking so much during lunch." with dissolve
    s sleepy "¿Mm? Oh, me disculpo. No estoy acostumbrada a hablar tanto durante el almuerzo." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:4687
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_46e86d0c:

    # "... We've barely started talking. But knowing what I know about her, I'm sure she uses this part of the day to nap as well."
    "... Apenas empezamos a hablar. Pero por lo que sé de ella, estoy seguro de que usa este momento del día para tomar siestas."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:4688
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_e6733771:

    # s sleeptalk "But as I was saying, I sought to test the effects of your hypnosis against a deliberate attempt to resist it." with dissolve
    s sleeptalk "Pero, como decía, buscaba probar los efectos de tu hipnosis contra un intento deliberado de resistir." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:4689
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_a86ddb94:

    # ks smirk "From the look of you, I guess you succeeded."
    ks smirk "Por tu aspecto, diría que tuviste éxito."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:4690
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_dddbf1bc:

    # s annoyed_right "..." with dissolve
    s annoyed_right "..." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:4691
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_a4981f42:

    # ks neutral "... What?"
    ks neutral "... ¿Qué?"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:4692
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_900b1d05:

    # s annoyed "I stayed up until my usual time, and as I settled for bed I mentally prepared myself to remain awake." with dissolve
    s annoyed "Me quedé despierta hasta la hora que acostumbro, y al irme a la cama, me preparé mentalmente para permanecer desierta." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:4693
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_94b59609:

    # s uniform_folded "I also set an alarm on my phone for this morning, plugged it into my earphones and set the volume loud just to make sure I would wake up in time to not be late again." with dissolve
    s uniform_folded "Adicionalmente, programé una alarma en mi teléfono para esta mañana, me puse los audífonos y subí el volumen, solo para asegurarme de despertar a tiempo y no llegar tarde otra vez." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:4694
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_e4cb26c6:

    # s annoyed_right "And do you know what happened, Kyou?" with dissolve
    s annoyed_right "¿Y sabes qué pasó, Kyou?" with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:4695
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_345cc149:

    # s "Despite the distractions I wrought upon my mind, the only thing I remember upon resting my head on my pillow was the sound of my phone alarm this morning."
    s "A pesar de las distracciones que forjé en mi mente, lo único que recuerdo tras posar mi cabeza en la almohada es el sonido de la alarma de mi teléfono esta mañana."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:4696
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_329a8545:

    # ks frown "You really don't remember anything else?"
    ks frown "¿En serio no recuerdas nada más?"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:4698
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_9a62eabb:

    # "Sayori bows her head and shakes it quietly as she pokes at her food." with dissolve
    "Sayori inclina la cabeza y la sacude silenciosamente, pellizcando su comida." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:4699
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_63226e3b:

    # s "I do not. So what do you think this tells us?"
    s "Absolutamente nada. ¿Qué crees que esto nos dice?"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:4700
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_eb6152c5:

    # s concerned "Because by my understanding it appears I am as helpless to stop the numbing of my mind as I was to free my arm last night." with dissolve
    s concerned "Porque, según lo que tengo entendido, parece que tengo tan pocas posibilidades de evitar el adormecimiento de mi mente como las tuve de liberar mi brazo anoche." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:4702
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_20fb4bad:

    # s uniform sleepy "I have been unable to explain to myself why that is... But perhaps you have some thoughts on this?" with dissolve
    s uniform sleepy "He sido incapaz de explicarme el porqué... Pero ¿quizá tú tengas alguna opinión en esto?" with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:4708
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_01a18c36:

    # "((Still feeling my way through this convo. Might change it later, but that's all the time I have for now.))"
    "((Sigo formando esta conversación poco a poco. Puede que cambie en el futuro, pero ese es todo el tiempo que tengo por ahora.))"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:4709
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_d852c494:

    # "((Join us next time for more updates!))"
    "((¡Acompáñennos a la próxima para más actualizaciones!))"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:4710
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_0e4cd879:

    # "((To be continued...))"
    "((Continuará...))"

