    extend "ESO qué significa?" with vpunch

# game/kyou 4.rpy:4572
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_964efddc:

    # s uniform concerned_right "No, Kyou, the sleep hypnosis did not wear off." with dissolve
    s uniform concerned_right "No, Kyou, la hipnosis para dormir no perdió el efecto." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:4574
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_282a4f5a:

    # s concerned "Although I had no time to do any further research on hypnosis, I took it upon myself to run an experiment last night." with dissolve
    s concerned "Si bien no tuve tiempo de investigar sobre hipnosis más a fondo, tomé la iniciativa de hacer un experimento anoche." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:4584
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_1253fb9b:

    # "... We've barely even started. But knowing what I know about her, I'm sure she uses this part of the day to nap as well."
    "... Apenas estamos empezando. Pero por lo que sé de ella, apuesto a que también usa esta hora del día para tomar una siesta."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:4585
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_9a3244a6:

    # "Why does she even bother spending lunch with her friends then?"
    "¿Entonces para qué se molesta en pasar el almuerzo con sus amigas?"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:4590
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_78e64b0c:

    # s annoyed "So I stayed up until my usual time, and as I settled for bed I mentally prepared myself to remain awake." with dissolve
    s annoyed "Por lo que esperé hasta mi hora habitual, y mientras me alistaba para ir a la cama, me preparé mentalmente para permanecer despierta." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:4591
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_615ea41e:

    # s uniform_folded "I also set an alarm on my phone for this morning and turned up the volume to ensure I would awaken in time to not be late again." with dissolve
    s uniform_folded "Adicionalmente, puse una alarma en mi teléfono para esta mañana, y subí el volumen para asegurarme de despertar a tiempo y no llegar tarde de nuevo." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:4596
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_9fda5cca:

    # "Sayori bows her head and shakes it quietly as she pokes at her lunch." with dissolve
    "Sayori inclina la cabeza y la sacude silenciosamente, pellizcando su almuerzo." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:4599
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_f3f73667:

    # s uniform neutral_right "I have been unable to explain to myself why that is... But perhaps you have some thoughts you would like to share with me?" with dissolve
    s uniform neutral_right "He sido incapaz de explicarme el porqué... ¿Pero tendrás tú alguna opinión que compartir conmigo?" with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:4600
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_962cfd20:

    # ks frown "Hmm..."
    ks frown "Mmm..."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:4601
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_69f29e95:

    # "Seriously, all I can think of is how she managed to lifehack her way out of a good night's sleep again."
    "En serio, lo único en lo que puedo pensar es que se las ingenió para tener una mala noche de sueño otra vez."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:4602
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_d29880ef:

    # ks sigh "I mean... your body wants what it wants, doesn't it? You must've been exhausted again, so are you really that surprised you fell asleep?"
    ks sigh "Bueno... tu cuerpo quiere lo que quiere, ¿no? De seguro estabas exhausta de nuevo. ¿De verdad te sorprende que te quedaras dormida?"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:4603
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_e6f4df05:

    # s annoyed_right "And? Were you not listening? I had made a conscious effort to remain awake at the time." with dissolve
    s annoyed_right "¿Y? ¿No estabas escuchando? En ese momento hice un esfuerzo consciente por permanecer despierta." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:4604
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_5455d9f0:

    # "A \"conscious effort\" she says..."
    "Un \"esfuerzo consciente\" dice..."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:4605
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_639935f5:

    # s irritated "Besides, it is not as if my body was predisposed to shutting down in the first place. That is why we are having this conversation at all." with dissolve
    s irritated "Además, no es como si mi cuerpo estuviera predispuesto a apagarse en primer lugar. Eso por eso precisamente que estamos teniendo esta conversación." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:4606
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_ff92ce35:

    # ks smirk "But that's the thing isn't it? We can't just think about your conscious desires here."
    ks smirk "Pero ahí está la cosa, ¿no? No podemos solo pensar en tus deseos conscientes."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:4607
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_bf15116d:

    # s annoyed_right "What on earth do you mean by that?" with dissolve
    s annoyed_right "¿Y qué intentas decir con eso?" with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:4608
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_414cf149:

    # ks "What I mean is... your conscious mind might be saying \"stay awake\", but subconsciously? That's a different story."
    ks "Lo que intento decir es que... tu mente consciente podrá decir \"quédate despierta\", pero ¿el subconsciente? Esa es otra historia."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:4609
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_dbaa35e6:

    # ks "Subconsciously you still wanted to shut down, and that's exactly what you did."
    ks "Subconscientemente aún querías apagarte, y eso fue exactamente lo que hiciste."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:4610
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_d8e8abfd:

    # s uniform_folded concerned_right "So... you are saying my subconscious desire was able to override my conscious will?" with dissolve
    s uniform_folded concerned_right "Así que... ¿dices que mi deseo subconsciente fue capaz de anular mi voluntad consciente?" with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:4611
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_43dcbd9f:

    # s sleepy "Does this not contradict what you told me yesterday? That hypnosis cannot force me into doing something I do not wish to do?" with dissolve
    s sleepy "¿Qué eso no contradice lo que me dijiste ayer? ¿Que la hipnosis no puede obligarme a hacer algo que no desee?" with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:4612
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_1d321782:

    # s sleeptalk_concerned "This makes so little sense to me..." with dissolve
    s sleeptalk_concerned "No me parece que tenga mucho sentido..." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:4614
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_1f934c07:

    # "Sayori frowns with concern, having given up trying to eat anything for the moment." with dissolve
    "Sayori frunce el ceño con preocupación, abandonando la idea de comer por el meomento." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:4615
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_ebb01360:

    # ks smile "I mean... okay, I get why it's confusing. But it sounds to me like that's what happened, and there's nothing unusual about it."
    ks smile "Bueno... Muy bien, entiendo por qué estás confundida. Pero a mí me suena a que eso fue lo que pasó, y no tiene nada de inusual."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:4616
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_4d534fa4:

    # s surprised_right "There isn't?" with dissolve
    s surprised_right "¿En serio?" with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:4617
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_306ca773:

    # "I smile and nod at her, hoping I can come off as reassuring again."
    "Le sonrío y afirmo con la cabeza, esperando nuevamente que le parezca reconfortante."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:4618
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_061ef18b:

    # ks "Yeah! When you think about it, it's no different to what happened to you the night before."
    ks "¡Claro! Si lo piensas, no es distinto a lo que te pasó la noche anterior."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:4620
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_0ad7dc9e:

    # ks "After we trained your subconscious with that hypnosis session it just got easier for your subconscious to take over and get you to sleep like you should." with dissolve
    ks "Desde que entrenamos tu subconsciente con esa sesión de hipnosis, le es más fácil asumir el control y hacerte dormir como deberías." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:4621
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_f5b88b26:

    # ks "Not to mention, our subconscious overrides our conscious will all the time. It's just that usually we don't even notice it's happening."
    ks "Sin mencionar que nuestro subconsciente anula nuestra voluntad consciente todo el tiempo. Es solo que normalmente ni siquiera nos damos cuenta."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:4622
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_f39221c9:

    # s neutral "Still though... The very idea that after our short hypnosis session the other day, for it to effect such a change in my subconscious..." with dissolve
    s neutral "De cualquier manera... La mera idea de nuestra corta sesión de hipnosis del otro día haya provocado tales cambios en mi subconsciente..." with dissolve

