# game/kyou 4.rpy:5894
translate spanish Day4_Redemption_a4fd9239:

    # ks sigh "Oh come on, 'Kiko, that's fucking dumb."
    ks sigh "Ay, no jodas, 'Kiko, qué tontería."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5896
translate spanish Day4_Redemption_d91cdae5:

    # "... And yet, just the very fact that I felt comfortable mouthing off to her seems to suggest something that silly actually helped." with dissolve
    "... Y sin embargo, el solo hecho de que me sentí cómodo diciendo una palabrota delante de ella sugiere que dicha tontería sí funcionó." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5897
translate spanish Day4_Redemption_057c3243:

    # "Well alright, if she wants me to treat her like just another classmate then I think I can do that."
