    # ks surprised "Kendo?"
    ks surprised "¿Kendo?"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5904
translate spanish Day4_Redemption_97d4f655:

    # "... You know, now that she mentions it, I can almost imagine her kitted in body armour and wielding a bamboo sword."
    "... ¿Saben? Ahora que lo menciona, casi puedo imaginarla con armadura y blandiendo una espada de bambú."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5905
translate spanish Day4_Redemption_04cff1d0:

    # a laugh "Yeah! It's hard going, and I get my butt whipped a whole bunch, but I enjoy it." with dissolve
    a laugh "¡Sí! Es difícil, y me patearon el trasero muchas veces, pero lo disfruté." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5906
translate spanish Day4_Redemption_d35b71d9:

    # ks smirk "You... enjoy getting your butt whipped?"
