# game/kyou 4.rpy:5927
translate spanish Day4_Redemption_d642d4a8:

    # a smirk "And I don't remember hearing any of this at introduction, Mr. Computers." with dissolve
    a smirk "Y no recuerdo haber oído nada de eso en su presentación, Sr. Computadoras." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:7854
translate spanish Day4_Redemption_c73c77cc:

    # a smirk "And I don't remember hearing about this at introduction, Mr. Computers." with dissolve
    a smirk "Y no recuerdo haber oído nada de eso en su presentación, Sr. Computadoras." with dissolve

