    # a smile_side "I'm into psychology myself. Actually, I want to study to become a therapist when I get into college." with dissolve
    a smile_side "A mí me interesa la psicología. De hecho, quiero estudiarla y volverme terapeuta cuando vaya a la universidad." with dissolve

