    # ks "In fact, the more you look up at this light, finding yourself so automatically drawn to it, the more you may realize how relaxed you are becoming."
    ks "De hecho, entre más miras la luz, sintiendo cómo te atrae, más te darás cuenta de lo relajada que empiezas a sentirte."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:1517
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_9111de24:

    # n "HLLTH! S-s-smoneth... h-hllpth!" with vpunch
    n "¡MYDM! ¡Qu-qu-qu-algn... me-yudm!" with vpunch

# game/kyou 4.rpy:1530
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_5a1d2db5:

    # "Meanwhile her friends keep her firmly gripped in their arms, completely nullifying her attempts to struggle."
    "Mientras tanto, sus amigas la sujetan firmemente entre sus brazos, anulando por completo sus intentos de luchar."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:1532
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_ee1a6c8c:

    # "It sure is a great feeling, knowing everything's going according to plan."
    "Se siente grandioso saber que todo está yendo de acuerdo al plan."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:1535
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_a36759d2:

    # s "I need to keep Nozomi muzzled. I can't do that AND stop him, can I?" with dissolve
    s "¡Debo mantener a Nozomi amordazada! No puedo hacer eso Y detenerlo, ¿o sí?" with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:1550
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_c1c98f8e:

    # ks "It's okay to close your eyes and drop into a deep trance if you need to, Nozomi."
    ks "Está bien cerrar los ojos y caer en un profundo trance si lo necesitas."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:1553
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_6ba9e314:

    # ks "Sleep now."
    ks "Duerme ahora."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:1603
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_20a8eab2:

    # ks "Sayori, Hiroko, you can let go of Nozomi now. Just let yourselves stand nice and straight, becoming more blank. More deep. More willing to listen to my voice."
    ks "Sayori, Hiroko, ya pueden soltar a Nozomi. Las quiero firmemente de pie, vaciando más su mente, yendo más profundo. Listas para escuchar mi voz."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:1606
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_4ea24e65:

    # "Their grip on Nozomi, so rigid until just a second ago, immediately slackens as they take to my words."
    "Su agarre, que hace solo un segundo envolvía tan rígidamente a Nozomi, se afloja de inmediato como dictan mis palabras."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:1607
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_31300338:

    # "And with no one restraining her, Nozomi stands fully upright as well. All thoughts of escape having disappeared from her now dormant mind."
    "Y sin nadie que la restrinja, Nozomi también se yergue. Toda idea sobre escapar ha desaparecido de su soñolienta mente."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:1608
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_1771a9c3:

    # ks "That's right. It feels so wonderful to listen to me. To listen and obey."
    ks "Eso es. Se siente maravilloso escucharme. Escuchar y obedecer."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:1615
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_7d868d9e:

    # "I smirk as the three mindlessly parrot the phrase into my ears while I take Nozomi's hand and nonchalantly swipe her fingers over her phone sensor."
    "Sonriendo al oír a las tres chicas repetir la frase al unísono, tomo la mano de Nozomi y, sin prisa, deslizo sus dedos sobre el sensor de su teléfono. "

# game/kyou 4.rpy:1652
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_d76073ca:

    # ks "Very good, girls. Listen and obey." with dissolve
    ks "Muy bien, chicas. Deben escuchar y obedecer." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:1614
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_7e7ab001:

    # ks smirk "Very good, girls." with dissolve
    ks smirk "Muy bien, chicas." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:1656
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_40664f2f:

    # ks "Now start counting, all of you." with dissolve
    ks "Ahora comiencen a contar." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:1557
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_45cce4d1:

