translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_54f1e069:

    # "And I'm sure my little bit of psychological warfare is helping with that goal in mind."
    "Y estoy seguro de que mi pequeño ataque psicológico ayuda con ese objetivo en mente."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5669
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_0bfa7c0c:

    # ks "Anyway, relax. This won't be as bad as you're thinking. I'm not seriously going to mess with your tennis career, or do anything really bad to you."
    ks "Como sea, relájate. No será tan malo como crees. No me meteré realmente con tu carrera de tenis, ni te haré nada malo."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5670
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_2a9fc2f1:

    # ks "There really is a limit to what hypnosis can do, even if it won't seem like it in your case."
    ks "Sí que hay límites para lo que la hipnosis puede hacer, por más que no lo parezca en tu caso."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5671
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_0966d619:

    # ks "But like I said, maybe your subconscious just wants you to lighten up a bit. You really might find yourself enjoying what we do together, Hiroko."
    ks "Pero como dije, tal vez tu subconsciente simplemente quiera que te sueltes un poco. Puede que incluso disfrutes lo que haremos juntos, Hiroko."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5673
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_e9e8ad5b:

    # h "Nothing's fun with you, you... c-creepy fuckin' asshole." with dissolve
    h "Nada es divertido contigo... b-bicho raro de mierda." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5675
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_53b1ea17:

    # h "I just wanna be done with this hypno shit and go home. C'mon." with dissolve
    h "Solo quiero terminar con este hipnocagadero e irme a casa. Vamos." with dissolve

