    # ks "And that's why, when you wake again, you'll be following some new suggestions of mine."
    ks "Y es por eso que, cuando vuelvas a despertar, seguirás una nueva sugestión, cortesía de mí."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5673
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_d823ee09:

    # h "Nothing's enjoyable with you, you... c-creepy fuckin' asshole." with dissolve
    h "Nada se disfruta contigo... b-bicho raro de mierda." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5693
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_2665aac9:

    # ks "Breathing in. Breathing out. Unclenching your jaw and letting those patterns before your eyes take you deeper..."
    ks "Inhala. Exhala. Afloja esa mandíbula y deja que los patrones que se encuentran ante tus ojos te lleven más profundo..."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5712
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_a55ab687:

    # "Yeah, Hiroko. Very good dropping back into trance like that. It's almost like you were prepared to drop before I even started the induction."
    "Sí, Hiroko. Muy bien. Cayendo de vuelta en trance. Es casi como si hubieras estado lista para ello desde antes de que siquiera empezara la inducción."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5713
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_14975dd6:

    # "You just knew you had to follow along, didn't you? Just \"knew\" that you were helpless to stop yourself dropping back into trance."
    "Simplemente sabías que debías dejarte llevar, ¿no es así? \"Sabías\" que no podrías evitar caer en un profundo trance."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5714
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_a1e267a2:

    # "You're so easy to mess with. But don't worry, I'm going to keep my word."
    "Es muy fácil jugar contigo. Pero no te preocupes, cumpliré con mi palabra."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5722
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_a256ce38:

    # "And now to keep the other half of the little promise I made her..." with dissolve
    "Y ahora cumpliré con la otra mitad de la pequeña promesa que le hice..." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5723
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_65e7da24:

    # ks "Very good, Hiroko. Still listening so closely. Still hypnotized so deeply."
    ks "Muy bien, Hiroko. Sigues escuchando atentamente. Sigues profundamente hipnotizada."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5724
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_d4e54404:

    # ks "That's why you'll find that as I say you'll be compelled to come back and visit me every day after tennis practice..."
    ks "Y eso por eso que, cuando diga que estarás obligada a venir a visitarme todos los días después de la práctica de tenis..."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5725
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_5a5fee3e:

    # ks "... you will, inevitably and irresistibly, find yourself coming to see me at my house, so long as you don't need to be anywhere else after tennis practice."
    ks "... inevitable e irresistiblemente vendrás a mi casa, siempre y cuando no necesites estar en otro lado."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5726
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_93429b2d:

    # ks "And when you arrive, you will be ready to become hypnotized by me again. Do you understand, Hiroko?"
    ks "Y cuando llegues, estarás lista para ser hipnotizada por mí una vez más. ¿Comprendes, Hiroko?"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5728
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_1a2f318f:

    # h "Yeah... I understand..." with dissolve
    h "Seh... Comprendo..." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5730
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_1dd38a54:

    # ks "So what will you do every day after tennis practice?" with dissolve
    ks "Entonces ¿qué harás todos los días después de tu práctica de tenis?" with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5732
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_4a195029:

    # h "Come see you at your house..." with dissolve
    h "Visitarte a tu casa..." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5739
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_a310d078:

    # "And it's as easy as that. After everything that's happened, I'm sure Hiroko will feel like she can't simply avoid me to stop what we're doing." with dissolve
    "Así de fácil. Luego de todo lo que ha pasado, estoy seguro de que Hiroko sentirá que no puede simplemente evitarme y dejar de hacer lo que hacemos." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5735
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_c5a2345e:

    # "But in case she gets any contradictory ideas during the day, I'll give her something else to think about."
    "Pero en caso de que tenga ideas contradictorias durante el día, le daré algo más en qué pensar."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5736
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_07047c58:

    # "Something she can use to remind herself of my hypnotic influence..."
    "Algo que le recordará mi influencia hipnótica..."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5737
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_63768482:

    # ks "That's right, Hiroko. And there's something else that you need to listen to. Something else that you need to act on, while you remain so incredibly suggestible."
    ks "Eso es, Hiroko. Y hay algo más que necesito que escuches. Algo que debes hacer, permaneciendo increíblemente sugestionable."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5738
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_ad9d5b13:

    # ks "Every day, while we're in our classroom at school, you need to keep your phone in your pocket and make sure it's set to vibrate."
    ks "Todos los días, mientras estemos en nuestro salón en la escuela, necesito que guardes tu teléfono en el bolcillo y te asegures de que esté en vibrador."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5739
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_d91f31a5:

    # ks "And every day, while we're in our classroom at school, if you feel your phone vibrate in your pocket, you will feel an incredible urge to yawn."
    ks "Y todos los días, mientras estemos en nuestro salón en la escuela, si sientes que tu teléfono vibra en tu bolcillo, sentirás unas increíbles ganas be bostezar."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5740
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_be20ad65:

    # ks "As you yawn in class, you'll find yourself feeling just a little sleepier than you were before. A little sleepier each and every time you yawn in our class."
    ks "Al bostezar en clase, notarás que sientes un poquito más de sueño que antes. Un poco más de sueño cada vez que bosteces en nuestra clase."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5741
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_7e512b32:

    # ks "And as you feel a little sleepier, you will feel reminded of our times right here, Hiroko. You'll remember how hypnotized and sleepy you get around me."
    ks "Y al sentir ese sueño, recordarás el tiempo que pasamos aquí, Hiroko. Recordarás cuán hipnotizada y soñolienta te sientes junto a mí."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5742
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_e8d5dab0:

    # ks "... Do you understand what you need to do in class now, Hiroko?"
    ks "... ¿Comprendes lo que debes hacer en clase, Hiroko?"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5744
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_0dba2303:

    # h "Y... y-yeah, I understand..." with dissolve
    h "S... s-sí, comprendo..." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5746
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_024b924b:

    # ks "I knew you would, Hiroko. You're taking in my every word, knowing how deeply hypnotized you are. How highly suggestible you are." with dissolve
    ks "Sabía que comprenderías, Hiroko. Estás absorbiendo cada palabra, sabiendo lo profundamente hipnotizada que estás. Lo sugestionable que eres." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5747
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_9a6c72c1:

    # ks "And because you're so hypnotized and so suggestible, you'll understand and accept one more thing."
    ks "Y como estas hipnotizada y eres tan sugestionable, comprenderás y aceptarás una cosa más."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5748
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_c228d9af:

    # ks "You'll accept that the moment you leave our classroom at the end of the day, any feelings of sleepiness you felt will be completely gone."
    ks "Aceptarás que, en el momento en que salgas de nuestro salón al final del día, toda sensación de sueño que hayas sentido desaparecerá por completo."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5749
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_760b6496:

    # ks "You'll be wide awake, fresh and alert for your tennis practice. Completely fresh and alert, do you understand?"
    ks "Estarás despierta, fresca y alerta para tu práctica de tenis. Completamente fresca y alerta, ¿comprendes?"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5751
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_5a8677d9:

    # h "I understand..." with dissolve
