translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_4a3ed514:

    # h "Uh, yeah so Sayori wants to talk to you."
    h "Em, este, Sayori quiere hablar contigo."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:667
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_24ef53ad:

    # "At the mention of her name, I notice the taller of Nozomi's friends has stood up from her desk and stepped over to join us." with dissolve
    "Con la mención de su nombre, noto que la más alta de las amigas de Nozomi se ha levantado de su escritorio para unirse a nosotros." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:718
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_95fd3222:

    # "I speak my thoughts quietly to Hiroko, and she smiles back before whispering conspiratorily." with dissolve
    "Le cuento silenciosamente mis ideas a Hiroko en voz baja, a lo que ella responde con una sonrisa para luego susurrar conspirativamente." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:4258
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_485342a1:

    # "As I look over to where Sayori is sitting by the window, it doesn't seem like she's in any discomfort as homeroom starts."
    "Miro hacia donde Sayori está sentada junto a la ventana, y no parece tener ninguna molestia al comienzo de la jornada."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:4634
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_0a6106d1:

    # "As the clock grinds its way to lunchtime, I look across the room as Sayori gets up and joins her friends."
    "Cuando el reloj marca la hora del almuerzo, miro al frente de la clase y veo a Sayori levantarse para unirse a sus amigas."

