    # n sad "I don't? It feels like everyone knows I'm limping as I walk, or that I'm wearing a little more makeup than usual." with dissolve
    n sad "¿Eso crees? Siento que todos saben que cojeo al caminar, o que estoy usando un poco más de maquillaje de lo normal." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3312
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_1cd2e90a:

    # n front irritated "And god, why did I use different stories for my friends and parents? I TOLD you I'm a terrible liar." with dissolve
    n front irritated "Y, Dios, ¿por qué use historias diferentes para mis amigas y mis padres? Te DIJE que soy una terrible mentirosa." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3317
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_e6ffaecc:

    # "Nozomi sighs once more, then turns her gaze towards the ground by my feet." with dissolve
    "Nozomi suspira una vez más, luego dirige su mirada al suelo junto a mis pies." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3319
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_c931af5c:

    # n sigh "Anyway, we'll talk soon, okay?" with dissolve
    n sigh "En fin, hablaremos pronto, ¿de acuerdo?" with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3321
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_7a04647b:

    # ks sigh "Sure..."
    ks sigh "Claro..."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3329
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_56c6f197:

    # "As Nozomi turns to leave, I think better of trying to stop her a second time."
    "Una vez Nozomi se abre paso a la salida, decido mejor no intentar detenerla por segunda."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3334
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_ce37f1a6:

    # "Still. I can't say I'm not disappointed."
    "Sin embargo, no puedo decir que no estoy decepcionado."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3335
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_948aab40:

    # "It's nice she stopped by at all, but I find myself thinking that this could've been a text."
    "Me alegra que por lo menos haya venido, pero esto bien podría haber sido un texto."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3343
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_8f499cab:

    # n pain "Tstststs..." with dissolve
    n pain "Tstststs..." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3344
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_343eabda:

    # "The sound of Nozomi hissing in pain takes me away from my thoughts."
    "Oír a Nozomi sisear de dolor me distrae de mis pensamientos."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3345
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_ebf8ce6e:

    # "It seems she forgot about the little injury she's carrying by trying to put her shoes back on so quickly."
    "Parece que se le olvidó su pequeña herida por intentar ponerse los zapatos tan rápido."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3347
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_11f8e9d8:

    # ks sigh "H-hey, be careful. The store's not closing that soon, is it?"
    ks sigh "O-oye, ten cuidado. La tienda no cerrará tan pronto, ¿o sí?"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3348
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_5d487d80:

    # n surprised "S-store? But I'm going straight home." with dissolve
    n surprised "¿T-tienda? Pero me voy casa." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3351
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_d9df168f:

    # n shocked "What?" with dissolve
    n shocked "¿Qué?" with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:4682
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_dc4b2569:

    # ks confused "What?"
    ks confused "¿Qué?"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3357
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_3087495b:

    # "Okay, that was pretty weird. She DID say she was getting her glasses fixed, right?"
    "Muy bien, qué extraño. Ella DIJO que mandaría a reparar sus anteojos, ¿no?"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3358
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_b7fdf742:

    # "So why would she..."
    "Entonces, ¿por qué...?"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3359
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_fd45bd7f:

    # ks "HUH?!"
    ks "¡¿EH?!"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3360
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_8c4f320b:

    # "My penlight?! Wasn't it in my pocket?"
    "¡¿Y mi linterna?! ¿Qué no estaba en mi bolsillo?"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3361
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_12265da0:

    # "Am I going fucking crazy, or..."
    "¿Estoy perdiendo la puta cabeza o...?"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3362
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_3b453336:

    # ks frown "Nozomi..."
    ks frown "Nozomi..."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3364
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_951023ea:

    # "I don't want to think this of her, but I gotta face facts."
    "No quiero pensar así de ella, pero debo afrontar los hechos."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3365
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_3aba2706:

    # "She took it. It's the only reason she was here."
    "Ella la tomó. Es la única razón por la que vino."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3368
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_9ec8ad9e:

    # "And she's still not responding to my texts..."
    "Y sigue sin responder a mis mensajes..."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3369
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_926f2c10:

    # "I'm just... fuck, why would she do this to me?"
    "Es que... carajo, ¿por qué me haría esto?"
