# game/kyou 4.rpy:3183
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_a1d550f2:

    # "As I make it to the school entrance, I'm relieved to see Nozomi standing by the gates."
    "Al llegar a la entrada de la escuela, me siento aliviado de ver a Nozomi junto a las puertas."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3184
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_9028cf87:

    # "I approach, and I'm about to greet her when I realize she's talking to someone..."
    "Me acerco, y estoy a punto de saludarla cuando me doy cuenta de que está hablando con alguien..."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3364
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_852db6bc:

    # "I don't want to think this of her. Not of Nozomi."
    "No quiero pensar así de ella. No de Nozomi."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3365
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_06f9dcc0:

    # "She's the nicest girl in school. It's not in her nature to lie, much less to steal."
    "Es la chica más dulce de la escuela. No está en su naturaleza mentir, mucho menos robar."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3366
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_ed7dd9dd:

    # "But why else would she have come here if not to take it from me?"
    "Pero ¿por qué otro motivo habrá venido aquí, sino para quitármela?"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3370
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_118e400c:

    # "I'm just... I don't believe it."
    "Es que... No puedo creerlo."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3371
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_0ac34c3b:

    # "Why would she do this to me?"
    "¿Por qué me haría esto a mí?"

# TODO: Translation updated at 2021-05-19 08:19

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3227
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_6c684e04:

    # "As Nozomi disentangles herself from Hiroko's embrace, she squints towards me, seeming to notice me standing there for the first time before quickly averting her gaze." with dissolve
    "Luego de desatarse de los brazos de Hiroko, echa un vistazo en mi dirección, al parecer dándose cuenta de que estoy aquí, para luego apartar rápidamente la mirada." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3261
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_d1f9a157:

    # "But just as I'm about to, Nozomi lets me go before walking over to the living room couch to take a seat." with dissolve
    "Pero justo cuando estoy a punto de hacerlo, Nozomi me suelta para ir a tomar asiento al sofá de la sala." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3266
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_4cfab432:

    # ncg neutral "I can't stay for very long, I'm afraid." with dissolve
    ncg neutral "No puedo quedarme mucho tiempo, me temo." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3268
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_35830d6a:

    # ks neutral "Oh... Y-yeah, of course."
    ks neutral "Oh... s-sí, por supuesto."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3269
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_b08b109c:

    # ncg "But I was thinking over and over about what happened. I've barely been able to put it out of my head."
    ncg "Pero estuve pensando una y otra vez en lo que pasó. Apenas pude sacármelo de la cabeza."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3270
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_e888302f:

    # ks neutral "Yeah... How are you holding up, anyway?"
    ks neutral "Sí... ¿y cómo lo llevas, a todo esto?"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3273
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_42fbdbeb:

    # "She sighs as she turns her head to look towards the television, staring wistfully into the screen with unfocused eyes." with dissolve
    "Suspira y voltea la cabeza para mirar el televisor, viendo en dirección a la pantalla con la mirada perdida." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3274
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_93f8550f:

    # ncg "Just... one moment I was falling asleep on your couch. The next I was waking up outside your house with cuts and bruises all over."
    ncg "Es que... en un momento me estaba durmiendo en tu sofá. Al siguiente estaba caminando fuera de tu casa llena de cortadas y moretones."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3275
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_7f59f073:

    # ncg neutral "It wasn't until I told my parents that I fell over on the way back from school that it really started to sink in." with dissolve
    ncg neutral "No fue hasta que les dije a mis padres que me tropecé de camino a casa que realmente comencé a asimilarlo." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3276
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_a92ffb28:

    # ncg sad "What happened could've been so much worse, and..." with dissolve
    ncg sad "Lo que ocurrió pudo ser mucho peor, y..." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3277
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_d52c4ace:

    # ncg stern "And I'm sorry, but I have to think it's all your fault!" with dissolve
    ncg stern "Y lo siento, ¡pero he de creer que es todo culpa tuya!" with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3278
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_6fda43da:

    # "My chest tightens as her words hit unpleasantly. And I'm finding it hard to concentrate when she looks at me like that."
    "Siento que el pecho me aprieta al recibir el golpe de sus palabras. Me es difícil concentrarme cuando me mira así."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3279
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_1727a459:

    # ks surprised "W-what, what do you mean?"
    ks surprised "¿Qu-qué? ¿De qué hablas? "

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3280
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_f5bf1d10:

    # "Nozomi impatiently holds up her cheap-looking smartphone and waggles it at me."
    "Nozomi saca inmediatamente ese teléfono barato suyo y lo agita en mi cara."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3281
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_a11ba093:

    # ncg annoyed "Kyou, I went over what you told me while I was in trance yesterday." with dissolve
    ncg annoyed "Kyou, estuve revisando lo que me dijiste mientras estaba en trance ayer." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3282
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_1d4bbf09:

    # ncg "You said I was supposed to \"become exactly what I believe a zombie to be\" when you told me the trigger phrase."
    ncg "Me dijiste que debía \"convertirme exactamente en lo que creyera que un zombi es\" cuando dijeras el ancla."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3286
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_60e70304:

    # "Maybe I could've been more specific, but I had my reasons for phrasing it that way." with dissolve
    "Tal vez pude ser más específico, pero tuve mis razones para elegir esas palabras." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3291
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_aaf0ca90:

    # ks sigh "Yeah... I really didn't think you'd take it that far, after you were so nervous about it before."
    ks sigh "Seh... en serio no pensé que lo llevarías tan lejos con lo nerviosa que estabas antes."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3292
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_1166d068:

    # ncg stern "But I did. And you didn't stop me!" with dissolve
    ncg stern "Pero sí lo hice. ¡Y no me detuviste!" with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3293
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_12bc4ab4:

    # ncg angry "You... you seriously let me wander around with that dangerous stuff in my head!" with dissolve
    ncg angry "Tú... ¡de verdad me dejaste deambulando por ahí con esa cosa peligrosa en la cabeza!" with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3294
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_9120e035:

    # ks surprised "Nozomi, I TRIED to stop you and you wouldn't listen!"
    ks surprised "¡Nozomi, INTENTÉ detenerte y no me escuchabas!"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3295
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_e9cb22e7:

    # ks "And hypnotized or not, you didn't have to do anything you didn't want to! You... know that, right?"
    ks "¡E, hipnotizada o no, no tenías que hacer nada que no quisieras! Eso... eso lo sabes, ¿no?"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3297
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_368ec9b1:

    # "Nozomi snorts." with dissolve
    "Nozomi resopla." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3298
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_67547dcb:

    # ncg "When someone is under the influence of hypnosis, their hypnotist has a responsibility to keep them safe."
    ncg "Cunado alguien está bajo la influencia de la hipnosis, su hipnotista tiene la responsabilidad de mantenerlo a salvo."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3299
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_f151ca32:

    # ncg "I was in your care, under a post-hypnotic suggestion that you planted and... and it really could've been so much worse."
    ncg "Estaba bajo tu cargo, bajo una sugestión posthipnótica que tú implantaste y... y en serio pudo salir mucho peor."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3300
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_da43ee3c:

    # ncg standing angry "YOU know that, right?" with dissolve
    ncg standing angry "Eso TÚ lo sabes, ¿no?" with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3301
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_4eae4f17:

    # ks neutral "Nozomi..."
    ks neutral "Nozomi..."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3302
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_75ec9829:

    # ncg sad "Gosh, if I had fallen differently down your stairs I could've been..." with dissolve
    ncg sad "Dios, si hubiera caído diferente por las escaleras, podría..." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3303
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_cf6d3bf9:

    # "Ugh... yeah, I've tried not to think about that time I was leading Nozomi out of the house."
    "Aj... sí, he tratado de no pensar en ese momento en el   que intentaba sacar a Nozomi de la casa."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3305
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_2cca492c:

    # "I gotta admit, with the way she was behaving she was lucky to get out of there with just a few bruises and a broken pair of glasses." with dissolve
    "Debo admitir que, por como estaba actuando, tuvo suerte de salir de ahí con solo unos pocos moretones y un par de anteojos roto." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3306
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_62d36887:

    # "Even if she doesn't remember it happening, or maybe BECAUSE she doesn't remember... I guess she can't help but imagine what could've happened."
    "Incluso si no recuerda lo que pasó, o tal vez DEBIDO a que no recuerda lo que pasó... supongo que no puede evitar imaginarse lo que pudo haber sucedido."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3307
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_b007915a:

    # "But that still raises the question:"
    "Pero eso aún nos deja con una pregunta:"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3308
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_1faaa323:

    # ks sigh "How did this even happen?"
    ks sigh "¿Cómo ocurrió esto?"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3309
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_335bdfc8:

    # ks "Even if my hypnotic suggestion to you was so dangerous, there's so many things that should've snapped you back to reality."
    ks "Incluso si la sugestión hipnótica que te di era tan peligrosa, hubo tantas cosas que debieron haberte hecho reaccionar."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3310
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_b31569c6:

    # ks "My kicking you, the hit you took when I opened my bedroom door on you, the falling down the stairs..."
    ks "Mi patada, el portazo que recibiste cuando salí de mi habitación, la caída por las escaleras..."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3311
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_4ad23f9c:

    # ks "All of those things should've made maintaining a state of post-hypnotic trance impossible!"
    ks "¡Todas esas cosas debieron hacer que mantener un estado de trance posthipnótico fuera imponsible!"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3313
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_ae85db60:

    # "Nozomi holds her arms around her stomach as she frowns in thought." with dissolve
    "Nozomi se abraza el estómago, frunciendo el ceño pensativamente." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3314
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_7182f944:

    # ncg "{cps=20}You're right. That SHOULD be impossible, but... {/cps}{w=1.0}{nw}"
    ncg "{cps=20}Tienes razón. DEBERÍA ser imposible, pero... {/cps}{w=1.0}{nw}"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3316
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_2e2d7ed1:

    # extend angry "wait, you KICKED ME?!"
    extend angry "¡espera, ¿me PATEASTE?!"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3317
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_87ef8e30:

    # ks surprised "A-ah, you had me on the floor and you were trying to bite my face! And I shouted at you to wake up and you didn't!"
    ks surprised "¡A-ah, me tenías en el suelo y estabas intentando morderme la cara! ¡Y te estaba gritando que despertaras, pero no servía de nada!"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3318
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_54af0b5c:

    # ks "I-I had to do SOMETHING!"
    ks "¡T-tenía que hacer ALGO!"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3319
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_c1aed210:

    # ncg surprised "I... what?" with dissolve
    ncg surprised "¿Que estaba... qué?" with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3322
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_cefdd17a:

    # "Nozomi sighs as she drops her gaze despondently."
    "Nozomi suspira, bajando abatida la mirada."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3323
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_37dbc843:

    # ncg "The more I find out about what happened last night, the more scared I get."
    ncg "Entre más descubro de lo que pasó anoche, más miedo me da."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3324
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_30f51fe3:

    # ncg standing confused "But the fact is whatever you did, it convinced me to hold myself to your ridiculous hypnotic suggestions no matter what happened." with dissolve
    ncg standing confused "Pero el hecho es que, sea lo que haya sido, me convenció de aferrarme a tus ridículas sugestiones hipnóticas sin importar lo que sucediera." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3325
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_8f25a9cc:

    # ncg "It's crazy. I mean, out of all the hypnosis videos I've seen, or when Satoshi hypnotized me, nothing has come close to what I've experienced with you."
    ncg "Es una locura. Digo, de todos los videos de hipnosis que he visto, o cuando Satoshi me hipnotizó, nada se ha comparado a lo que experimenté contigo."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3326
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_e7200301:

    # ncg neutral "What's so wildly different about how you hypnotize me?" with dissolve
    ncg neutral "¿Qué es lo que vuelve tan absurdamente distinto el cómo me hipnotizaste tú?" with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3327
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_5196dd81:

    # ncg "The only answer I have..."
    ncg "La única respuesta que tengo..."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3331
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_7142d339:

    # "She frowns as she pulls out a penlight that was hidden inside the sleeve of her blazer." with dissolve
    "Frunce el ceño sacando una pluma que ocultaba bajo la manga de su chaqueta." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3332
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_d56ed405:

    # ncg "Is this!"
    ncg "¡Es esto!"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3333
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_33d78bd3:

    # "Wait a sec."
    "Un seguno."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3335
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_80dcc6c2:

    # ncg folded annoyed "Kyou, you keep your penlight in your right pants pocket. I've seen you with it a couple of times now; it wasn't hard." with dissolve
    ncg folded annoyed "Kyou, guardas esto en el bolsillo derecho de tu pantalón. Ya te vi con ella un par de veces; no fue difícil." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3846
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_abfde241:

    # ncg "Anyway, I've lied to everyone I care about since last night. I may as well be a thief, too."
    ncg "Como sea. Les mentí a todos los que me importan desde anoche. Ya que estamos, también seré una ladrona."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3344
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_39a1e2e4:

    # "Did she just raise an eyebrow at me?"
    "¿Me acaba de levantar una ceja?"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3345
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_499710de:

    # ncg "I wonder what \"rash\" thing you're expecting me to do with this, Kyou?"
    ncg "Me pregunto qué cosa \"imprudente\" piensas que haré con esto, Kyou."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3346
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_1e5d88a5:

    # ks "W... w-well..."
    ks "P... p-pues..."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3347
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_a69dcee9:

    # ncg stern "As rash as shining this attention-grabbing light over YOUR eyes?" with dissolve
    ncg stern "¿Algo tan imprudente como encender esta luz que captura tan bien la atención en TUS ojos?" with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3348
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_badc4bf0:

    # "There's a soft click as Nozomi presses her thumb into the penlight, illuminating the cushion beside her."
    "Se escucha un suave clic cuando Nozomi presiona la linterna con su pulgar, iluminando el cojín que tiene a su lado."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:3349
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_936a15af:

    # ncg smile "Maybe say a few words while I'm doing it?" with dissolve
    ncg smile "¿Tal vez decir algunas palabras mientras lo hago?" with dissolve

