# game/kyou 4.rpy:857
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_6aeacf4c:

    # "I want to have some more fun with her like this, and I think I can get my points across at the same time..."
    "Quiero divertirme un poco más con ella, y creo que puedo explicarle lo que necesito al mismo tiempo..."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:858
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_780cb808:

    # ks frown "Alright you dopey chick, settle down. There's a lot of things I need to tell you and you need to understand all of it if my plan's gonna work."
    ks frown "Muy bien, niñita boba, ya cálmate. Tengo muchas cosas que decirte y debes entenderlo todo para que mi plan funcione."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:860
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_e87fdccf:

    # ks "Don't fuck this up like you did with Nozomi. This is your last chance." with dissolve
    ks "No la cagues como lo hiciste con Nozomi. Esta es tu última oportunidad." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:862
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_b3771074:

    # h "Ahh..." with dissolve
    h "Aah..." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:863
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_c860a5e2:

    # ks "Do I make myself clear?"
    ks "¿Quedó claro?"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:865
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_284ce0ff:

    # h "T-t-totally! I ain't gonna fuck up again, Kyou! I promise!" with dissolve
    h "¡P-p-por supuesto! ¡No la volveré a cagar! ¡Lo prometo!" with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:866
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_a8305ce1:

    # ks "Yeah, we'll see about that."
    ks "Sí, ya veremos."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:868
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_57f458ff:

    # "I know she'll do anything to make sure my plan goes smoothly. And she won't think any worse of me at all for treating her like dirt." with dissolve
    "Sé que hará lo que sea para asegurarse de que mi plan vaya sin problemas. Y no pensará mal de mí por tratarla como basura." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:869
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_bd70052e:

    # "On the contrary, any negative thought she has about me only makes her love me tenfold."
    "Muy por el contrario, cualquier pensamiento negativo que tenga de mí solo la hace amarme diez veces más."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:870
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_ea39c316:

    # "And just one look at her makes it obvious she's getting turned on bigtime from being talked down to."
    "Y solo basta una mirada para saber cuánto la enciende que le hable con desprecio."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:871
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_0be5eb0a:

    # "So what's the downside here?"
