translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_866ac10c:

    # ks angry "Do you know or not?"
    ks angry "¿Lo sabes o no?"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:877
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_b36078a4:

    # h "H'y-yeah, you were saying I'm your... like, lackey, right?" with dissolve
    h "Sí, estabas diciendo que soy tu... este, lacaya, ¿no?" with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:878
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_a13b9d79:

    # ks frown "Right. And you are, but when you meet with Sayori soon you'll need to fool her that you're not. At least sow a little doubt in her head."
    ks frown "Claro. Y lo eres, pero cuando te encuentres con Sayori, tendrás que hacerle creer que no. Por lo menos sembrar algo de duda en su cabeza."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:880
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_255b102e:

    # ks "First, you need to leave here nice and early. It's only five minutes to the school from here, but you'll be heading out at least twenty minutes before then."
    ks "Primero que nada, tendrás que irte de aquí temprano. La escuela está a solo cinco minutos de aquí, pero saldrás al menos veinte minutos antes."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:885
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_366473d9:

    # "Tapping my foot impatiently, I watch with some amusement as the panicked girl fusses with her socks."
    "Zapateando impacientemente con un pie, veo con regocijo cómo la chica llena de pánico se hace un lío con sus calcetines."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:887
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_2e27b235:

    # "She hops awkwardly back and forth as she pulls them onto her feet one by one, then bends down and hurriedly pulls her sweatbands onto her wrists to finish her ensemble." with dissolve
    "Se los pone un pie a la vez dando torpes saltitos, luego se agacha y coloca con prisa las bandas en sus muñecas para completar el conjunto." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:888
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_181e61e7:

    # "Would've been a lot quicker if I hadn't rushed her."
    "Habría sido mucho más rápido si no la hubiera apresurado."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:889
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_bc99c9aa:

    # ks sigh "What a waste of my time."
    ks sigh "Qué pérdida de tiempo."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:890
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_7a69deea:

    # h cry "S-sorry! Don't be mad at meee!" with dissolve
    h cry "¡B-bueno, pero no te enojeees! ¡Perdón!" with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:891
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_02901f41:

    # "With a shrug I point her towards my bed. For once, it's not like I'm actually upset with her."
    "Me encojo de hombros y luego señalo mi cama. Por una vez, no estoy realmente molesto con ella."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:892
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_a6be7f9e:

    # ks frown "Whatever. Just sit there and listen, there's a lot of ground to cover and I need you ready in time."
    ks frown "Como sea. Solo siéntate ahí y escucha. Hay mucho que explicar y necesito que estés lista esta vez."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:897
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_08ad9c12:

    # "Hiroko obediently sits herself down, looking a little subdued. At least for the time being."
    "Hiroko se sienta obedientemente, luciendo un tanto sumisa. Al menos de momento."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:898
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_0358b91d:

    # "So let's get back to the plan."
    "Muy bien, volvamos al plan."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:899
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_f90b1c52:

    # ks neutral "Now, what were we talking about before you got changed?"
    ks neutral "Bien, ¿de qué estábamos hablando antes de que te cambiaras?"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:901
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_1e40fd78_2:

    # h "Sayori thinks I'm sus~" with dissolve
    h "Que Sayori sospecha de mí." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:903
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_7ea404a4_2:

    # ks "Right. Yeah, even though it's only like, five minutes to school from here you're going to leave ten... no, twenty minutes earlier than that." with dissolve
    ks "Cierto. Sí, a pesar de que la escuela está a unos cinco minutos de aquí, te irás diez... no, veinte minutos antes que eso." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:910
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_53552dde:

    # h "Aww. How come?" with dissolve
    h "Ayy. ¿Por qué?" with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:911
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_67ea1b7b:

    # ks frown "You told me you were training for that big tennis tournament that's supposed to be the most important thing in your life, right?"
    ks frown "Me dijiste que estabas entrenando para ese gran torneo de tenis que se supone que es lo más importante en tu vida, ¿verdad?"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:913
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_90ef3ef5:

    # h "Yeah, that's right~" with dissolve
    h "Sip, es correcto." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:914
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_deb0926a:

    # ks "So we need you looking the part. Keep you in character, maybe throw Sayori off the scent a little bit."
    ks "Pues debes verte como tal. Mantenerte en personaje, tal vez despistar un poco a Sayori."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:918
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_c25770e9:

    # ks frown "So before you head over there you're going for a run. Go around the block a few times and work up a really good sweat."
    ks frown "Así que antes de ir allá, saldrás a correr. Dale un par de vueltas a la manzana y ponte a sudar."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:923
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_a440eefe:

    # ks "When you get there, you're going to be panting and exhausted, and about five minutes late."
    ks "Cuando llegues allá, estarás jadeando y exhausta, y será unos cinco minutos tarde."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:924
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_d6ce01dc:

    # ks "Tell Sayori you're sorry, but you were training so hard that you lost track of time and forgot all about your appointment until just a couple minutes before. Okay?"
    ks "Dile a Sayori que lo sientes, pero que estabas entrenando tan duro que perdiste noción del tiempo y te habías olvidado de la reunión hasta hace unos pocos minutos. ¿De acuerdo?"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:934
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_8dfd9ce8:

    # h "Run around and get sweaty, be late on purpose, pretend it was 'cuz I was training."
    h "Correr hasta sudar, llegar tarde a propósito, fingir que fue porque estaba entrenando."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:927
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_a39acb61:

    # h "Got it~ {font=DejaVuSans.ttf}♥{/font}" with dissolve
    h "Entendido. {font=DejaVuSans.ttf}♥{/font}" with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:928
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_f2e68291:

    # ks "That's right. Next, you and Sayori will get to talking and you'll need to tell her your opinion about what happened between me and Nozomi."
    ks "Es correcto. Después, Sayori y tú hablarán y debes decirle tu opinión de lo que pasó entre Nozomi y yo."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:930
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_cdfb9578:

    # ks "I'll tell you what to say, so you need to listen carefully." with dissolve
    ks "Te diré qué decir, así que escucha con cuidado." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:945
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_9655203e:

    # "Pulling out my phone, I clear my throat as I read the little piece I'd been working on since lunch, while Hiroko straightens up on the bed and appears to focus." with dissolve
    "Sacando mi teléfono, me aclaro la garganta para leer el pequeño texto en el que he estado trabajando desde el almuerzo, mientras que Hiroko se endereza en la cama y parece concentrarse." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:946
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_007b866f:

    # ks "You'll tell her that you're upset about Nozomi and the pain she's in. Of course you are."
    ks "Le dirás que te molesta el dolor de Nozomi. Claro que sí."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:947
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_cabb2005:

    # ks "Hearing it made you so angry that you went to confront me on my way home from school. You demanded I confess to my crimes."
    ks "Escucharlo te hizo enfadar tanto que viniste a enfrentarme de camino a la escuela. Exigiste que confesara mis crímenes."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:948
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_ef86ac88:

    # ks "But as you listened to my side of the story you realized, in your heart of hearts, that I was telling the truth."
    ks "Pero al escuchar mi lado de la historia, te diste cuanta, con toda sinceridad, de que estaba diciendo la verdad."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:949
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_a06937f6:

    # ks "It was hard for you to accept, because you hate my guts and Nozomi's your best friend, but you're a woman who believes in justice."
    ks "Te fue difícil aceptarlo, porque a mí me detestas y Nozomi es tu mejor amiga, pero eres una mujer que cree en la justicia."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:950
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_0316cace:

    # ks "You couldn't just stand idly by and see an innocent man be punished. Even if that man is me."
    ks "No podías quedarte parada y ver cómo un hombre inocente es castigado. Incluso si ese hombre era yo."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:954
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_e73c3994:

    # ks "What happened to Nozomi was a simple but tragic misunderstanding. I never laid a hand on her. I meant her no harm whatsoever."
    ks "Lo que ocurrió con Nozomi fue un simple y trágico malentendido. Nunca le puse una mano encima. No fue mi intención causar ningún daño."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:952
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_cfcbc63e:

    # ks "All that happened in the end was a silly prank involving a cheap penlight and Nozomi took it completely the wrong way."
    ks "Todo sucedió por una tonta broma que involucraba una linterna, y Nozomi lo malinterpretó."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:953
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_9fb48009:

    # ks "Those are the facts as you know them, and Nozomi needs to face reality like you have. You got all that?"
    ks "Esos son los hechos hasta donde tú sabes, y Nozomi debe afrontar la realidad como tú lo hiciste. ¿Tienes todo?"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:962
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_85df3bcb:

    # h "Yeah, I got it!" with dissolve
    h "¡Sí, lo tengo!" with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:963
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_4e89e60b:

    # "I put my phone away and frown at her. It's important for the plan that she gets her act down, and I don't trust that cheery response of hers."
    "Guardo mi teléfono y le frunzo el ceño. Es preciso para el plan que dé una buena actuación, y esa risueña expresión no me da confianza."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:964
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_74e30cc8:

    # ks "You sure? Because when you talk to her you can't behave like you worship the ground I walk on."
    ks "¿Segura? Porque cuando hables con ella no puedes actuar como si adoraras el suelo por el que camino."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:967
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_03e1826a:

    # ks "And as we've established you're not the brightest bulb in the box, are you?" with dissolve
    ks "Y ya establecimos que no eres precisamente la más brillante, ¿o sí?" with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:969
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_24036b60:

    # h "Um, y-yeah, I'm a... a dopey chick like you said...." with dissolve
    h "Em, s-sí, soy una niñita boba, como dijiste..." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:970
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_45de05f2:

    # ks "So I'll explain myself extra carefully so you don't misunderstand."
    ks "Te lo explicaré con extremo cuidado para que lo entiendas bien."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:974
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_18f37c61:

    # ks "You need to channel some of your old bitchy self from before I set you right." with dissolve
    ks "Debes canalizar un poco de tu antiguo y odioso yo de antes de que arreglara." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:975
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_fa05fac7:

    # ks "Pretend you hold a grudge against me, as if being on my side doesn't come naturally to you."
    ks "Finge que me tienes rencor, como si estar de mi lado no se sintiera natural."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:976
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_9fa5e587:

    # ks "Like I said, you need to throw her off just a little. Sow some doubt into her head so she listens to you."
    ks "Como dije, debes despistarla solo un poco. Sembrar algo de duda en su cabeza para que así te escuche."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:977
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_8dcc5da9:

    # ks "So let's see how you do. Imagine you're in the study club room right now and Sayori's standing here instead of me."
    ks "Así que, veamos qué tal lo haces. Imagina que estás en el salón del club de estudio y Sayori está aquí en vez de mí."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:978
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_883da5ea:

    # ks "What will you say to her when she asks why you're supporting me?"
    ks "¿Qué le dirás cuando pregunte por qué me estás apoyando?"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:983
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_b2f5e519:

    # h "H'yeah, okay... It sucks about Nozo. Like, when she was telling us how scared she was of that dude, I thought he'd gone too far this time." with dissolve
    h "Seh, muy bien... Qué feo lo de Nozo. O sea, cuando nos dijo lo asustada que estaba de ese tipo, creí que había ido muy lejos esta vez." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:985
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_2f995e4b:

    # h "I wanted to kill that motherfucker so bad." with dissolve
    h "Moría de ganas de matar a ese hijo de puta." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:994
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_bea42bb8:

    # h "I was so fuckin' angry I skipped practice to go find that asshole so I could give him what for! Make him fess up!" with dissolve
    h "¡Estaba tan encabronada que me salté la práctica de tenis para ir a buscar a ese cabrón y darle su merecido! ¡Hacerlo confesar!" with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:995
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_0b75ecf9:

    # h "But he was telling me his side of things, and..."
    h "Pero el me empezó a contar su versión, y..."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:997
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_d2ac8773:

    # h "Like, fuck, I didn't want to admit it, Sayori, but the dude was talking a lot of sense." with dissolve
    h "O sea, mierda, no quería admitirlo, Sayori, pero lo que decía tenía mucho sentido." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:1006
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_3a1e7fca:

    # h "He's gotta be telling the truth. He ain't the bad guy here, and I'm a... a woman who believes in justice." with dissolve
    h "Tiene que estar diciendo la verdad. Él no es el malo aquí, y yo soy una... una mujer que cree en la justicia." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:1010
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_6c731cb6:

    # h "It don't matter that Nozo's my bestie, and it don't matter that I'm talking about Kyou fuckin' Koyama. I can't just watch her ruin his life like this, y'know?"
    h "No importa que Nozo sea mi mejor amiga, y no importa que esté hablando del puto Kyou Koyama. No puedo verla arruinar así su vida, ¿sabes?"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:1027
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_772a3acf:

    # h "She's gotta stop before she gets him thrown outta school, because... b-because..." with dissolve
    h "Debe detenerse antes de que haga que lo echen de la escuela, porque... p-porque..." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:1029
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_ae590e56:

    # h "Kyou's {nw}" with dissolve
    h "¡Kyou es TO{nw}" with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:1030
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_472d0a96:

    # extend "TOTALLY innocent, Sayori! It's the last fucking thing I ever thought I'd say!" with vpunch
    extend "TALMENTE inocente, Sayori! ¡Y nunca creí que diría eso en mi puta vida!" with vpunch

# game/kyou 4.rpy:1031
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_4bec9013:

    # h "But I believe it with all my heart!"
    h "¡Pero lo creo de todo corazón!"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:1032
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_9a802230:

    # "I smile at her, satisfied."
