    # s "{cps=10}I... {w=1.0}{/cps}{nw}"
    s "{cps=10}Me... {w=1.0}{/cps}{nw}"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5735
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_76392c2e:

    # extend "y-you..."
    extend "t-tú..."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5737
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_1beca12e:

    # "Sayori's eyes lock with mine for a moment before they start to move again, finally registering the fact our classmates are staring and gossiping at the scene she's making." with dissolve
    "Sayori mantiene la mirada fija en mí por un momento y luego empieza a moverse otra vez, finalmente notando a nuestros compañeros que observan la escena." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5738
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_34917d3e:

    # s "H-haah... n-nevermind, it's... it is nothing. Everyone, go back to what you were doing."
    s "A-aah... o-olvídenlo, no es nada. Todos, regresen a lo que estaban haciendo."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5710
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_60589974:

    # "She shudders, and her grip loosens on my uniform while she looks back and forth at the assembled onlookers with their worried faces; their currently unattended lunchboxes at their desks." with dissolve
    "Con un escalofrío, suelta mi uniforme. Su mirada va y viene de los rostros preocupados de los espectadores que han dejado desatendidas sus loncheras." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5711
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_dfaa00cf:

    # ks confused "C'mon, it's fine... everything's fine, see? Nothing to worry about."
    ks confused "Sí, todo bien... todo está bien, ¿ves? Nada de qué preocuparse."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5712
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_dfe64bc4:

    # s "{size=16}So it is lunchtime?{/size}"
    s "{size=16}Entonces, ¿es la hora del almuerzo?{/size}"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5713
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_14a91787:

    # "Is she even listening to me now?"
    "¿Siquiera me está escuchando?"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5714
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_90d2a569:

    # ks "Yeah, it's the start of lunchbreak. Like I said, nothing to worry about."
    ks "Sí, está empezando. Como dije, nada de qué preocuparse."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5716
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_1db70313:

    # "At least she seems to stopped freaking out as she slowly backs away from me..." with dissolve
    "Al menos ya no parece estar envuelta en pánico, y lentamente se aleja de mí..." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5717
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_e55bf580:

    # s alert_concerned_right "You... I am going to join my friends now a-and you..." with dissolve
    s alert_concerned_right "Tú... voy a ir con mis amigas y t-tú..." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5718
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_836f9fcf:

    # s alert_scared_right "Y-you... need to stay away from me. Do you understand?" with dissolve
    s alert_scared_right "T-tú... aléjate de mí. ¿Entendido?" with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5720
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_ce73e1c5:

    # ks surprised "What? Sayori, wait up!" with dissolve
    ks surprised "¿Qué? ¡Sayori, espera!" with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5722
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_e15b4df7:

    # "But Sayori just turns on her heel and flees the classroom without looking back."
    "Pero Sayori simplemente se da la vuelta y huye del salón sin mirar atrás."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5723
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_843b8d6b:

    # "I don't chase her. Instead, I slump back down at my desk, let out a sigh I've been holding and I just..."
    "No la persigo. En vez de eso, me reclino en mi escritorio, suelto un suspiro que había estado guardando y..."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5724
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_aff96f58:

    # "Man, I can't wrap my head around what fucking happened just now."
    "Cielos, no logro asimilar la mierda que acaba de pasar."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5725
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_a0156c08:

    # "The moment I spoke the words to flip her back to normal, it's like she had no awareness of her time acting as \"[alt_name]\" at all."
    "En cuanto dije las palabras para devolverla a la normalidad, fue como si no tuviera consciencia del tiempo que estuvo actuando como \"[alt_name]\"."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5726
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_c69850d1:

    # "It really did feel like she had become a whole different person, with separate memories and everything."
    "En verdad pareciera que se convirtió en una persona completamente diferente, con memorias distintas y todo."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5727
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_ca23e702:

    # "But that's... that's impossible! How in the world did she internalize my suggestions as much as that?"
    "Pero eso... ¡eso es imposible! ¿Cómo podría internalizar mis sugestiones así?"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5729
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_0b143ef4:

    # "Dammit Sayori, I need to know more. I need to talk to you again."
    "Demonios, Sayori, necesito saber más. Tengo que hablar contigo otra vez."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5730
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_e414923f:

    # "You can't just run away from me like this..."
    "No puedes huir de mí, así como así..."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5756
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_eeba23d1:

    # "The lunch period comes and goes, and Sayori returned to her desk without making eye contact."
    "El periodo del almuerzo viene y se va, y Sayori retorna a su escritorio sin hacer contacto visual."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5757
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_41a993f6:

    # "We're supposed to be reviewing some lesson material for our upcoming exams, but I can't concentrate on any of that."
    "Se supone que repasemos algunas lecciones para nuestros próximos exámenes, pero no me puedo concentrar en nada de eso."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5758
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_1b5cf210:

    # "I'm kinda freaking out a bit."
    "Me está poniendo de los nervios."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5759
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_130bdf37:

    # "Hypnosis can't force someone to do things they don't want to do. I know that. Pretty much everything I read on it confirmed that."
    "La hipnosis no puede obligar a alguien a hacer algo que no quiera. Eso lo sé. Todo lo que leo lo confirma."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5760
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_16df0c9e:

    # "But even so, I've also read how it can lower a person's inhibitions. Convince them to maybe go a little further than they meant to."
    "Sin embargo, también leí que puede reducir la inhibición de la gente. Convencerla de tal vez ir un poco más lejos de lo que normalmente haría."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5766
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_5e4cb232:

    # "Sayori was nervous about this whole deal, but she went along with it for my sake."
    "A Sayori la ponía nerviosa todo esto, pero aceptó hacerlo por mí."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5767
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_97dce551:

    # "And yeah, she did come around to it in a big way, more than she ever thought she would."
    "Y sí, vaya que lo hizo en grande, más de lo que jamás imaginé."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5768
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_fa3bfa44:

    # "But it was supposed to be just a little trick for my hypnosis show. And a trick is supposed to end when the show's over."
    "Pero se suponía que fuera un simple truco para mi acto de hipnosis. Y un truco debe terminar cuando termina el espectáculo."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5769
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_c3e52b43:

    # "I REALLY should've told her to go back to normal before I let her leave last night."
    "REALMENTE debí decirle que volviera a la normalidad antes de dejarla ir anoche."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5783
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_0824c957_1:

    # n "Stand!" with dissolve
    n "¡De pie!" with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5784
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_e819aba9_1:

    # n "Bow!"
    n "¡Reverencia!"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5786
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_aea56e41:

    # "But no, I just had to see how far she'd go, didn't I? I just had to know how good of a hypnotist I was." with dissolve
    "Pero no, tenía que ver qué tan lejos iría, ¿no? Tenía que saber lo buen hipnotista que soy." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5787
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_0d22db45:

    # "I'm a fucking idiot. I wasn't thinking about her comfort at all."
    "Soy un puto idiota. No pensé ni un segundo en su comodidad."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5792
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_c2bce0c4:

    # s "Nozomi? Do you have a moment to talk?" with dissolve
    s "¿Nozomi? ¿Tienes un momento para hablar?" with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5793
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_6912931b:

    # "What am I going to do? The school day's over, and I feel nothing but tension between me and Sayori."
    "¿Ahora qué voy a hacer? La jornada escolar terminó, y no siento más que tensión entre Sayori y yo."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5794
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_0a1e1076:

    # n smile_side "Oh, sure, Sayori. What's up?" with dissolve
    n smile_side "Oh, claro, Sayori. ¿Qué ocurre?" with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5795
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_af2adcc2:

    # "She's right there, but she hasn't acknowledged me even once this afternoon."
    "Está justo ahí, pero lleva ignorándome toda la tarde."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5796
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_59fc8d4c:

    # s uniform_handup alert_sleeptalk "Well, it is just... w-well..." with dissolve
    s uniform_handup alert_sleeptalk "Bueno, es que... p-pues..." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5797
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_49d1d6cc:

    # "I could go say something?"
    "¿Podría ir y decir algo?"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5798
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_55336e93:

    # n sad_side "Um... Should we take this someplace else?" with dissolve
    n sad_side "Em... ¿Deberíamos llevar esto a otro lado?" with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5799
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_2b8cb28c:

    # "... No, I'd better leave her be. At least for now."
    "... No, mejor la dejo en paz. Al menos por ahora."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5802
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_49217e9a:

    # "I was only going to make it worse anyway."
    "De todos modos, solo lo empeoraría."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5803
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_96ffcb81:

    # "She just... she just needs some time to clear her head. Work out how she feels."
    "Solo... solo necesita algo de tiempo para aclarar su mente. Pensar en cómo se siente."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5805
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_a9821f80:

    # "Maybe talking to Nozomi will help calm her down?"
    "¿Tal vez hablar con Nozomi la ayude a calmarse?"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5808
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_56cb10b8:

    # "Heading back home, I slump down on my bed as my head continues to spin."
    "Al regresar a casa, me desplomo en la cama y mi cabeza no deja de dar vueltas."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5811
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_6a66123e:

    # "Because yeah, maybe I shouldn't have done something with Sayori that I knew she wasn't fully on board with."
    "Porque sí, tal vez no debí hacer algo con Sayori que sabía que no era exactamente lo que acordamos."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5812
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_e97a14a2:

    # "Maybe I should've ensured she was fine before letting her leave the house last night..."
    "Tal vez debí asegurarme de que estuviera bien antes de dejar que se fuera de la casa anoche."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5813
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_bc6c80b2:

    # "... Or maybe I shouldn't have ruined it by telling the real Sayori to come back when she seemed to be enjoying herself as \"[alt_name]\"?"
    "... ¿O tal vez no debí haberlo arruinado diciéndole a la verdadera Sayori que saliera cuando parecía estarse divirtiendo como \"[alt_name]\"?"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5814
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_c143d6b9:

    # "Seriously, how was I supposed to know she'd take to a suggestion like that so completely? Does that kind of thing even happen?"
    "En serio, ¿cómo iba a saber yo que asimilaría así de bien la sugestión? ¿Algo así siquiera es posible?"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5817
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_3d7e8293:

    # "How was I supposed to know she'd react so strongly to this little light I have in my hand?"
    "¿Cómo iba a saber que reaccionaría tan intensamente a esta lucecita en mi mano?"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5818
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_1c96de8c:

    # "I need answers, and the only person who can give them doesn't want to come near me."
    "Necesito respuestas, y la única persona que puede dármelas no quiere estar cerca de mí."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5820
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_da047c5c:

    # "What am I supposed to do?"
    "¿Qué se supone que haga?"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:7414
translate spanish Day4_Redemption_fc7bb644:

    # "As we head to the front of the classroom, Akiko turns to address me gently."
    " Tras caminar al frente de la clase, Akiko se da la vuelta para dirigirse gentilmente a mí."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:7422
translate spanish Day4_Redemption_e8cc90b6:

    # "I do as she says, forcing myself to stand in front of this class full of disinterested faces as they chatter amongst themselves." with dissolve
    "Hago lo que dice, obligándome a mí mismo a pararme frente a la clase llena de rostros desinteresados que conversan entre ellos." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:7423
translate spanish Day4_Redemption_ae3e78f6:

    # "But it's too much to look any of them in the eye, so I find myself glancing sidewards at Akiko, who stands beside me with a complicated expression on her face."
    "Pero verlos a los ojos es demasiado, así que termino mirando de costado hacia Akiko, quien expresa complicación en su rostro."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:7424
translate spanish Day4_Redemption_63785232:

    # "I mean, yeah... What the hell is there to say about me anyway?"
    "O sea, sí... ¿Qué diablos se puede decir de mí?"

