# game/kyou 4.rpy:5259
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_39a6fdba:

    # s "Good morning, Kyou! Did I scare you?" with dissolve
    s "¡Buenos días, Kyou! ¿Te asusté?" with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5260
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_54e1faf0:

    # "And wow, I am not used to girls approaching me voluntarily let alone jumping out from behind the school gates to surprise me."
    "Y guau, no estoy acostumbrado a que las chicas se me acerquen voluntariamente, mucho menos que salten de detrás de las puertas para sorprenderme."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5262
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_d607ac25:

    # "That's really cute, especially coming from someone like her."
    "Es adorable, sobre todo viniendo de alguien como ella."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5263
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_c759c7c4:

    # ks smile "Ehh, a little maybe. Good morning, Sayori."
    ks smile "Eeeh, un poquito, tal vez. Buenos días, Sayori."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5264
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_b0784155:

    # "It's a nice feeling to start the day with, knowing someone's actually happy to see me around here."
    "Es una sensación agradable para empezar el día: saber que alguien está feliz de verme por aquí."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5272
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_e37b4f01:

    # ks confused "{cps=15}W-well, yeah because it's- {/cps}{w=0.5}{nw}"
    ks confused "{cps=15}B-bueno, sí, porque es- {/cps}{w=0.5}{nw}"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5727
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_742c900b:

    # "At least she seems to have stopped freaking out as she slowly backs away from me..." with dissolve
    "Al menos ya no parece estar envuelta en pánico, y lentamente se aleja de mí..." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5817
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_ac91480c:

    # "Maybe talking to a friend like Nozomi will help calm her down?"
    "¿Tal vez hablar con una amiga como Nozomi la ayude a calmarse?"
