# game/kyou 4.rpy:4758
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_d661bdf4:

    # "As I follow Nozomi's voice to the living room and get seated, I gingerly hold out a hand to try and get a feel for where exactly she is."
    "Siguiendo la voz de Nozomi hasta la sala, pongo cautelosamente una mano delante para intentar sentir exactamente dónde se encuentra."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5018
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_4703d0a3:

    # n "Gosh, you want me to do... t-that?"
    n "Cielos, ¿quieres que haga... e-eso?"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5019
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_73da8942:

    # "Nozomi's reaction gives me pause, and as I look down on my half-naked self I can't help my cheeks from burning as red as hers."
    "La reacción de Nozomi me hace dar una pausa, y al mirar mi cuerpo semidesnudo, no puedo evitar que mis mejillas enrojezcan tanto como las suyas."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5020
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_98a4f4b0:

    # ks sigh "Uhhh... s-sorry, maybe I was out of line trying to make you do something like this."
    ks sigh "Eeeh... l-lo siento, tal vez me pasé de la raya intentando que hagas algo así."

