    # s alert_annoyed_right "Oh, do tell me. What \"good\" explanation could you possibly have for me?" with dissolve
    s alert_annoyed_right "Oh, ilústrame. Dime, ¿cuál es la \"buena\" explicación que tienes para ofrecerme?" with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5672
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_c40ff652:

    # "... It's no good. Under her hardened gaze I know no explanation I can give will calm her."
    "... Es inútil. Bajo su dura mirada, sé que no hay explicación que pueda calmarla."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5673
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_2797dc8d:

    # "I knew it wasn't right to let her leave the house thinking she was the person I selfishly constructed for my own amusement."
    "Sabía que no era buena idea dejarla salir de la casa pensando que era la persona que construí de forma egoísta para mi propia diversión."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5675
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_016ce7ae:

    # "And it sure wasn't right to let her go on living her life as \"[alt_name]\" for an entire day, talking to her family and friends and classmates like she was some happy, carefree girl with a crush." with dissolve
    "Y definitivamente no estuvo bien dejarla vivir su vida como \"[alt_name]\" por un día entero, hablando con su familia y amigos y compañeros como una chica alegre, despreocupada y enamorada." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5676
