    # n sleeptalk_concerned "I want to... become his girlfriend?" with dissolve
    n sleeptalk_concerned "Quiero... ¿ser su novia?" with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:1623
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_90ad4c73:

    # "I know it's a lie. I know Nozomi doesn't feel anything for me, no matter how hard I tried for her."
    "Sé que es mentira. Sé que Nozomi no siente nada por mí, sin importar cuánto esfuerzo haya invertido por ella."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:1625
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_2c4436d7:

    # h "Yes... ever since you... talked to him alone at cleaning... you realized you had... feelings for him, Nozomi." with dissolve
    h "Sí... desde que hablaste... con él a solas en la limpieza... te diste cuenta de... lo que sentías por él, Nozomi." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:1626
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_45e560e4:

    # "But it doesn't matter anymore. Not when I can correct her. Reprogram her..."
    "Pero eso ya no importa. No cuando puedo corregirla. Reprogramarla..."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:1627
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_5f619f7e:

    # h "There is no denying how... you really feel about Kyou Koyama. You love and accept him... no matter what."
    h "No puedes negar... lo que realmente sientes por Kyou Koyama. Lo amas y lo aceptas... sin importar qué."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:1628
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_15f2ab47:

    # "Make her mine..."
    "Hacerla mía..."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:1629
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_b0812978:

    # h "So embrace that feeling in your heart... and accept it completely... as though you have never... been more sure about anything... in your life."
    h "Así que deja que ese sentimiento envuelva tu corazón... y acéptalo completamente... como si nunca hubieras... estado más segura de nada... en tu vida."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:1630
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_3a12f9ea:

    # h "Do you know your truth now?"
    h "¿Ahora sabes tu realidad?"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:1634
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_38a23a9c:

    # n sleeptalk_concerned "Th- that I... want to be Kyou Koyama's girlfriend..." with dissolve
    n sleeptalk_concerned "Qu- que quiero... ser la novia de Kyou Koyama..." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:1636
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_c6fe7762:

    # h "That's right... So when your conciousness returns... you will go to him, and confess your love..." with dissolve
    h "Así es... Así que cuando regrese tu consciencia... irás con él, y le declararás tu amor..." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:1637
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_3149938b:

    # h "You will beg him to be your boyfriend. You will not be content... until you know you are in a relationship with him..."
    h "Le rogarás que sea tu novio. No estarás satisfecha... hasta que sepas que estás en una relación con él..."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:1638
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_2428b7d0:

    # h "Do you understand what you must do?"
    h "¿Entiendes lo que debes hacer?"

