    # "The very sight of her excites me too much to even try to act surprised at her sudden arrival like I'd planned."
    "El solo verla me emociona tanto que ni siquiera intento actuar sorprendido de su repentida llegada como planeé."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:1658
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_d25e32ab:

    # n sleepy "Kyou... please go out with me!" with dissolve
    n sleepy "Kyou... ¡por favor sal conmigo!" with dissolve

