translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_7c31094f:

    # "The look on her face. God, I've never felt more attracted to her than I do now."
    "La mirada en su rostro. Dios, jamás me he sentido más atraído a ella que ahora mismo."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:1662
translate spanish Day4_Villain_Kyou_c234599e:

    # n concerned "All those times you tried to talk to me... you even tried to tell me when we... w-when we were cleaning the classroom before..." with dissolve
    n concerned "Todas esas veces que intentaste hablar conmigo... incluso intentaste decirme cuando... c-cuando estábamos limpiando el salón... " with dissolve

