# game/kyou 4.rpy:2052
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_48cd23b4:

    # "The next morning begins with a sense of anticipation as I begin my walk to school."
    "La mañana siguiente comienza con un sentido de anticipación al caminar a la escuela."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2054
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_05a4c43b:

    # "I shouldn't expect much. As committed to change as Akiko seemed to be, she's hardly going to transform overnight."
    "No debería esperar mucho. Por comprometida a cambiar que parecía Akiko, dudo que vaya a transformarse de la noche a la mañana."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2055
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_238fd698:

    # "But right now, just the very idea that she's doing it at all is exciting to me."
    "Pero ahora mismo, tan solo la idea de que vaya a hacerlo me pone emocionado."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2057
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_5e512268:

    # "It's an excitement that'll have to carry me through the morning as I settle into my desk for the lessons ahead."
    "Es una emoción que tendré que llevar conmigo toda la mañana, acomodándome en mi escritorio y preparándome para las lecciones."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2061
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_7f3a04b9:

    # "Huh, Nozomi came in on time today. That's... good."
    "Oh, Nozomi llegó a tiempo hoy. Eso es... bueno."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2062
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_ef913fe5:

    # "Ugh, no, I can't stare. Not anymore."
    "Aj, no, no puedo quedármele viendo. Ya no más."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2063
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_078aa882:

    # "Just got to keep my head down and try to shut her out. Think of Akiko."
    "Tengo que mantener la cabeza baja e intentar olvidarme de ella. Pensar en Akiko."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2067
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_2307daa9:

    # "Or rather... think of her as Nozomi."
    "O más bien... pensar en ella como Nozomi."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2068
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_357039bf:

    # "Maybe the real Akiko can't live up to perfection, but when she's just in my imagination now, she can be perfect."
    "Tal vez la verdadera Akiko no puede estar a la altura de la perfección, pero cuando está solo en mi imaginación, puede ser perfecta."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2069
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_04fe002b:

    # "This is the girl I'm interested in. The girl sitting across from me may as well not exist."
    "Esta es la chica en la que estoy interesado. La chica sentada por allá bien podría no existir."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2070
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_d6ffc848:

    # "That's the mental image I want to focus on. At least until lunch, anyway."
    "Esa es la imagen mental en la que quiero concentrarme. Al menos hasta el almuerzo."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2073
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_639c7c78:

    # "When lunch does eventually come around, I take my time to get up from my desk."
    "Y cuando el almuerzo eventualmente llega, me tomo mi tiempo para levantarme de mi escritorio."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2079
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_bf6a17e1:

    # s "Well then, shall we go?" with dissolve
    s "Entonces, ¿andando?" with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2080
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_3c85d1fc:

    # "Better if I let these girls go ahead of me."
    "Será mejor dejar que estas chicas salgan antes que yo."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2081
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_74c57baf:

    # n sad_closed "Yeah, let's get out of here." with dissolve
    n sad_closed "Sí, salgamos de aquí." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2088
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_5c8e2e27:

    # "I can feel that one's eyes linger on me before she leaves."
    "Puedo sentir sus ojos quedarse unos momentos sobre mí antes de irse."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2089
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_d9cfb692:

    # "She rejected me. But I can tell she's still thinking about me."
    "Me rechazo. Pero puedo notar que sigue pensando sobre mí."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2090
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_3a07b758:

    # "But I don't want to think about her. Not anymore."
    "Pero yo no quiero pensar en ella. Ya no más."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2092
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_60fe84d0:

    # "Once they're gone, I make my way slowly towards the student council room, lunch in hand, before knocking on the door."
    "Una vez se van, me dirijo lentamente hacia la sala del consejo estudiantil, con mi almuerzo en mano, para luego tocar la puerta."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2093
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_874431af:

    # ks confused "N-... Akiko? Are you in there?"
    ks confused "¿N-... Akiko? ¿Estás ahí?"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2094
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_5b0b6ddf:

    # a "Ah, Kyou! Door's open~"
    a "¡Ah, Kyou! La puerta está abierta."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2098
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_8318b1aa:

    # "And I brace myself for the sight that is about to greet me..."
    "Y me preparo para lo que estoy a punto de ver..."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2106
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_e5a4da03:

    # a happy "What do you think? Pretty cute, huh?" with dissolve
    a happy "¿Qué opinas? Muy lindo, ¿no?" with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2105
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_25f93419:

    # "(( AUTHOR'S NOTE: And I'm so sorry to have to do this, but this is where I'll have to leave this for now ^^; ))"
    "(( NOTA DE LA AUTORA: Y lamento mucho tener que hacer esto, pero aquí lo tendré que dejar por ahora. ^^;"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2106
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_e52fd183:

    # "(( Next month will see more of Akiko's transformation as Kyou continues to put his nefarious plan into motion. ))"
    "(( El próximo mes vendrá con más transformaciones para Akiko, mientras Kyou continúa intentando poner su macabro plan en marcha. ))"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2107
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_a08c132c:

    # "{size=30}TO BE CONTINUED...{/size}"
    "{size=30}CONTINUARÁ...{/size}"

# TODO: Translation updated at 2025-03-01 19:16

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2090
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_b0d82b51:

    # "But I don't want to think about her. I can't."
    "Pero no quiero pensar en ella. No puedo."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2091
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_1f8a4b4b:

    # "Not anymore."
    "Ya no más."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2107
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_15f2de84:

    # "The door seems to swing closed by itself while I just stand there motionless for a moment."
    "La puerta parece cerrarse por sí sola mientras yo me paro inmóvil por un momento."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2108
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_727954a4:

    # "The girl I'm seeing now is... well..."
    "La chica a la que estoy viendo ahora... puesto..."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2109
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_cae55c75:

    # a uniform_up2 armband_up smile_side blush "I, um... spoke with Nozomi yesterday. Student council business." with dissolve
    a uniform_up2 armband_up smile_side blush "Este, em... hablé con Nozomi ayer. Asuntos del consejo estudiantil." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2112
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_4db1bfad:

    # "I find myself starting to walk in a slow circle around our student council president. And Akiko, for her part, shyly runs a hand through her hair as I openly check her out."
    "Empiezo a caminar lentamente alrededor de la presidenta del consejo estudiantil. Y Akiko, por su parte, pasa tímidamente una mano por su cabello mientras la examino."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2113
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_0a092f4b:

    # ks confused "You did, huh?"
    ks confused "Ya veo."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2114
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_825a0bb7:

    # a uniform_down2 armband_down happy "Yup! And she was looking as great as ever; her hair really is to die for~ {font=DejaVuSans.ttf}♥{/font}" with dissolve
    a uniform_down2 armband_down happy "¡Sipi! Y lucía genial como siempre; su cabello de verdad está para morirse. {font=DejaVuSans.ttf}♥{/font}" with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2115
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_f3cbddc2:

    # ks "What did you guys talk about?"
    ks "¿Y de qué hablaron?"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2116
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_a96d2ceb:

    # a smile "Like I said, student council business. She's in charge of making sure everyone in your class gets their applications for the culture festival submitted in time." with dissolve
    a smile "Como dije, asuntos del consejo estudiantil. Está a cargo de asegurarse de que todos en su clase envíen sus aplicaciones para el festival cultural a tiempo." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2117
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_9e4818f9:

    # a neutral -blush "The deadline's next week, so I wanted to check in with everybody." with dissolve
    a neutral -blush "La fecha límite es la próxima semana, así que quería saber cómo iban todos." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2118
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_98c56120:

    # "I'm no expert on any of this stuff, but it's obvious even to me that she's put a ton of effort into her hair since we last spoke."
    "No soy experto en estas cosas, pero es obvio incluso para mí que puso mucho esfuerzo en su cabello desde la última vez que nos vimos."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2119
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_8770dec8:

    # a smile "She mentioned you, actually. Said you apologized to her?" with dissolve
    a smile "Te mencionó, de hecho. Me dijo que te disculpaste con ella." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2120
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_9bf86320:

    # ks "Oh... yeah, I did."
    ks "Oh... sí, eso hice."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2121
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_795807bf:

    # a happy "That's great, Kyou! Not that I think you had anything to apologize for after our talk, but sometimes you just have to swallow your pride a little to defuse a bad situation." with dissolve
    a happy "¡Eso es grandioso, Kyou! No es que crea que tuvieras algo de que disculparte después de nuestra charla, pero a veces debes tragarte tu orgullo para calmar una situación." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2122
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_a55d2649:

    # "Her straight bob from before seems almost totally transformed."
    "Su peinado recto casi parece haberse transformado por completo."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2123
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_151dec1a:

    # a uniform2 armband smile "I don't think she's ready to move on, and she has no idea why I'm so committed to talking with you, but I suppose she just needs a little more time." with dissolve
    a uniform2 armband smile "No sé si esté lista para dejar las cosas atrás, y no entiende mi convicción de hablar contigo, pero supongo que solo necesita más tiempo." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2124
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_677d1572:

    # "She even got Nozomi's bangs right from the looks of it."
    "Incluso tiene el flequillo de Nozomi, por lo que veo."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2125
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_2afee267:

    # a sigh "And wow, I have no idea what she'd think if she knew I was checking her out so I could copy her hair!" with dissolve
    a sigh "¡Y guau, no tengo idea de qué pensaría si supiera que la estoy viendo de cerca para copiarle el cabello!" with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2126
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_865989fe:

    # a sad_side "And when that wasn't enough, I looked at some of her old photos she put on her socials when I got home." with dissolve
    a sad_side "Y cuando no me fue suficiente, me puse a ver algunas de sus viejas fotos en redes sociales cuando llegué a mi casa." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2127
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_ae6aa24f:

    # ks neutral "Ah... yeah, she doesn't really post much anymore, huh."
    ks neutral "Ah... sí, no publica mucho últimamente, ¿eh?"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2128
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_2d611989:

    # "If Nozomi had her hair cut short and dyed it black, I imagine it'd look very much like this."
    "Si Nozomi tuviera el cabello corto y se lo tiñera de negro, imagino que se vería justo así."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2129
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_9d63fc05:

    # a confused "Yeah. It's interesting how her look's hardly changed since she was a first year. She wears glasses now, but besides that?" with dissolve
    a confused "Sí, es interesante cómo apenas ha cambiado desde primer año. Ahora usa antejos, pero poco más." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2130
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_5edce7e6:

    # a laugh "Well, I guess there's no improving on perfection~ {font=DejaVuSans.ttf}♥{/font}" with dissolve
    a laugh "Bueno, supongo que no se puede mejorar la perfección. {font=DejaVuSans.ttf}♥{/font}" with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2132
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_76a0d812:

    # "And as I come to a stop in front of Akiko and she awkwardly strikes a pose, I have to think she very much believes the same." with dissolve
    "Y cuando me detengo frente a ella, tímidamente hace una pose, y he de creer que ella opina lo mismo." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2133
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_6efb9e5b:

    # a "Sooo? How is it?"
    a "¿Y bieeen? ¿Qué tal está?"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2134
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_afebf695:

    # ks smile "It's... did you do this all by yourself?"
    ks smile "Está... ¿lo hiciste todo tú sola?"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2136
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_38e7f319:

    # "Akiko lets out an embarrassed chuckle and nods." with dissolve
    "Akiko suelta una apenada risita y asiente." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2137
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_9a96edc9:

    # a "Ahahah, yup! You won't believe the work I had to put in to get it just right."
    a "¡Ajaja, sipi! No creerás el trabajo que tuve que invertir para que quedara bien."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2138
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_be418757:

    # a surprised "But I was so... wow, I can't believe how DRIVEN I was last night! I've never felt so motivated to do anything in my entire life!" with dissolve
    a surprised "Pero estaba tan... ¡guau, no puedo creer lo DETERMINADA que estaba anoche! ¡Nunca me había sentido tan motivada al hacer algo en mi vida!" with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2139
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_db1bfa56:

    # a sad "And... a-and it's good, right? I've gotten comments about my hair all morning, but you're the only one who knows why I did it. What it's for..." with dissolve
    a sad "Y... y-y luce bien, ¿verdad? He recibido comentarios sobre mi cabello toda la mañana, pero tú eres el único que sabe por qué lo hice. Para qué es..." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2140
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_4f8e9c20:

    # a uniform_down2 armband_down sad_side "And now I've gone through with it, I can't stop thinking about... well..." with dissolve
    a uniform_down2 armband_down sad_side "Y ahora que lo hice, no puedo dejar de pensar en... bueno..." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2141
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_da7a8ca6:

    # a sigh -blush "Nozomi's so wonderful, and here I am trying to imitate her. How disrespectful is that?" with dissolve
    a sigh -blush "Nozomi es tan maravillosa, y yo aquí estoy tratando de imitarla. ¿No te parece muy irrespetuoso?" with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2142
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_3845727d:

    # a sad_side "I'm such a phony." with dissolve
    a sad_side "Soy una farsante." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2143
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_fdc6bfbd:

    # a confused "But I still want to do it more?! It feels so wrong, like I'm giving up parts of myself to chase a shadow. And I still want to do it." with dissolve
    a confused "¡Pero ¿aún quiero seguir haciéndolo?! Se siente incorrecto, como si abandonara partes de mi ser por perseguir una sombra. Y aun así quiero hacerlo." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2145
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_1bf25b60:

    # a sad_side "Even though I know I'm not her. And I'll never be her, no matter how hard I try to change myself." with dissolve
    a sad_side "Incluso sabiendo que no soy ella. Y que nunca seré ella, sin importar cuánto intente cambiarme." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2146
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_46ee0513:

    # a sad "Do you... do you even like it? You still haven't said anything." with dissolve
    a sad "¿Siquiera... siquiera te gusta? Aún no me has dicho nada." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2147
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_c4243a7a:

    # "Oh damn, she's right. I've been so fascinated about the changes she's made, both physically and mentally, that I forgot to tell her what I actually thought about any of it."
    "Oh, diablos, tiene razón. Estaba tan fascinado por los cambios que hizo, tanto física como mentalmente, que olvidé decirle lo que pensaba realmente."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2148
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_e152af19:

    # a uniform2 armband pain "You hate it, don't you!" with dissolve
    a uniform2 armband pain "¡Te parece horrible, verdad!" with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2149
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_e30f09ad:

    # ks surprised "Oh, no! Akiko, nothing could be further from the truth!"
    ks surprised "¡Oh, no! ¡Akiko, nada más lejos de la realidad!"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2150
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_92dccebf:

    # "This is the path I wanted her to take. And she's already surpassed my meagre expectations."
    "Este es el camino que quería que tomara. Y ya superó mis escasas expectativas."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2151
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_3ce53af1:

    # "I guess the doubts she's having are understandable, as driven as she is to match Nozomi's perfection. But all she needs is a little more encouragement from yours truly."
    "Supongo que las dudas que está teniendo son entendibles, por motivada que esté por igualar la perfección de Nozomi. Pero solo necesita algo de aliento de un servidor."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2153
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_9bc1ed14:

    # ks smile "I really like what you've done with your hair, Akiko. I think it was worth the effort you put in." with dissolve
    ks smile "De verdad me gusta lo que hiciste con tu cabello, Akiko. Creo que valió la pena el esfuerzo que le invertiste." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2154
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_40857186:

    # "I mean, she's still no Nozomi. But she does look prettier like this, I have to admit."
    "Digo, sigue sin ser Nozomi. Pero sí está más bonita así, debo admitir."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2155
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_d1e58890:

    # ks "And you're not a phony for wanting to make a change. Don't be so hard on yourself."
    ks "Y no eres una farsante por querer hacer un cambio. No seas tan dura contigo."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2156
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_c4584704:

    # "Now if I could get her to grow her hair out some more. Get her to dye it..."
    "Ahora, si pudiera hacer que se dejara crecer el cabello un poco más. Lograr que se lo tiña..."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2157
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_fca1a6ad:

    # ks "Feeling guilty about copying her just shows that you care; that you're kind and consider other people. That's Nozomi all over."
    ks "Sentirte culpable por copiarla es muestra de que te importa; que eres gentil y considerada con los demás. Tal como Nozomi."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2158
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_04c7843b:

    # "Well, that'll come in time. For now, I have other priorities."
    "Bueno, ya habrá tiempo para eso. Por ahora, tengo otras prioridades."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2159
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_1e43e510:

    # a uniform_down2 armband_down sleeptalk "Nozomi really brings out the best in us, doesn't she. I barely even know her, but she's become such an inspiration to me." with dissolve
    a uniform_down2 armband_down sleeptalk "Nozomi realmente saca lo mejor de nosotros, ¿no? Apenas la conozco, pero se ha vuelto toda una inspiración para mí." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2160
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_bd4ca1e2:

    # a neutral_side "If only we had been classmates. It feels like all the good folks wound up in 3-B." with dissolve
    a neutral_side "Si tan solo estuviéramos en la misma clase. Parece que los mejores alumnos terminan en el 3-B." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2161
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_dc7c8586:

    # a confused "There's Nozomi, of course. Then there's Sayori, you, Shiro..." with dissolve
    a confused "Está Nozomi, por supuesto. Y también Sayori, tú, Shiro... " with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2163
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_d9e3c376:

    # "Akiko sighs." with dissolve
    "Akiko suspira." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2164
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_fdf6222e:

    # a "Haaah... Sorry, there's that jealousy again."
    a "Aaah... Lo siento, ahí van mis celos otra vez."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2165
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_e9128c1d:

    # a neutral "Being in 3-C isn't terrible, I suppose. There's just this one couple who've been at each other's throats lately, and it's driving everyone nuts." with dissolve
    a neutral "Estar en el 3-C no es tan terrible, supongo. Salvo por una parejita que siempre está peleando últimamente, y están volviendo locos a todos." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2166
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_6200ade0:

    # a neutral_side "Not to mention... well, maybe I'm overthinking it, but sometimes I wonder how many people in there even like me." with dissolve
    a neutral_side "Sin mencionar... bueno, tal vez solo estoy pensando demasiado, pero a veces me pregunto a cuánta gente le agrado realmente." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2167
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_cab2bb1f:

    # a uniform2 armband sigh "I mean, I do my best to be friendly with everyone, and I try not to let anything get to me." with dissolve
    a uniform2 armband sigh "Digo, me esfuerzo por ser amable con todos, e intento no dejar que nada me moleste." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2168
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_ae7afbc1:

    # a neutral "If someone puts me down, I'll always dust myself off, get back on my feet and try again." with dissolve
    a neutral "Si alguien me derriba, siempre me sacudo el polvo, me pongo de pie y lo vuelvo a intentar." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2169
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_c67ef8b8:

    # a neutral_side "But sometimes I wonder if anyone only talks to me at all because of this armband I'm wearing." with dissolve
    a neutral_side "Pero a veces me pregunto si la única razón por la que los demás siquiera me hablan es por esta banda en mi brazo." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2170
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_6f8e1440:

    # ks confused "Why would you think that? People liked you enough to vote you president didn't they?"
    ks confused "¿Por qué creerías eso? Le agradaste a la gente lo suficiente para que te eligiera presidenta, ¿no?"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2171
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_fd270c49:

    # a uniform_down2 armband_down sad_side "That is true, and it'll look good on my resumé for sure. But it's hardly a glamorous position." with dissolve
    a uniform_down2 armband_down sad_side "Eso es cierto, y sin duda se verá bien en mi currículum. Pero no puedo decir que es una posición glamorosa." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2172
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_1968ccbd:

    # a neutral_side "I guess no one else wanted the responsibility. Maybe everyone could count on me not to rock the boat too much." with dissolve
    a neutral_side "Supongo que nadie más quería la responsabilidad. Tal vez todos podían contar con que no sacudiera demasiado el barco." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2173
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_321d7c5e:

    # a sad "And geez, I don't even know why I'm telling you all this. I'm sorry." with dissolve
    a sad "Y cielos, ni siquiera sé por qué te estoy contando todo esto. Lo siento." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2174
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_fd2d2225:

    # a confused "I guess you're just that easy to talk to? I'm certainly enjoying these one-on-ones we're having." with dissolve
    a confused "¿Supongo que es lo fácil que es hablar contigo? Ciertamente estoy disfrutando estas charlas uno a uno que estamos teniendo." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2175
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_0d2095ca:

    # a smile "So when I think on that, sharing a class with Nozomi and the rest of you feels like it'd be just the best time right now." with dissolve
    a smile "Y cuando pienso en eso, compartir una clase con Nozomi y el resto de ustedes suena a que sería lo más lindo ahora mismo." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2176
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_b52a901b:

    # "Akiko breaks into a smile as she thinks of Nozomi again, and I smile back."
    "Akiko pone una sonrisa al pensar en Nozomi otra vez, y yo le sonrío a ella."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2177
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_da9960b2:

    # "But I need to get Akiko's focus back on what we're doing here."
    "Pero necesito regresar la atención de Akiko a lo que estamos haciendo aquí."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2178
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_56d4ddfb:

    # ks smile "Yeah. But still, I bet you could find a way to spend some more time with Nozomi too. Get to know her some more as a person."
    ks smile "Sí. Pero apuesto a que tú podrías encontrar una forma de pasar más tiempo con Nozomi. Conocerla un poco más como persona."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2180
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_c44a648a:

    # ks "Maybe being the student council president isn't so hot, but you still have some clout around here. I bet you could set up a meeting after school to talk about something or other." with dissolve
    ks "Ser la presidenta del consejo no será lo más alucinante, pero aun así tienes algo de influencia. Quizá podrías agendar una reunión después de clases para conversar." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2181
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_d4dee615:

    # a uniform2 armband sad "Kyou, I don't know what kind of authority you think I have, but I can't just compel another student to make smalltalk with me for no good reason." with dissolve
    a uniform2 armband sad "Kyou, no sé qué clase de autoridad crees que tengo, pero no puedo obligar a otro estudiante a charlar conmigo sin una buena razón." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2182
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_e63aa680:

    # ks neutral "Yeah, but... well, you could tell her you want to talk about me and what you were trying to accomplish with these lunchtime sessions."
    ks neutral "Sí, pero... bueno, podrías decirle que quieres hablar a cerca de mí y lo que has estado intentando lograr con estas sesiones durante los almuerzos."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2183
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_b2cad491:

    # a neutral_side "Hmm..." with dissolve
    a neutral_side "Mmm..." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2184
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_3a157305:

    # ks "She'd be interested, right? And the whole time you could really pay attention to what she says, how she says it, and how she carries herself. Really get to know the real Nozomi."
    ks "Estará interesada, ¿no? Y en ese tiempo podrás prestar atención a lo que dice, cómo lo dice, cómo actúa. Conocer realmente a la verdadera Nozomi."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2185
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_54d0d046:

    # a sad "Wow. I just..." with dissolve
    a sad "Guau. Eso..." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2186
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_85b67bb8:

    # ks smirk "Maybe leave out the fact we've mostly been talking about her this whole time."
    ks smirk "Tal vez omitiendo el hecho de que hemos estado hablando mayormente de ella todo este tiempo."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2187
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_679fe259:

    # a sad_side "Kyou..." with dissolve
    a sad_side "Kyou..." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2188
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_fb99aae4:

    # ks smile "Probably best not to mention that I hypnotized you too, just to be on the safe side."
    ks smile "Y probablemente sea mejor tampoco mencionar que te hipnoticé, solo para estar seguros."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2190
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_411083c4:

    # "I watch as Akiko uncomfortably runs one hand through her hair, while her other runs nervously over her stomach." with dissolve
    "Veo cómo Akiko pasa incómodamente una mano por su cabello, mientras que la otra se desliza nerviosamente por su estómago." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2191
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_e000dcab:

    # a "I don't know. I sort of want to... s-spend more time with her. Of course I do, but with my intentions? Keeping secrets from her? It just seems so invasive, and obviously deceitful."
    a "No lo sé... Sí quiero... p-pasar más tiempo con ella. Claro que sí, pero ¿con mis intenciones? ¿Guardándole secretos? Suena invasivo, como si la estuviera engañando."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2192
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_d5583b5d:

    # "Yeah. This whole time we've been talking, it's seemed to me that Akiko's deep desire to be more like Nozomi is warring with the fact Nozomi would never do this kind of stuff."
    "Sí. Todo el tiempo que llevamos hablando, parece que el profundo deseo de Akiko de ser más como Nozomi está en guerra con el hecho de que Nozomi nunca haría estas cosas."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2193
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_d6598d7e:

    # "So maybe I need to get a little more... persuasive with her."
    "Así que tal vez deba ser un poco más... persuasivo con ella."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2195
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_5a0530a6:

    # ks smile "Okay, well, let's set that aside for the time being. How about we have a little fun while there's still time." with dissolve
    ks smile "Está bien, bueno, dejemos eso de lado de momento. ¿Qué te parece si nos divertimos un poco mientras aún tenemos tiempo?" with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2199
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_07dc306f:

    # "It really shouldn't take much, as I pull my penlight from out of my pocket in front of her." with dissolve
    "No debería ser difícil, al sacar mi linterna del bolsillo frente a ella." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2200
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_1f4794aa:

    # a "Huh? Isn't that..."
    a "¿Eh? ¿Eso es...?"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2201
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_97cc718b:

    # ks "It's what I've been using to hypnotize you and Nozomi. So what do you say? Want to go under again?"
    ks "Es lo que he estado usando para hipnotizarlas a ti y a Nozomi. ¿Qué dices? ¿Quieres probarlo otra vez?"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2203
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_c900b870:

    # "And sure enough, Akiko can't resist the allure of being hypnotized. Not when she knows her idol would never turn down such an opportunity." with dissolve
    "Y desde luego, Akiko no puede resistir la tentación de ser hipnotizada. No cuando sabe que su ídolo nunca rechazaría una oportunidad así." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2204
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_2bee5785:

    # a "Oh, w-wow, what are you even planning to do this time?"
    a "Oh, g-guau, ¿y qué planeas hacer esta vez?"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2205
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_12db8d1b:

    # a laugh "Ahaha, no, don't tell me! It was such a thrill before, I don't even care~" with dissolve
    a laugh "¡Ajaja, no, no me digas! Fue tan emocionante la última vez que ni siquiera me importa." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2209
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_8435aa87:

    # "I gesture to her desk and she happily goes to sit while she keeps her eyes on me, an eager look on her face."
    "Señalo su escritorio y ella se sienta felizmente, manteniendo sus ojos en mí con una entusiasmada mirada en su rostro."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2210
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_0f08d8f1:

    # a "Do you think this could be a regular thing for us?"
    a "¿Crees que esto pueda volverse algo rutinario entre nosotros?"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2212
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_06e6fe94:

    # "I grin down on her as I hold my penlight aloft." with dissolve
    "Le sonrío mientras sostengo mi linterna en el aire." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2213
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_a1315661:

    # "Not gonna lie, this eagerness she's showing for me is something I could become very attracted to."
    "No mentiré, el entusiasmo que me está mostrando es algo que puede que empiece a atraerme bastante."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2214
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_d36b3f0b:

    # ks smile "We'll see. Now just relax and stare, Akiko."
    ks smile "Ya veremos. Ahora solo relájate y mantén la vista aquí, Akiko."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2215
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_b0a0e146:

    # "If only Nozomi would look at me the same way..."
    "Si tan solo Nozomi pudiera mirarme de la misma forma..."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2221
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_026a5312:

    # ks "Relax, and simply let this light hit your eyes as it passes back and forth."
    ks "Relájate, y simplemente deja que esta luz llegue a tus ojos al pasar de lado a lado."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2227
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_2faf0525:

    # ks neutral "Back and forth. Let everything else slip away, and observe this familiar pattern forming in front of you."
    ks neutral "De lado a lado. Deja que todo lo demás se desvanezca, y observa este familiar patrón formándose frente a ti."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2231
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_1ded8494:

    # ks "Focus on it and take a deep breath in, then out."
    ks "Concéntrate en él e inhala profundo, luego exhala."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2235
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_2c2b0dd1:

    # ks "Allow your body to melt into your chair, and let those eyes of yours do all the work."
    ks "Deja que tu cuerpo se derrita en la silla, y deja que tus ojos hagan todo el trabajo."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2239
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_c156271b:

    # ks "That's right, Akiko. It feels so good to let yourself drift into a hypnotic trance."
    ks "Eso es, Akiko. Se siente muy bien dejarte caer en un trance hipnótico."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2243
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_2caa3fc1:

    # ks "So just relax. And breathe. And stare..."
    ks "Solo relájate. E inhala. Y observa..."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2247
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_7f010497:

    # a "{size=16}Mmmmn...{/size}"
    a "{size=16}Mmmmn...{/size}"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2248
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_61ba9686:

    # "Heh. Was that a purr I just heard?"
    "Je. ¿Fue un ronroneo lo que escuché?"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2249
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_a0f7544c:

    # ks "And feel those eyelids becoming heavy. Allow yourself to become sleepier and sleepier..."
    ks "Y siente cómo tus párpados se ponen pesados y empiezas a sentir más y más sueño..."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2255
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_3a2d8ae3:

    # "I know I compelled you to want this, Akiko, but now I really do wonder if you were always this eager to be hypnotized. Always this easy to hypnotize..."
    "Sé que fui yo quien hizo que quisieras esto, Akiko, pero ahora me pregunto si siempre anhelaste tanto ser hipnotizada. Si siempre fuiste tan fácil de hipnotizar..."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2256
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_cd0ab13d:

    # ks "Allow yourself to sink. Deeper..."
    ks "Empiezas a hundirte. Más y más profundo..."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2260
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_978211ae:

    # ks "And deeper. Falling back into hypnosis."
    ks "Y más profundo. Cayendo de vuelta en hipnosis."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2264
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_0a9be0de:

    # "It's almost a shame that we'll never get to find out."
    "Es casi una pena que nunca lo averiguaremos."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2265
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_11a1504c:

    # ks "Now close your eyes, Akiko. Sleep."
    ks "Ahora cierra los ojos, Akiko. Duerme."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2269
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_3623e2b9:

    # "With my penlight, it's all become so completely irrelevant."
    "Con mi linterna, todo eso se ha vuelto completamente irrelevante."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2270
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_66ec9391:

    # ks "Sleep, and fall so very deep for me now. Let every conscious thought in your head disappear, and allow your subconscious to listen very carefully."
    ks "Duerme, y cae muy, muy profundo. Deja que todos tus pensamientos conscientes desaparezcan, y permite que tu subconsciente escuche con atención."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2271
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_9c96f4f4:

    # ks "Because we need to have another talk about Nozomi and your admiration for her."
    ks "Porque debemos tener otra charla sobre Nozomi y tu admiración por ella."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2272
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_09717e37:

    # ks "And you do admire Nozomi, don't you Akiko?"
    ks "Y tú admiras a Nozomi, ¿no es así, Akiko?"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2274
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_6e332c2a:

    # a "Yes... I admire Nozomi so much..." with dissolve
    a "Sí... admiro mucho a Nozomi..." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2276
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_69f9f502:

    # ks "You want to be everything that Nozomi is, don't you." with dissolve
    ks "Quieres ser todo lo que Nozomi es, ¿no es así?" with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2278
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_4aeacfa8:

    # a "Mmn, yes... want to be... everything she is..." with dissolve
    a "Mmn, sí... quiero ser... todo lo que ella es..." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2280
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_c5fb1e93:

    # ks "That's right. After all, these are your true, honest thoughts. But you're conflicted, because someone as perfect as Nozomi would never imitate another person to get ahead." with dissolve
    ks "Así es. Ese es u sincero deseo. Pero estás en conflicto, porque alguien tan perfecta como Nozomi nunca imitaría a otra persona." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2281
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_780079f9:

    # ks "Am I right about that, Akiko?"
    ks "¿Tengo razón, Akiko?"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2283
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_7756caf3:

    # a "Yes..." with dissolve
    a "Sí..." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2284
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_979d4dd3:

    # "Not that it wasn't obvious, but it's good to have her confirm it."
    "No es como si no fuera obvio, pero es bueno que me lo confirme."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2286
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_a19b99db:

    # "Maybe she'd push past it on her own if I gave her more time. She changed her hair quickly enough." with dissolve
    "Tal vez lo supere por su cuenta si le doy algo de tiempo. Cambió su cabello bastante rápido." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2287
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_638496b6:

    # "But why wait for results when I know I can just push her myself?"
    "Pero ¿por qué esperar por resultados cuando sé que puedo impulsarla yo mismo?"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2288
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_294e27b4:

    # ks smirk "Akiko... have you considered that imitation is the sincerest form of flattery?"
    ks smirk "Akiko... ¿has considerado que la imitación es la forma más sincera de adulación?"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2290
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_35ab0ebc:

    # a "I... n-no. Not really..." with dissolve
    a "Eh... n-no. No lo he... pensado..." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2292
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_fe0a0394:

    # ks neutral "You should. As a matter of fact, by impersonating Nozomi you would be honoring her." with dissolve
    ks neutral "Deberías. De hecho, al imitar a Nozomi, le estarías haciendo honor." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2293
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_6d84f269:

    # ks "There's no higher compliment you could give Nozomi than by doing everything in your power to replicate her to the tiniest detail."
    ks "No hay mayor cumplido que hacer todo lo que esté en tu poder para replicarla hasta el más fino detalle."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2294
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_3bdeea63:

    # ks "Do you understand now, Akiko?"
    ks "¿Entiendes ahora, Akiko?"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2296
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_74da31e8:

    # a "Yes... I understand." with dissolve
    a "Sí... entiendo." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2298
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_5ad8c5d8:

    # ks "I knew you would, Akiko. You're so very good at understanding, so very good at being hypnotized. Just like Nozomi." with dissolve
    ks "Sabía que entenderías, Akiko. Eres muy buena entendiendo, muy buena siendo hipnotizada. Justo como Nozomi." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2299
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_66d12d2c:

    # ks "So now it's almost time to wake up. I'm going to once again count you up to five, when you will awaken."
    ks "Y ahora casi es momento de despertar. Una vez más voy a contar hasta cinco, y en ese momento despertarás."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2300
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_0e8c3933:

    # ks "And when you wake you will once again not remember any suggestions I made to your subconscious. You will only remember that you were hypnotized."
    ks "Y cuando despiertes, una vez más no recordarás ninguna sugestión que le haya dado a tu subconsciente. "

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2301
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_bd77a022:

    # ks "Counting up now... one, two, feeling lighter... three, four..."
    ks "Empezando ahora... uno, dos, te sientes más ligera... tres, cuatro..."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2303
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_e203c574:

    # ks "Thoughts returning, waking up happy and refreshed... five."
    ks "Tus pensamientos regresan, y despiertas fresca y contenta... cinco."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2306
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_d01f61e7:

    # a "{size=16}Mmm... {/size}" with dissolve
    a "{size=16}Mmm... {/size}" with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2308
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_f0846940:

    # "I watch with satisfaction as the student council president opens her eyes with another happy little purr."
    "Observo con satisfacción cómo la presidenta del consejo estudiantil abre los ojos con otro alegre ronroneo."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2309
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_8a8ec08f:

    # ks smile "Welcome back, Akiko. Wasn't that fun?"
    ks smile "Bienvenida de vuelta, Akiko. ¿Fue divertido?"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2310
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_decf66b9:

    # a "I don't even know how you do it, but... wow, you give me such a thrill every time we do this, Kyou!"
    a "¡Ni siquiera sé cómo lo haces, pero... guau, siento mucha emoción cada vez que hacemos esto, Kyou!"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2311
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_b7ab6aa8:

    # "There. I'm sure Akiko's about to find any doubts she had about what I'm asking of her have suddenly resolved themselves."
    "Listo. Estoy seguro de que todas las dudas que Akiko tenía sobre lo que le estoy pidiendo se habrán resuelto por sí solas."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2312
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_db3f96bc:

    # ks "That's great to hear. Hypnosis is supposed to feel good, and it feels great to put you under, Akiko."
    ks "Me alegra escuchar eso. Se supone que la hipnosis se sienta bien, y se siente grandioso hipnotizarte, Akiko."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2313
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_39f38c60:

    # ks "Not to mention how awesome it is that you seem so into it. Guess that's something you and Nozomi just naturally have in common, huh?"
    ks "Sin mencionar lo genial que es que parezca gustarte tanto. Supongo que eso es algo que Nozomi y tú tienen naturalmente en común."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2318
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_7764c387:

    # "To that, Akiko just giggles as she stands up from the seat."
    "En respuesta a eso, Akiko simplemente se levanta de su asiento con una risita."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2319
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_e6748950:

    # a "Ahaha, you can say that again~ {font=DejaVuSans.ttf}♥{/font}"
    a "Ajaja, eso puedes decirlo de nuevo. {font=DejaVuSans.ttf}♥{/font}"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2320
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_f9eb23d0:

    # ks smile "Speaking of which, have you thought any more on what I said about meeting Nozomi later?"
    ks smile "Hablando de eso, ¿has pensado más en lo que dije sobre reunirte con Nozomi más tarde?"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2322
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_b12b3034:

    # "The moment I ask, Akiko responds with a happy little nod of her head." with dissolve
    "Tan pronto pregunto, Akiko responde asintiendo alegremente la cabeza." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2323
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_1df9f3a3:

    # a "Yup! I'm excited to make more time for her if I'm being totally honest."
    a "¡Sipi! Estoy emocionada por hacer tiempo para ella, siendo honesta."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2324
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_c8ad308e:

    # ks smirk "Just remember what I said. Make sure she doesn't know what you're up to and don't say I hypnotized you, okay?"
    ks smirk "Solo recuerda lo que dije. Asegúrate de que no sepa lo que pretendes y no digas que te hipnoticé, ¿de acuerdo?"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2325
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_50052d58:

    # a happy "But of course! I can be discreet, and it'd be the best way to honor her brilliance anyhow." with dissolve
    a happy "¡Pero desde luego! Puedo ser discreta, y será la mejor manera de hacerle honor a su esplendor." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2326
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_79b52904:

    # a laugh_wink "I'll be her secret admirer~ {font=DejaVuSans.ttf}♥{/font}" with dissolve
    a laugh_wink "Seré su admiradora secreta. {font=DejaVuSans.ttf}♥{/font}" with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2327
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_7a53e30e:

    # "I can't help but chuckle at this infectious enthusiasm of hers."
    "No puedo evitar reírme ante su contagioso entusiasmo."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2328
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_33b6fcbd:

    # ks smile "You sure will. I'm looking forward to finding out how much you've learned tomorrow."
    ks smile "Así se habla. Muero de ganas de averiguar cuánto aprendiste mañana."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2331
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_36aa98fb:

    # "After all that, we barely had any time to wolf down our lunches and head back to class. But I'm satisfied."
    "Después de eso, apenas tuvimos tiempo de acabarnos nuestros almuerzos y volver a clase. Pero estoy satisfecho."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2338
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_69269ff7:

    # n "Stand!"
    n "¡De pie!"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2339
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_e819aba9:

    # n "Bow!"
    n "¡Reverencia!"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2341
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_5306f3dc:

    # "The rest of the day dragged on as usual, but we're past it now." with dissolve
    "El resto del día fue lento como de costumbre, pero por fin terminó." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2344
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_633cc44f:

    # h "Alright, I'm outta here. C'mon, Nozo." with dissolve
    h "Muy bien, me largo de aquí. Vamos, Nozo." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2345
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_d9531fbc:

    # "Naturally I'm still keeping as low a profile as I can in the classroom."
    "Naturalmente, aún mantengo un perfil tan bajo como puedo en el salón."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2349
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_b37bf7e6:

    # n "Right behind you, Hiroko. Good luck in practice today." with dissolve
    n "Voy detrás de ti, Hiroko. Buena suerte en la práctica de hoy." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2350
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_74c12099:

    # "Not that it seems to have diffused the tension in here much."
    "Aunque eso no parece haber reducido mucho la tensión por aquí."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2353
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_5e3ad567:

    # s "Yes, let us all do our best today." with dissolve
    s "Sí, todas hagamos nuestro mayor esfuerzo hoy." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2357
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_feea5124:

    # "Still, I'm mindful to wait until Nozomi is out the door before I stand up to leave myself." with dissolve
    "Aun así, procuro esperar a que Nozomi haya salido por la puerta antes de levantarme." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2359
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_7221844d:

    # "It's just better that I don't get too close to her now. Not even by accident."
    "Será mejor no acercarme demasiado a ella. Ni siquiera por accidente."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2360
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_68894c31:

    # a "Excuse me, Nozomi? Do you have a moment?"
    a "Disculpa, ¿Nozomi? ¿Tienes un momento?"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2369
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_b2c61708:

    # "So when I hear a now familiar voice ring out amongst the crowds of departing students, I come to a sudden halt before quickly ducking behind a corner." with dissolve
    "Así que cuando escucho una voz familiar entre la multitud de estudiantes, me detengo en seco y me oculto rápidamente detrás de una esquina." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2370
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_707f9e9b:

    # n shocked_side "A-Akiko?! Is... that a new look?" with dissolve
    n shocked_side "¡¿A-Akiko?! ¿Te... hiciste un cambio de imagen?" with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2371
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_e9e4a825:

    # s uniform_handup "It most certainly is." with dissolve
    s uniform_handup "Ciertamente así parece." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2372
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_59c2c227:

    # "And I simply listen."
    "Y simplemente escucho."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2373
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_590de2c6:

    # a uniform_up2 armband_up embarrassed_side blush "Oh wow, i-it's just like you to notice~ {font=DejaVuSans.ttf}♥{/font}" with dissolve
    a uniform_up2 armband_up embarrassed_side blush "Oh, guau, s-sabía que tenías un buen ojo. {font=DejaVuSans.ttf}♥{/font}" with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2375
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_6f2e4139:

    # h annoyed_side "'s pretty obvious, 'Kiko." with dissolve
    h annoyed_side "Es bastante obvio, 'Kiko." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2376
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_69d2cc1e:

    # n smile_side "Well, that's... great. You look really nice, Akiko." with dissolve
    n smile_side "Bueno, es... genial. Te ves muy bien, Akiko." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2377
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_cf5aa222:

    # a uniform2 armband laugh "Wow... eee, that means SO much coming from you, Nozomi!" with dissolve
    a uniform2 armband laugh "Guau... ¡aah, significa MUCHO viniendo de ti, Nozomi!" with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2378
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_b4ab6d9d:

    # "Oh my god, don't blow this, Akiko. Dial it down a notch..."
    "Oh, por Dios, no lo heches a perder, Akiko. Bájale dos rayitas..."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2379
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_3159d24e:

    # a smile_side "Err, b-but enough about me. I just wanted to ask if you had time to chat tonight?" with dissolve
    a smile_side "Emm, p-pero basta de mí. Solo quería preguntar si tenías tiempo de conversar esta noche." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2380
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_bce74ed7:

    # n sad_side "Huh? Why, is something the matter?" with dissolve
    n sad_side "¿Eh? ¿Por qué, sucede algo?" with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2381
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_ccf2942f:

    # a uniform_down2 armband_down confused_side -blush "It's... well, I can't really go into it here. Actually that's why I wanted to talk to you off the premises, if you know what I mean." with dissolve
    a uniform_down2 armband_down confused_side -blush "Es... bueno, no puedo entrar en detalles aquí. De hecho, quería hablar contigo fuera de las instalaciones, si es que me entiendes." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2382
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_0948792d:

    # s uniform frown_right "Well that can only mean one thing, as far as Nozomi is concerned." with dissolve
    s uniform frown_right "Bueno, solo puede ser una cosa, en lo que a Nozomi concierne." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2383
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_545cbd9a:

    # "That's better. I think she's saved herself, but..."
    "Así está mejor. Creo que logró salvarlo, pero..."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2386
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_ab048838:

    # h frown "An' I sure as shit didn't see him pass us. Did you?" with dissolve
    h frown "Y de puta casualidad no es él al que vi pasar. ¿O sí?" with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2388
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_5ee4dc28:

    # "I need to make myself scarce."
    "Tengo que esfumarme."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2390
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_33723c37:

    # "So I hurried into the men's bathroom and hid in a cubicle until I was sure those girls departed for their clubs."
    "Así que corrí al baño de hombres y me escondí en un cubículo hasta que estuve seguro de que esas chicas se fueron cada una a su club."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2392
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_7ea16563:

    # "And once the coast was clear, I headed straight home with nothing left to do but listlessly gaze at my study notes and think about tomorrow."
    "Cuando supe que no había moros en la costa, me fui directo a casa sin nada más que hacer que mirar desganado mis notas de estudio, pensando en mañana."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2393
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_e0bdb6de:

    # "Really wish I could be there for Akiko and Nozomi's talk."
    "En serio desearía poder estar ahí durante la charla entre Akiko y Nozomi."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2395
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_806c4dd1:

    # "It would've been far too dangerous to tail them; I know that. Hell, it was kinda dicey to even have her do this for me."
    "Habría sido muy peligroso seguirlas; eso lo sé. Caray, el solo mandarla a hacer esto por mí ya es arriesgado."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2396
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_b0423056:

    # "I have no idea what Nozomi really thinks of mine and Akiko's little lunchtime sessions. Whether she thinks I did anything to her."
    "No tengo idea de lo que Nozomi piensa realmente de mis sesiones con Akiko durante el almuerzo. O si piensa que le hice algo."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2397
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_2059520c:

    # "She's surely still worried about me. But... well, if Nozomi knows anything about hypnosis, she'll know hypnosis only works on the willing, like I did."
    "Es seguro que aún la preocupo. Pero... bueno, si Nozomi sabe algo sobre hipnosis, sabrá que solo funciona si así lo deseas, como lo supe yo."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2400
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_fbf3a515:

    # "She certainly doesn't know what I have here with this penlight. Certainly doesn't know it like I do."
    "Ciertamente no sabe de lo que tengo aquí con esta linterna. Ciertamente no lo sabe como yo."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2401
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_0836b6f1:

    # "Maybe she felt scared to go along, like Akiko said. Maybe she really did feel a temptation to go along, like I thought she had when I tried it on her."
    "Tel vez siguió la corriente por miedo, como dijo Akiko. Tal vez en realidad sintió la tentación de seguir la corriente, como yo pensé cuando lo intenté con ella."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2402
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_e3670b82:

    # "There's plenty of ways for her to rationalize what happened that day that doesn't involve me having such a powerful hypnotic tool at my disposal."
    "Hay muchas formas en las que puede racionalizar lo que pasó ese día que no involucran que yo tenga una poderosa herramienta hipnótica a mi disposición."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2406
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_481692ee:

    # "Yeah. So long as Akiko doesn't cream her panties talking to her idol, I'm sure Nozomi won't suspect I did anything weird on her."
    "Sí. Mientras Akiko no empape demasiado su ropa interior mientras habla con su ídolo, estoy seguro de que Nozomi no sospechará que le hice nada raro."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2407
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_18553507:

    # "Man, she'd better not fuck this up for me..."
    "Caray, más vale que no eche todo a la mierda..."
# TODO: Translation updated at 2025-05-02 21:19

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2376
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_9861f9a8:

    # s sleeptalk "Indeed. When we were colleagues at student council, you always wore that same bobbed haircut." with dissolve
    s sleeptalk "Efectivamente. Cuando éramos colegas en el consejo estudiantil, siempre llevaste el mismo corte Bob." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2377
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_65f8a051:

    # s concerned "Curious that you went to such an effort now of all times." with dissolve
    s concerned "Qué curioso que hayas elegido nada menos que este día para dedicar tal esfuerzo." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:2378
translate spanish Day4_Villain2_Kyou_db17099a:

    # n smile_side "W-well... that being said, it suits you. You look really nice, Akiko." with dissolve
    n smile_side "B-bueno... dicho eso, te queda bien. Te ves muy linda, Akiko." with dissolve
