# game/kyou 4.rpy:7829
translate spanish Day4_Redemption_f69ce6ee:

    # a smile "I was part of the choir in elementary school, and then in junior high I joined their kendo club." with dissolve
    a smile "Fui parte del coro en mi primaria, y luego en secundaria me uní al club de kendo." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:7856
translate spanish Day4_Redemption_931e2607:

    # a uniform_down smile "Well, I'm happy you're opening up a bit more. It's nice to meet you properly, Kyou Koyama." with dissolve
    a uniform_down smile "Bueno, me alegra que te estés abriendo un poco más. Es un gusto conocerte adecuadamente, Kyou Koyama." with dissolve
