# game/kyou 4.rpy:5494
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_6e91c0e4:

    # ks frown "Sayori, that's enough!"
    ks frown "¡Sayori, ya es suficiente!"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5495
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_a661700f:

    # "I can't... I can't handle this."
    "No puedo... no puedo con esto."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5496
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_6aecfcb2:

    # s scared_right "{cps=15}Y-you... no, don't you dare-{/cps}{w=0.5}{nw}" with dissolve
    s scared_right "{cps=15}N-no... ¡no, no te atrevas-{/cps}{w=0.5}{nw}" with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5497
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_88f67381:

    # ks "Become [alt_name]."
    ks "Conviértete en [alt_name]."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5498
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_25954959:

    # s uniform "Nng..." with dissolve
    s uniform "Nng..." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5499
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_994d8260:

    # "I could see, from that momentary expression of wild panic in her eyes that she knew what I was about to say."
    "Pude ver, en esa momentánea expresión desbordante de pánico en sus ojos, que sabía lo que estaba a punto de decir."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5501
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_d22df3f6:

    # ks confused "You're [alt_name] now... right?" with dissolve
    ks confused "Eres [alt_name] ahora... ¿verdad?" with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5502
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_85fa7ed9:

    # "But it doesn't seem to matter. Even now, it doesn't matter."
    "Pero eso no parece importar. Incluso ahora, no importa en lo absoluto."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5504
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_3b5fa3cf:

    # s uniform_handup "Y-yes, of course I am. But... Kyou?" with dissolve
    s uniform_handup "S-sí, por supuesto. Pero... ¿Kyou?" with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5505
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_c89f6d09:

    # "Just those two words is all it takes to bring all that shit she was talking; the tears, the hysterics, all of it... to an abrupt end."
    "Solo esas tres palabras hacen falta para que toda esa mierda de la que estaba hablando: las lágrimas, la histeria, todo... se detenga abruptamente."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5506
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_4d3950e0:

    # ks "Yeah?"
    ks "¿Sí?"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5507
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_6d10d97a:

    # s uniform_folded concerned_right "Why am I... s-shaking like this? I feel so tense and... teary?" with dissolve
    s uniform_folded concerned_right "¿Por qué estoy... t-temblando así? Me siento tensa y... ¿me lloran los ojos?" with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5508
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_7227066a:

    # "I don't exactly feel the best about that, but at least things are starting to calm down around here."
    "No estoy muy orgulloso que digamos de eso, pero al menos las cosas comienzan a calmarse por aquí."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5509
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_3e7f7513:

    # "All I need to do is put the particulars out of my head for now, and reassure Sayori... no, \"[alt_name]\", that everything's fine."
    "Lo único que debo hacer es no pensar en los detalles ahora, y asegurarle a Sayori... no, a \"[alt_name]\", que todo está bien."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5510
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_0fa22ccb:

    # ks smile "It's okay, [alt_name]. I hypnotized you again just now, and you're a little disoriented. That's all it is."
    ks smile "No te preocupes, [alt_name]. Te acabo de volver a hipnotizar, y estás un poco desorientada. Eso es todo."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5511
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_89ecc280:

    # s surprised_right "Really?" with dissolve
    s surprised_right "¿De verdad?" with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5512
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_98e09a23:

    # ks "Really. Maybe it's best if we lay off the hypnosis for now, at least until you're feeling better."
    ks "De verdad. Tal vez sea mejor tomarnos un descanso de la hipnosis por ahora, al menos hasta que te sientas mejor."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5514
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_e337a617:

    # "Sayori, now fully embracing her light-hearted side, puts a hand to her chest and lets out a hearty giggle as she nods in agreement." with dissolve
    "Sayori, ahora apegándose por completo a su lado jovial, se lleva una mano al pecho y asiente con una vigorosa risita." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5515
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_e96b2c23:

    # s "I am beginning to feel better already, but... yes, perhaps that would be for the best."
    s "Ya empiezo a sentirme mejor, pero... sí, quizá eso sea para mejor."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5516
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_84468966:

    # s smile_right "Although I am just dying to know what sort of mental trickery you played upon me this time. Were you attempting something ambitious?" with dissolve
    s smile_right "Aunque muero por saber qué clase de artimaña mental me jugaste esta vez. ¿Intentabas algo ambicioso?" with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5517
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_b62e4b0a:

    # ks "Yeah... you could say that."
    ks "Sí... podría decirse."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5518
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_c7ebfb70:

    # "Convincing Sayori to take on a new persona certainly does feel wild as hell. Even more so that it seems to be working."
    "Convencer a Sayori de adoptar una nueva personalidad ciertamente parece una tremenda locura. Y más aún que parezca estar funcionando."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5519
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_4d23b77b:

    # s happy "Mhmhmhm come now, don't get coy with me~" with dissolve
    s happy "Jijiji, vamos, no seas tímido conmigo." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5520
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_9f0225ed:

    # "So could I... leave her like this? Just let her out of here thinking happy thoughts for tonight?"
    "Entonces ¿podría... dejarla así? ¿Permitir que salga de aquí con pensamientos alegres por esta noche?"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5521
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_15b4292a:

    # ks "Ahhh, well it's..."
    ks "Aaah, bueno, pues..."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5522
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_7580759e:

    # "Would that be so bad? After all the stress she's put herself under it might do her some good."
    "¿Sería tan malo? Luego de todo el estrés al que se ha sometido, tal vez le haga bien."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5523
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_92cc06fc:

    # s frown "Oh... wait, hold that thought." with dissolve
    s frown "Oh... aguarda, espera un segundo." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5524
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_998046b8:

    # "But just then that happy facade fades as a frown creases her features."
    "Pero en ese momento, la feliz fachada desaparece, y en su lugar, un ceño fruncido se forma en su rostro."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5525
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_69d5e8c4:

    # ks confused "What's wrong?"
    ks confused "¿Qué ocurre?"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5527
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_c653ce34:

    # "At first I fear she's already about to drop the act. But something about Sayori's theatrical sigh makes me think this is not about our fight at all." with dissolve
    "Al principio temí que estuviera a punto de dejar el acto. Pero hay algo en el teatral suspiro de Sayori que me hace pensar que esto no tiene nada que ver con nuestra pelea." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5528
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_95020191:

    # s "Haaah... I need to attend cram school, much as I so badly wish that were not the case."
    s "Aaay... debo asistir a los cursos nocturnos, por más que desee que ese no fuese el caso."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5529
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_67da3e86:

    # ks "Oh... right."
    ks "Oh... cierto."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5530
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_61a8c2db:

    # s uniform_folded rolleyes "Perhaps if I hadn't already skipped class this morning I would be tempted to try my luck." with dissolve
    s uniform_folded rolleyes "Quizá si no me hubiera saltado la clase esta mañana, estaría tentada a poner a prueba mi suerte." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5531
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_985e1e0b:

    # "... Wait a minute."
    "... Un segundo."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5532
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_4fcef83d:

    # ks confused "Wasn't that..."
    ks confused "¿Qué eso no fue...?"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5533
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_8b46cb3d:

    # s smile_right "Well, it was nice while it lasted. We'll have to do this again!" with dissolve
    s smile_right "Bueno, fue lindo mientras duró. ¡Será en otra ocasión!" with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5534
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_fe8a7144:

    # "Didn't she \"skip class\" yesterday?"
    "¿Qué no se \"saltó la clase\" ayer?"

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5535
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_1662c083:

    # ks "Uh... yeah."
    ks "Eh... sí."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5536
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_8f49cb23:

    # "I don't know if I want to press her on that."
    "No sé si quiero preguntarle al respecto."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5537
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_33be3362:

    # s happy "Have a good evening, Kyou!" with dissolve
    s happy "¡Que tengas una buena velada, Kyou!" with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5538
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_21d5bf4a:

    # "And besides, she's already strapped for time so I probably shouldn't keep her."
    "Y además, ya de por sí está corta de tiempo, por lo que tal vez no deba retenerla."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5539
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_6c9768e3:

    # ks smile "You too."
    ks smile "Igual tú."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5541
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_ef61f0dd:

    # "But still, if she really is confused about what day it is then... what does that mean?" with dissolve
    "Pero, si de verdad no sabe qué día es... ¿eso qué significa?" with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5544
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_d0dec468:

    # "... I probably shouldn't worry so much."
    "... Tal vez no debería preocuparme demasiado."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5545
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_39e3a24f:

    # "I mean... if Sayori really, *really* wants to she'll snap back to her regular self a little later."
    "Digo... si Sayori, *realmente* quiere, regresará a su yo habitual más tarde."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5546
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_2392d0e7:

    # "Sayori can rant and rave about \"second personalities\" and not being able to resist a simple hypnotic suggestion, but she has to know she's just overthinking it."
    "Sayori podrá quejarse de \"segundas personalidades\" y no poder resistir una simple sugestión hipnótica, pero seguro entiende que lo está pensando demasiado."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5547
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_be48eb4d:

    # "She just needed an excuse to chill out about this. But tomorrow we can try this conversation again when we both have clearer heads."
    "Solo necesitaba una excusa para relajarse y despreocuparse. Pero mañana podemos volver a intentar esta conversación cuando ambos hayamos aclarado nuestras ideas."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5549
translate spanish Day4_Con_Kyou_Sayori_ccd4fe27:

    # "Maybe then she won't be so damned dramatic..."
    "Tal vez entonces no se ponga tan dramática..."
# TODO: Translation updated at 2026-02-02 20:26

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5369
translate spanish Day4_Switch_Safe_2a86464a:

    # "The next morning arrives, and I'm walking to school with only one purpose..."
    "Llega la mañana siguiente, y yo camino a la escuela con solo un propósito..."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5373
translate spanish Day4_Switch_Safe_68b5cc07:

    # "... To see this dull day through to the end."
    "... Llegar al final de este tedioso día."

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5377
translate spanish Day4_Switch_Safe_a65a0866:

    # h "C'mooon, what're you thinking about?" with dissolve
    h "Aaanda, no seas malita, ya dime en qué tanto estás pensando." with dissolve

# game/kyou 4.rpy:5378
